#: functions/bitops.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Bit Operations"
msgstr "Oibríocht Giotán"

#: functions/bitops.xml:11 functions/bitops.xml:31 functions/bitops.xml:49
#: functions/bitops.xml:67 functions/bitops.xml:87 functions/math.xml:71
#: functions/math.xml:92
#, kde-format
msgid "First number"
msgstr "An chéad uimhir"

#: functions/bitops.xml:15 functions/bitops.xml:71 functions/bitops.xml:91
#: functions/math.xml:75 functions/math.xml:96
#, kde-format
msgid "Second number"
msgstr "An dara uimhir"

#: functions/bitops.xml:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BITAND() function performs a bit-wise AND operation for the two integer "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm BITAND() oibríocht AND giotán-bhunaithe don dá "
"pharaiméadar slánuimhreach."

#: functions/bitops.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid "BITAND(value; value)"
msgstr "BITAND(luach;luach)"

#: functions/bitops.xml:21
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"BITAND(12;10) returns 8 (because decimal 12 is binary 1100, and decimal 10 "
"is binary 1010; and 1100 \"anded\" with 1010 is 1000, which is integer 8)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann BITAND(12;10) 8 ar ais (toisc go bhfuil deachúil 12 ina dhénártha "
"1100, agus go bhfuil deachúil 10 ina dhénártha 1010; agus nuair a chuirtear "
"\"and\" le 1100 agus 1010 ina dhénártha, is é sin slánuimhir 8)."

#: functions/bitops.xml:35
#, kde-format
msgid "Amount to left shift by"
msgstr "Méid le haistriú ar chlé"

#: functions/bitops.xml:39
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BITLSHIFT() function performs a bit-wise left shift operation of the "
"first parameter. The number of bits to shift by is specified by the second "
"parameter. Note that a negative number of bits to left shift by becomes a "
"right shift. "
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm BITLSHIFT() oibríocht aistrithe ar chlé de réir giotán "
"den chéad pharaiméadar. Sonraítear líon na ngiotán le haistriú leis an dara "
"paraiméadar. Tabhair faoi deara go n-éiríonn líon diúltach giotán le "
"haistriú ar chlé ina aistriú ar dheis. "

#: functions/bitops.xml:40
#, kde-format
msgid "BITLSHIFT(value; shift size)"
msgstr "BITLSHIFT(luach; méid aistrithe)"

#: functions/bitops.xml:53
#, kde-format
msgid "Amount to right shift by"
msgstr "Méid le haistriú ar dheis"

#: functions/bitops.xml:57
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BITRSHIFT() function performs a bit-wise right shift operation of the "
"first parameter. The number of bits to shift by is specified by the second "
"parameter. Note that a negative number of bits to right shift by becomes a "
"left shift. "
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm BITRSHIFT() oibríocht aistrithe ar dheis de réir giotán "
"an chéad pharaiméadar. Sonraítear líon na ngiotán le haistriú leis an dara "
"paraiméadar. Tabhair faoi deara go n-éiríonn líon diúltach giotán le "
"haistriú ar dheis ina aistriú ar chlé. "

#: functions/bitops.xml:58
#, kde-format
msgid "BITRSHIFT(value; shift size)"
msgstr "BITRSHIFT(luach; méid aistrithe)"

#: functions/bitops.xml:75
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BITOR() function performs a bit-wise OR operation for the two integer "
"parameters. "
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm BITOR() oibríocht NÓ giotán-chiallach don dá pharaiméadar "
"slánuimhir. "

#: functions/bitops.xml:76
#, kde-format
msgid "BITOR(value; value)"
msgstr "BITOR(luach;luach)"

#: functions/bitops.xml:77
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"BITOR(12;10) returns 14 (because decimal 12 is binary 1100, and decimal 10 "
"is binary 1010; and 1100 \"ored\" with 1010 is 1110, which is integer 14)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann BITOR(12;10) 14 ar ais (toisc go bhfuil deachúil 12 ina ionann le "
"1100, agus go bhfuil deachúil 10 ina ionann le 1010; agus 1100 \"ored\" le "
"1010 ina ionann le 1110, arb ionann é agus slánuimhir 14)."

#: functions/bitops.xml:95
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BITXOR() function performs a bit-wise exclusive-OR operation for the two "
"integer parameters. "
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm BITXOR() oibríocht eisiach-OR giotán-dhóthanach don dá "
"pharaiméadar slánuimhir. "

#: functions/bitops.xml:96
#, kde-format
msgid "BITXOR(value; value)"
msgstr "BITXOR(luach; luach)"

#: functions/bitops.xml:97
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"BITXOR(12;10) returns 6 (because decimal 12 is binary 1100, and decimal 10 "
"is binary 1010; and 1100 \"xored\" with 1010 is 0110, which is integer 6)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann BITXOR(12;10) 6 ar ais (toisc go bhfuil deachúil 12 ina dhénártha "
"1100, agus go bhfuil deachúil 10 ina dhénártha 1010; agus is é 1100 \"xored"
"\" le 1010 ná 0110, arb ionann é agus slánuimhir 6)."

#: functions/conversion.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Conversion"
msgstr "Tiontú"

#: functions/conversion.xml:11 functions/conversion.xml:44
#, kde-format
msgid "Bool value to convert"
msgstr "Luach Boole le tiontú"

#: functions/conversion.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BOOL2STRING() function returns a string value for a given boolean value. "
"This method is intended for using a boolean in methods which require a string"
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm BOOL2STRING() luach teaghráin ar ais le haghaidh luach "
"booléanach ar leith. Tá an modh seo beartaithe chun luach booléanach a úsáid "
"i modhanna a éilíonn teaghrán"

#: functions/conversion.xml:16
#, kde-format
msgid "BOOL2STRING(value)"
msgstr "BOOL2STRING(luach)"

#: functions/conversion.xml:17
#, kde-format
msgid "BOOL2STRING(true) returns \"True\""
msgstr "Filleann BOOL2STRING(true) é seo: \"True\""

#: functions/conversion.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid "BOOL2STRING(false) returns \"False\""
msgstr "Filleann BOOL2STRING(false) é seo: \"False\""

#: functions/conversion.xml:19
#, kde-format
msgid "upper(BOOL2STRING(find(\"nan\";\"banana\"))) returns TRUE"
msgstr "Tugann upper(BOOL2STRING(find(\"nan\";\"banana\"))) TRUE ar ais"

#: functions/conversion.xml:27
#, kde-format
msgid "Integer value to convert"
msgstr "Slánuimhir le tiontú"

#: functions/conversion.xml:31
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The INT2BOOL() function returns a boolean value for a given integer number. "
"This method is intended for using an integer in methods which require a "
"boolean. It only accepts 0 or 1. If any other value is given, false is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm INT2BOOL() luach booléanach ar ais le haghaidh slánuimhir "
"ar leith. Tá an modh seo beartaithe chun slánuimhir a úsáid i modhanna a "
"éilíonn luach booléanach. Ní ghlacann sé ach le 0 nó 1. Má thugtar aon luach "
"eile, cuirtear bréagach ar ais."

#: functions/conversion.xml:32
#, kde-format
msgid "INT2BOOL(value)"
msgstr "INT2BOOL(luach)"

#: functions/conversion.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid "INT2BOOL(1) returns true"
msgstr "Filleann INT2BOOL(1) é seo: true"

#: functions/conversion.xml:34
#, kde-format
msgid "INT2BOOL(0) returns false"
msgstr "Filleann INT2BOOL(0) é seo: false"

#: functions/conversion.xml:35
#, kde-format
msgid "OR(INT2BOOL(1); false) returns true"
msgstr "Filleann OR(INT2BOOL(1); false) é seo: true"

#: functions/conversion.xml:48
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BOOL2INT() function returns an integer value for a given boolean value. "
"This method is intended for using a boolean value in methods which require "
"an integer."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm BOOL2INT() luach slánuimhir ar ais do luach booléanach ar "
"leith. Tá an modh seo beartaithe chun luach booléanach a úsáid i modhanna a "
"éilíonn slánuimhir."

#: functions/conversion.xml:49
#, kde-format
msgid "BOOL2INT(value)"
msgstr "BOOL2INT(luach)"

#: functions/conversion.xml:50
#, kde-format
msgid "BOOL2INT(True) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann BOOL2INT(True) é seo: 1"

#: functions/conversion.xml:51
#, kde-format
msgid "BOOL2INT(False) returns 0"
msgstr "Filleann BOOL2INT(False) é seo: 0"

#: functions/conversion.xml:60 functions/conversion.xml:77
#, kde-format
msgid "Number to convert into string"
msgstr "Uimhir le tiontú go teaghrán"

#: functions/conversion.xml:64
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The NUM2STRING() function returns a string value for a given number. Note "
"that Calligra Sheets can auto-convert numbers to strings if needed, so this "
"function should rarely be needed."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm NUM2STRING() luach teaghráin ar ais d'uimhir ar leith. "
"Tabhair faoi deara gur féidir le Calligra Sheets uimhreacha a thiontú go "
"teaghráin go huathoibríoch más gá, mar sin is annamh a bheadh gá leis an "
"bhfeidhm seo."

#: functions/conversion.xml:65
#, kde-format
msgid "NUM2STRING(value)"
msgstr "NUM2STRING(luach)"

#: functions/conversion.xml:66
#, kde-format
msgid "NUM2STRING(10) returns \"10\""
msgstr "Filleann NUM2STRING(10) é seo: \"10\""

#: functions/conversion.xml:67
#, kde-format
msgid "NUM2STRING(2.05) returns \"2.05\""
msgstr "Filleann NUM2STRING(2.05) é seo: \"2.05\""

#: functions/conversion.xml:68
#, kde-format
msgid "=find(\"101\";NUM2STRING(A1)) (A1 = 2.010102) returns True"
msgstr "=aimsigh(\"101\";NUM2STRING(A1)) (A1 = 2.010102) tugann sé Fíor ar ais"

#: functions/conversion.xml:81
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The STRING() function returns a string value for a given number. It is the "
"same as the NUM2STRING function."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm STRING() luach teaghráin ar ais le haghaidh uimhir ar "
"leith. Tá sé mar an gcéanna leis an fheidhm NUM2STRING."

#: functions/conversion.xml:90
#, kde-format
msgid "A one character string to convert"
msgstr "Teaghrán aon charachtair amháin le tiontú"

#: functions/conversion.xml:94
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CHARTOASCII() function returns the ASCII code for the given character."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm CHARTOASCII() an cód ASCII don charachtar tugtha ar ais."

#: functions/conversion.xml:95
#, kde-format
msgid "CHARTOASCII(value)"
msgstr "CHARTOASCII(luach)"

#: functions/conversion.xml:96
#, kde-format
msgid "CHARTOASCII(\"v\") returns 118"
msgstr "Filleann CHARTOASCII(\"v\") é seo: 118"

#: functions/conversion.xml:97
#, kde-format
msgid "CHARTOASCII(r) is an error. The character must be in quotes."
msgstr ""
"Is earráid í CHARTOASCII(r). Caithfidh an carachtar a bheith idir "
"athfhriotail."

#: functions/conversion.xml:105
#, kde-format
msgid "The ASCII values to convert"
msgstr "Na luachanna ASCII le tiontú"

#: functions/conversion.xml:109
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ASCIITOCHAR() function returns the character for each given ASCII code"
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ASCIITOCHAR() an carachtar ar ais do gach cód ASCII tugtha"

#: functions/conversion.xml:110
#, kde-format
msgid "ASCIITOCHAR(value)"
msgstr "ASCIITOCHAR(luach)"

#: functions/conversion.xml:111
#, kde-format
msgid "ASCIITOCHAR(118) returns \"v\""
msgstr "Filleann ASCIITOCHAR(118) é seo: \"v\""

#: functions/conversion.xml:112
#, kde-format
msgid "ASCIITOCHAR(75; 68; 69) returns \"KDE\""
msgstr "Filleann ASCIITOCHAR(75; 68; 69) é seo: \"KDE\""

#: functions/conversion.xml:120 functions/conversion.xml:142
#, kde-format
msgid "Value in X"
msgstr "Luach X"

#: functions/conversion.xml:124 functions/conversion.xml:146
#, kde-format
msgid "Value in Y"
msgstr "Luach Y"

#: functions/conversion.xml:128
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The POLR() function returns the radius corresponding to the position of a "
"point in a cartesian landmark."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm POLR() an ga ar ais a fhreagraíonn do shuíomh pointe i "
"sainchomhartha Cairtéiseach."

#: functions/conversion.xml:129
#, kde-format
msgid "POLR(X;Y)"
msgstr "POLR(X;Y)"

#: functions/conversion.xml:130
#, kde-format
msgid "POLR(12;12) returns 16.9705"
msgstr "Filleann POLR(12;12) é seo: 16.9705"

#: functions/conversion.xml:131
#, kde-format
msgid "POLR(12;0) returns 12"
msgstr "Filleann POLR(12;0) é seo: 12"

#: functions/conversion.xml:150
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The POLA() function returns the angle (in radians) corresponding to the "
"position of a point in a cartesian landmark."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm POLA() an uillinn (i raidiain) ar ais a fhreagraíonn do "
"shuíomh pointe i sainchomhartha Cairtéiseach."

#: functions/conversion.xml:151
#, kde-format
msgid "POLA(X;Y)"
msgstr "POLA(X;Y)"

#: functions/conversion.xml:152
#, kde-format
msgid "POLA(12;12) returns 0.78539816"
msgstr "Filleann POLA(12;12) é seo: 0.78539816"

#: functions/conversion.xml:153
#, kde-format
msgid "POLA(12;0) returns 0"
msgstr "Filleann POLA(12;0) é seo: 0"

#: functions/conversion.xml:154
#, kde-format
msgid "POLA(0;12) returns 1.5707"
msgstr "Filleann POLA(0;12) é seo: 1.5707"

#: functions/conversion.xml:165 functions/conversion.xml:225
#, kde-format
msgid "Radius"
msgstr "Ga"

#: functions/conversion.xml:169 functions/conversion.xml:229
