#: functions/datetime.xml:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The WEEKDAY() function returns the weekday of given date. If the method is 1 "
"(default) WEEKDAY() returns 1 for sunday, 2 for monday,.. If the method is "
"2, monday is 1, tuesday 2, ... and if the method is 3 WEEKDAY() returns 0 "
"for monday, 1 for tuesday,..."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm WEEKDAY() lá na seachtaine den dáta tugtha ar ais. Más é 1 "
"an modh (réamhshocrú), tugann WEEKDAY() 1 ar ais don Domhnach, 2 don "
"Luan,... Más é 2 an modh, is é 1 an Luan, 2 an Máirt, ... agus más é 3 an "
"modh, tugann WEEKDAY() 0 ar ais don Luan, 1 don Mháirt,..."

