#: functions/datetime.xml:42
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The DAYS360() function returns the number of days from date1 to date2 using "
"a 360-day calendar in which all months are assumed to have 30 days. If "
"method is false (default) the US method will be used, the European otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm DAYS360() líon na laethanta ó date1 go date2 ar ais ag "
"baint úsáide as féilire 360 lá ina nglactar leis go bhfuil 30 lá i ngach mí. "
"Má tá an modh bréagach (réamhshocrú), úsáidfear modh SAM, agus an modh "
"Eorpach mura bhfuil."

#: functions/datetime.xml:43
#, kde-format
msgid "DAYS360(date1; date2; method)"
msgstr "DAYS360(dáta1; dáta2; modh)"

