msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm CURRENTTIME() an t-am reatha ar ais, formáidithe le "
"paraiméadair áitiúla."

#: functions/datetime.xml:565
#, kde-format
msgid "CURRENTTIME()"
msgstr "CURRENTTIME()"

#: functions/datetime.xml:566
#, kde-format
msgid "CURRENTTIME() returns \"19:12:01\""
msgstr "Filleann CURRENTTIME() é seo: \"19:12:01\""

#: functions/datetime.xml:578
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The EASTERSUNDAY() function returns the date which corresponds to Easter "
"Sunday in the year given as the parameter."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm EASTERSUNDAY() an dáta ar ais a fhreagraíonn do Dhomhnach "
"Cásca sa bhliain a thugtar mar pharaiméadar."

#: functions/datetime.xml:579
#, kde-format
msgid "EASTERSUNDAY(year)"
msgstr "EASTERSUNDAY(bliain)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:580
#, kde-format
msgid "EASTERSUNDAY(2003) returns \"20th April 2003\""
msgstr "Filleann EASTERSUNDAY(2003) é seo: \"20th April 2003\""

#: functions/datetime.xml:592
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ISOWEEKNUM() function returns number of the week which the date falls "
"into. Note that this function is compliant with the ISO8601 standard: a week "
"always begins on a Monday, and ends on a Sunday. The first week of a year is "
"that week which contains the first Thursday of the year."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ISOWEEKNUM() uimhir na seachtaine ar ais ina dtiteann an "
"dáta. Tabhair faoi deara go gcomhlíonann an fheidhm seo an caighdeán "
"ISO8601: tosaíonn seachtain i gcónaí ar an Luan, agus críochnaíonn sí ar an "
"Domhnach. Is í an chéad seachtain den bhliain an tseachtain ina bhfuil an "
"chéad Déardaoin den bhliain."

#: functions/datetime.xml:593
#, kde-format
msgid "ISOWEEKNUM(date)"
msgstr "ISOWEEKNUM(dáta)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:594
#, kde-format
msgid "ISOWEEKNUM(A1) returns 51 when A1 is \"21st of Dec\"."
msgstr "Filleann ISOWEEKNUM(A1) é seo: 51 when A1 is \"21st of Dec\"."

#: functions/datetime.xml:611
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The WEEKNUM() function returns the non-ISO week number in which the date "
"falls into."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm WEEKNUM() an uimhir seachtaine nach bhfuil san ISO ina "
"bhfuil an dáta ar ais."

#: functions/datetime.xml:612
#, kde-format
msgid "WEEKNUM(date; method)"
msgstr "WEEKNUM(dáta; modh)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:613
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"WEEKNUM(A1; 1) returns 11 when A1 is \"9th of March 2008\". Number of the "
"week in the year, with a week beginning on Sunday (1, this is the default if "
"Method is omitted.)"
msgstr ""
"Tugann WEEKNUM(A1; 1) 11 ar ais nuair a bhíonn A1 cothrom le \"9 Márta "
"2008\". Uimhir na seachtaine sa bhliain, le seachtain ag tosú ar an Domhnach "
"(1, is é seo an réamhshocrú mura bhfuil an Modh san áireamh.)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:614
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"WEEKNUM(A1; 2) returns 10 when A1 is \"9th of March 2008\". Number of the "
"week in the year, with a week beginning on Monday (2)"
msgstr ""
"Tugann WEEKNUM(A1; 2) 10 ar ais nuair a bhíonn A1 mar \"9 Márta 2008\". "
"Uimhir na seachtaine sa bhliain, le seachtain ag tosú Dé Luain (2)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:623 functions/datetime.xml:647
#, kde-format
msgid "First date"
msgstr "An chéad dáta"

#: functions/datetime.xml:627 functions/datetime.xml:651
