msgid "Second date"
msgstr "An dara dáta"

#: functions/datetime.xml:631 functions/datetime.xml:655
#, kde-format
msgid "interval"
msgstr "eatramh"

#: functions/datetime.xml:635
#, kde-format
msgid "The DATEDIF() function returns the difference between two dates."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm DATEDIF() an difríocht idir dhá dháta ar ais."

#: functions/datetime.xml:636
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Interval must be one of the following: \"m\": month; \"d\": days; \"y\": "
"complete years; \"ym\": month excluding years; \"yd\": days excluding years; "
"\"md\": days excluding months and years"
msgstr ""
"Ní mór don eatramh a bheith ar cheann de na nithe seo a leanas: \"m\": mí; "
"\"d\": laethanta; \"y\": blianta iomlána; \"ym\": mí gan blianta a áireamh; "
"\"yd\": laethanta gan blianta a áireamh; \"md\": laethanta gan míonna agus "
"blianta a áireamh"

#: functions/datetime.xml:637
#, kde-format
msgid "DATEDIF(first date; second date; interval)"
msgstr "DATEDIF(céad dáta; dara dáta; eatramh)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:638
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"DATEDIF(A1;A2;\"d\") A1 is \"1st of January 1995\" and A2 is \"15th of June "
"1999\" returns number of days 1626"
msgstr ""
"DATEDIF(A1;A2;\"d\") Is é A1 \"1 Eanáir 1995\" agus is é A2 \"15 Meitheamh "
"1999\" agus tugann sé sin líon na laethanta ar ais 1626"

#: functions/datetime.xml:639
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"DATEDIF(A1;A2;\"m\") A1 is \"1st of January 1995\" and A2 is \"15th of June "
"1999\" returns number of months 53"
msgstr ""
"DATEDIF(A1;A2;\"m\") Is é A1 \"1 Eanáir 1995\" agus is é A2 \"15 Meitheamh "
"1999\" agus tugann sé sin líon na míonna 53 ar ais"

#: functions/datetime.xml:659
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The YEARFRAC() function returns the number of full days between start date "
"and end date according to the basis."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm YEARFRAC() líon na laethanta iomlána idir an dáta tosaigh "
"agus an dáta deiridh ar ais de réir an bhoinn."

#: functions/datetime.xml:660
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Basis must be one of the following: 0 = 30/360 US, 1 = Actual/actual, 2 = "
"Actual/360, 3 = Actual/365, 4 = European 30/360"
msgstr ""
"Ní mór don bhunús a bheith ar cheann de na nithe seo a leanas: 0 = 30/360 "
"SAM, 1 = Iarbhír/iarbhír, 2 = Iarbhír/360, 3 = Iarbhír/365, 4 = Eorpach "
"30/360"

#: functions/datetime.xml:661
#, kde-format
msgid "YEARFRAC(start date; end date; basis)"
msgstr "BLIAINFRAC(dáta tosaigh; dáta deiridh; bunús)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:669 functions/datetime.xml:692
#, kde-format
msgid "Start date"
msgstr "Dáta tosaigh"

#: functions/datetime.xml:673
#, kde-format
msgid "Working days"
msgstr "Laethanta oibre"

#: functions/datetime.xml:677 functions/datetime.xml:700
#, kde-format
msgid "Holidays"
msgstr "Laethanta saoire"

#: functions/datetime.xml:681
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The WORKDAY() function returns the date which is working days from the start "
"date."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm WORKDAY() an dáta ar ais, is é sin laethanta oibre ón dáta "
"tosaigh."

#: functions/datetime.xml:682 functions/datetime.xml:705
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Holidays must be one of the following: number = days to add, a single date "
"or an array of dates."
msgstr ""
"Ní mór laethanta saoire a bheith ar cheann de na nithe seo a leanas: uimhir "
"= laethanta le cur leis, dáta aonair nó eagar dátaí."

#: functions/datetime.xml:683
#, kde-format
msgid "WORKDAY(start date; days; holidays)"
msgstr "LÁ OIBRE(dáta tosaithe; laethanta; laethanta saoire)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:684
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"if B9 is \"01/01/2001\", D3 is \"01/03/2001\", D4 is \"01/04/2001\" then "
"WORKDAY(B9;2;D3:D4) returns \"Fri Jan 5 2001\""
msgstr ""
"Más é B9 \"01/01/2001\", más é D3 \"01/03/2001\", más é D4 \"01/04/2001\", "
"ansin tugann WORKDAY(B9;2;D3:D4) \"Aoine 5 Eanáir 2001\" ar ais"

#: functions/datetime.xml:696
#, kde-format
msgid "End date"
msgstr "Dáta deiridh"

#: functions/datetime.xml:704
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The NETWORKDAY() function returns the number of working days between "
"startdate and enddate."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm NETWORKDAY() líon na laethanta oibre idir an dáta tosaigh "
"agus an dáta deiridh ar ais."

#: functions/datetime.xml:706
#, kde-format
msgid "NETWORKDAY(start date; end date; holidays)"
msgstr "LÁOIBRE NETWORK(dáta tosaithe; dáta deiridh; laethanta saoire)"

#: functions/datetime.xml:707
#, kde-format
msgid "NETWORKDAY(\"01/01/2001\";\"01/08/2001\") returns 5 workdays"
msgstr ""
"Tugann LÁ OBAIR NETWORKDAY(\"01/01/2001\";\"01/08/2001\") 5 lá oibre ar ais"

#: functions/datetime.xml:708
#, kde-format
msgid "NETWORKDAY(\"01/01/2001\";\"01/08/2001\";2) returns 3 workdays"
msgstr ""
"Tugann LÁ OBAIR NETWORKDAY(\"01/01/2001\";\"01/08/2001\";2) 3 lá oibre ar ais"

#: functions/datetime.xml:720
