msgstr "Bunús comhaireamh laethanta"

#: functions/financial.xml:39
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ACCRINT function returns accrued interest for a security which pays "
"periodic interest. Allowed frequencies are 1 - annual, 2 - semi-annual or 4 "
"- quarterly. Basis is the type of day counting you want to use: 0: US 30/360 "
"(default), 1: real days, 2: real days/360, 3: real days/365 or 4: European "
"30/360."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ACCRINT ús carntha ar ais le haghaidh urrúis a íocann ús "
"tréimhsiúil. Is iad na minicíochtaí ceadaithe ná 1 - bliantúil, 2 - "
"leathbhliantúil nó 4 - ráithiúil. Is é Basis an cineál comhairimh laethanta "
"is mian leat a úsáid: 0: SAM 30/360 (réamhshocraithe), 1: laethanta fíor, 2: "
"laethanta fíor/360, 3: laethanta fíor/365 nó 4: Eorpach 30/360."

#: functions/financial.xml:40
#, kde-format
msgid "ACCRINT(issue; first interest; settlement; rate; par; frequency; basis)"
msgstr "ACCRINT(eisiúint; céad ús; socraíocht; ráta; par; minicíocht; bonn)"

#: functions/financial.xml:41
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"ACCRINT(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; \"5/1/2001\"; 0.1; 1000; 2; 0) returns "
"16,944"
msgstr ""
"Filleann ACCRINT(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; \"5/1/2001\"; 0.1; 1000; 2; "
"0) é seo: 16,944"

#: functions/financial.xml:70
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ACCRINTM function returns accrued interest for a security which pays "
"interests at maturity date. Basis is the type of day counting you want to "
"use: 0: US 30/360 (default), 1: real days, 2: real days/360, 3: real "
"days/365 or 4: European 30/360."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ACCRINTM ús carntha ar ais le haghaidh urrúis a íocann ús "
"ar dháta aibíochta. Is é Basis an cineál comhairimh laethanta is mian leat a "
"úsáid: 0: SAM 30/360 (réamhshocraithe), 1: laethanta fíor, 2: laethanta "
"fíor/360, 3: laethanta fíor/365 nó 4: Eorpach 30/360."

#: functions/financial.xml:71
#, kde-format
msgid "ACCRINTM(issue; settlement; rate; par; basis)"
msgstr "ACCRINTM(eisiúint; socraíocht; ráta; par; bonn)"

#: functions/financial.xml:72
#, kde-format
msgid "ACCRINTM(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 0.1; 100) returns 5.0278"
msgstr ""
"Filleann ACCRINTM(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 0.1; 100) é seo: 5.0278"

