#: functions/financial.xml:149
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The COMPOUND() function returns the value of an investment, given the "
"principal, nominal interest rate, compounding frequency and time. For "
"example: $5000 at 12% interest compounded quarterly for 5 years will become "
"COMPOUND(5000;0.12;4;5) or $9030.56."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm COMPOUND() luach infheistíochta ar ais, agus an "
"phríomhshuim, an ráta úis ainmniúil, minicíocht agus am an chomhshuimithe "
"san áireamh. Mar shampla: athróidh $5000 ag ús 12% comhshuite go ráithiúil "
"ar feadh 5 bliana go COMPOUND(5000;0.12;4;5) nó $9030.56."

#: functions/financial.xml:150
#, kde-format
msgid "COMPOUND(initial;interest;periods;periods_per_year)"
msgstr "COMHDHÍOLL(tosaigh;ús;tréimhsí;tréimhsí_in_aghaidh_na_bliana)"

#: functions/financial.xml:151
#, kde-format
msgid "COMPOUND(5000;0.12;4;5) equals 9030.56"
msgstr "Is ionann COMHDHÚIL(5000;0.12;4;5) agus 9030.56"

#: functions/financial.xml:171
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CONTINUOUS() function calculates the return on continuously compounded "
"interest, given the principal, nominal rate and time in years. For example: "
"$1000 earning 10% for 1 year becomes CONTINUOUS(1000;.1;1) or $1105.17."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm CONTINUOUS() an toradh ar ús comhchodach leanúnach, ag "
"cur an phríomhshuim, an ráta ainmniúil agus an t-am i mblianta san áireamh. "
"Mar shampla: bíonn $1000 ag tuilleamh 10% ar feadh 1 bhliain ina "
"CONTINUOUS(1000;.1;1) nó $1105.17."

#: functions/financial.xml:172
#, kde-format
msgid "CONTINUOUS(principal;interest;years)"
msgstr "LEANÚNACH(príomhshuim;ús;blianta)"

#: functions/financial.xml:173
#, kde-format
msgid "CONTINUOUS(1000;0.1;1) equals 1105.17"
msgstr "Is ionann CONTINUOUS(1000;0.1;1) agus 1105.17"

