#: functions/financial.xml:388
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The DOLLARDE() function returns a dollar price expressed as a decimal "
"number. The fractional dollar is the number to be converted and the fraction "
"is the denominator of the fraction"
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm DOLLARDE() praghas dollar ar ais mar uimhir dheachúil. Is "
"é an dollar codánach an uimhir atá le tiontú agus is é an codán ainmneoir an "
"chodáin"

