#: functions/financial.xml:1136
#, kde-format
msgid "Periods"
msgstr "Tréimsí"

#: functions/financial.xml:487
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The EFFECT() function calculates the effective yield for a nominal interest "
"rate (annual rate or APR). For example: 8% interest compounded monthly "
"provides an effective yield of EFFECT(.08;12) or 8.3%."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm EFFECT() an toradh éifeachtach le haghaidh ráta úis "
"ainmniúil (ráta bliantúil nó APR). Mar shampla: soláthraíonn ús 8% atá "
"comhdhéanta go míosúil toradh éifeachtach EFFECT(.08;12) nó 8.3%."

#: functions/financial.xml:488
#, kde-format
msgid "EFFECT(nominal;periods)"
msgstr "EFFECT(luach ainmniúil;tréimhsí)"

#: functions/financial.xml:489
#, kde-format
msgid "EFFECT(0.08;12) equals 0.083"
msgstr "Is ionann EFFECT(0.08;12) agus 0.083"

#: functions/financial.xml:507
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The EFFECTIVE() function calculates the effective yield for a nominal "
"interest rate (annual rate or APR). It is the same as the EFFECT function."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm EFFECTIVE() an toradh éifeachtach le haghaidh ráta úis "
"ainmniúil (ráta bliantúil nó APR). Tá sé mar an gcéanna leis an fheidhm "
"EFFECT."

#: functions/financial.xml:508
#, kde-format
msgid "EFFECTIVE(nominal;periods)"
msgstr "EFFECTIVE(luach ainmniúil;tréimhsí)"

#: functions/financial.xml:517
#, kde-format
msgid "Currency"
msgstr "Airgeadra"

#: functions/financial.xml:521
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The EURO() function converts one Euro to a given national currency in the "
"European monetary union. Currency is one of the following: ATS (Austria), "
"BEF (Belgium), CYP (Cyprus), DEM (Germany), EEK (Estonia), ESP (Spain), EUR "
"(Euro), FIM (Finland), FRF (France), GRD (Greece), IEP (Ireland), ITL "
"(Italy), LTL (Lithuania), LUF (Luxembourg), LVL (Latvia), MTL (Malta), NLG "
"(Netherlands), PTE (Portugal), SIT (Slovenia), or SKK (Slovakia)."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm EURO() euro amháin a thiontú go hairgeadra náisiúnta "
"áirithe san aontas airgeadaíochta Eorpach. Is é an t-airgeadra ceann amháin "
"díobh seo a leanas: ATS (an Ostair), BEF (an Bheilg), CYP (an Chipir), DEM "
"(an Ghearmáin), EEK (an Eastóin), ESP (an Spáinn), EUR (Euro), FIM (an "
"Fhionlainn), FRF (an Fhrainc), GRD (an Ghréig), IEP (Éire), ITL (an Iodáil), "
"LTL (an Liotuáin), LUF (Lucsamburg), LVL (an Laitvia), MTL (Málta), NLG (an "
"Ísiltír), PTE (an Phortaingéil), SIT (an tSlóivéin), nó SKK (an tSlóvaic)."

#: functions/financial.xml:522
#, kde-format
msgid "EURO(currency)"
msgstr "EURO(airgeadra)"

#: functions/financial.xml:523
#, kde-format
msgid "EURO(\"DEM\") equals 1.95583"
msgstr "Is ionann EURO (\"DEM\") agus 1.95583"

#: functions/financial.xml:536
#, kde-format
msgid "Source currency"
msgstr "Airgeadra foinseach"

#: functions/financial.xml:540
#, kde-format
msgid "Target currency"
msgstr "Airgeadra sprice"

#: functions/financial.xml:544
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The EUROCONVERT() function converts a number from one national currency to "
"another currency in the European monetary union by using EURO an "
"intermediary. Currency is one of the following: ATS (Austria), BEF "
"(Belgium), DEM (Germany), ESP (Spain), EUR (Euro), FIM (Finland), FRF "
"(France), GRD (Greece), IEP (Ireland), ITL (Italy), LUF (Luxembourg), NLG "
"(Netherlands), or PTE (Portugal)."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm EUROCONVERT() uimhir a thiontú ó airgeadra náisiúnta "
"amháin go hairgeadra eile san aontas airgeadaíochta Eorpach trí úsáid a "
"bhaint as EURO mar idirghabhálaí. Is é an t-airgeadra ceann amháin díobh seo "
"a leanas: ATS (An Ostair), BEF (An Bheilg), DEM (An Ghearmáin), ESP (An "
"Spáinn), EUR (Euro), FIM (An Fhionlainn), FRF (An Fhrainc), GRD (An Ghréig), "
"IEP (Éire), ITL (An Iodáil), LUF (Lucsamburg), NLG (An Ísiltír), nó PTE (An "
"Phortaingéil)."

#: functions/financial.xml:545
#, kde-format
msgid "EUROCONVERT(number; source currency; target currency)"
msgstr "EUROCONVERT(uimhir; airgeadra foinse; airgeadra sprice)"

#: functions/financial.xml:546
#, kde-format
msgid "EUROCONVERT(1; \"EUR\"; \"DEM\") equals 1.95583"
msgstr "Is ionann EUROCONVERT(1; \"EUR\"; \"DEM\") agus 1.95583"

#: functions/financial.xml:555 functions/financial.xml:1033
#: functions/financial.xml:1158
#, kde-format
msgid "Present value"
msgstr "Luach láithreach"

#: functions/financial.xml:567
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FV() function returns the future value of an investment, given the yield "
"and the time elapsed. If you have $1000 in a bank account earning 8% "
"interest, after two years you will have FV(1000;0.08;2) or $1166.40."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm FV() luach todhchaí infheistíochta ar ais, ag cur an "
"toradh agus an t-am atá caite san áireamh. Má tá $1000 i gcuntas bainc a "
"thuilleann ús 8%, tar éis dhá bhliain beidh FV(1000;0.08;2) nó $1166.40 agat."

#: functions/financial.xml:568
#, kde-format
msgid "FV(present value;yield;periods)"
msgstr "FV(luach láithreach;toradh;tréimhsí)"

#: functions/financial.xml:569
#, kde-format
msgid "FV(1000;0.08;2) equals 1166.40"
msgstr "Is ionann FV(1000;0.08;2) agus 1166.40"

#: functions/financial.xml:581 functions/financial.xml:1128
#, kde-format
msgid "Payment per period"
msgstr "Íoc sa tréimhse"

#: functions/financial.xml:593
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FV_ANNUITY() function returns the future value of a stream of payments "
"given the amount of the payment, the interest rate and the number of "
"periods. For example: If you receive $500 per year for 20 years, and invest "
"it at 8%, the total after 20 years will be FV_annuity(500;0.08;20) or "
"$22,880.98. This function assumes that payments are made at the end of each "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm FV_ANNUITY() luach todhchaí sruth íocaíochtaí ar ais nuair "
"a thugtar méid na híocaíochta, an ráta úis agus líon na dtréimhsí. Mar "
"shampla: Má fhaigheann tú $500 in aghaidh na bliana ar feadh 20 bliain, agus "
"má infheistíonn tú é ag 8%, beidh an t-iomlán tar éis 20 bliain "
"FV_annuity(500;0.08;20) nó $22,880.98. Glacann an fheidhm seo leis go "
"ndéantar íocaíochtaí ag deireadh gach tréimhse."

#: functions/financial.xml:594
#, kde-format
msgid "FV_ANNUITY(amount;interest;periods)"
msgstr "FV_ANNUITY(méid;ús;tréimhsí)"

#: functions/financial.xml:595
#, kde-format
msgid "FV_ANNUITY(1000;0.05;5) equals 5525.63"
msgstr "Is ionann FV_ANNUITY(1000;0.05;5) agus 5525.63"

#: functions/financial.xml:612 functions/financial.xml:800
#: functions/financial.xml:1192
#, kde-format
msgid "Investment"
msgstr "Infheistíocht"

#: functions/financial.xml:624
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The INTRATE function returns the interest rate for a fully invested "
"security. Basis is the type of day counting you want to use: 0: US 30/360 "
"(default), 1: real days, 2: real days/360, 3: real days/365 or 4: European "
"30/360."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm INTRATE an ráta úis ar ais le haghaidh urrús atá "
"infheistithe go hiomlán. Is é Basis an cineál comhairimh laethanta is mian "
"leat a úsáid: 0: SAM 30/360 (réamhshocraithe), 1: laethanta fíor, 2: "
"laethanta fíor/360, 3: laethanta fíor/365 nó 4: Eorpach 30/360."

#: functions/financial.xml:625
#, kde-format
msgid "INTRATE(settlement; maturity; investment; redemption; basis)"
msgstr "INTRATE(socraíocht; aibíocht; infheistíocht; fuascailt; bonn)"

#: functions/financial.xml:626
#, kde-format
msgid "INTRATE(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 1000000; 2000000; 1) returns 1.98"
msgstr ""
"Filleann INTRATE(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 1000000; 2000000; 1) é seo: "
"1.98"

#: functions/financial.xml:642 functions/financial.xml:704
#: functions/financial.xml:1029
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of periods"
msgstr "Líon na dtréimhsí"

#: functions/financial.xml:646
#, kde-format
msgid "Present values"
msgstr "Luachanna láithreacha"

#: functions/financial.xml:650 functions/financial.xml:1037
#, kde-format
msgid "Future value (optional)"
msgstr "Luach cumaisc (roghnach)"

#: functions/financial.xml:654 functions/financial.xml:854
#: functions/financial.xml:1003 functions/financial.xml:1041
#, kde-format
msgid "Type (optional)"
msgstr "Cineál (roghnach)"

#: functions/financial.xml:658
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"IPMT calculates the amount of a payment of an annuity going towards interest."
msgstr "Ríomhann IPMT méid íocaíochta bliantúlachta a théann i dtreo úis."

#: functions/financial.xml:659 functions/financial.xml:713
#: functions/financial.xml:1046
#, kde-format
msgid "Rate is the periodic interest rate."
msgstr "Is é an ráta an ráta úis tréimhsiúil."

#: functions/financial.xml:660 functions/financial.xml:1047
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Period is the amortizement period. 1 for the first and NPER for the last "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Is í an tréimhse an tréimhse amúchta. 1 don chéad cheann agus NPER don "
"tréimhse dheireanach."

#: functions/financial.xml:661 functions/financial.xml:1048
#, kde-format
msgid "NPER is the total number of periods during which annuity is paid."
msgstr "Is é NPER líon iomlán na dtréimhsí ina n-íoctar bliantúlacht."

#: functions/financial.xml:662 functions/financial.xml:716
#: functions/financial.xml:1049
#, kde-format
msgid "PV is the present value in the sequence of payments."
msgstr "Is é PV an luach láithreach i seicheamh na n-íocaíochtaí."

#: functions/financial.xml:663 functions/financial.xml:1050
#, kde-format
msgid "FV (optional) is the desired (future) value.  default: 0."
msgstr ""
"Is é FV (roghnach) an luach atá ag teastáil (sa todhchaí). réamhshocraithe: "
"0."

#: functions/financial.xml:664 functions/financial.xml:1051
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Type (optional) defines the due date. 1 for payment at the beginning of a "
"period and 0 (default) for payment at the end of a period."
msgstr ""
"Sainmhíníonn cineál (roghnach) an dáta dlite. 1 le haghaidh íocaíochta ag "
"tús tréimhse agus 0 (réamhshocraithe) le haghaidh íocaíochta ag deireadh "
"tréimhse."

#: functions/financial.xml:665
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The example shows the interest to pay in the last year of a three year loan. "
"The interest rate is 10 percent."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an sampla an t-ús atá le híoc sa bhliain dheireanach d’iasacht "
"trí bliana. Is é 10 faoin gcéad an ráta úis."

#: functions/financial.xml:666
#, kde-format
msgid "IPMT(Rate; Period; NPer; PV; FV; Type)"
msgstr "IPMT(Ráta; Tréimhse; NPer; PV; FV; Cineál)"

#: functions/financial.xml:667
#, kde-format
msgid "IPMT(0.1;3;3;8000) equals -292.45"
msgstr "Is ionann IPMT(0.1;3;3;8000) agus -292.45"

#: functions/financial.xml:678 functions/financial.xml:796
#: functions/financial.xml:1395 functions/financial.xml:1422
#: functions/math.xml:15 functions/math.xml:292 functions/math.xml:310
