#: functions/math.xml:639
#, kde-format
msgid "Values"
msgstr "Luachanna"

#: functions/financial.xml:682 functions/financial.xml:1170
#: functions/financial.xml:1403
#, kde-format
msgid "Guess"
msgstr "Buille Faoi Thuairim"

#: functions/financial.xml:686
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The IRR function calculates the internal rate of return for a series of cash "
"flows."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm IRR an ráta inmheánach tuairisceáin do shraith sreafaí "
"airgid."

#: functions/financial.xml:687
#, kde-format
msgid "IRR( Values[; Guess = 0.1 ] )"
msgstr "IRR(Luachanna[; Buille faoi thuairim = 0.1])"

#: functions/financial.xml:708
#, kde-format
msgid "Present values (PV)"
msgstr "Luachanna láithreacha (LL)"

#: functions/financial.xml:712
#, kde-format
msgid "Calculates the interest paid on a given period of an investment."
msgstr "Ríomhann sé an t-ús a íoctar ar thréimhse áirithe infheistíochta."

#: functions/financial.xml:714
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Period is the amortizement period. 1 for the first and NPer for the last "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Is í an tréimhse an tréimhse amúchta. 1 don chéad cheann agus NPer don "
"tréimhse dheireanach."

#: functions/financial.xml:715
#, kde-format
msgid "NPer is the total number of periods during which annuity is paid."
msgstr "Is é NPer líon iomlán na dtréimhsí ina n-íoctar bliantúlacht."

#: functions/financial.xml:717
#, kde-format
msgid "ISPMT(Rate; Period; NPer; PV)"
msgstr "ISPMT(Ráta; Tréimhse; NPer; PV)"

#: functions/financial.xml:718
#, kde-format
msgid "ISPMT(0.1; 1; 3; 8000000) equals -533333"
msgstr "Is ionann ISPMT(0.1; 1; 3; 8000000) agus -533333"

#: functions/financial.xml:731 functions/financial.xml:1508
#, kde-format
msgid "Face value"
msgstr "Aghaidhluach"

#: functions/financial.xml:735
#, kde-format
msgid "Coupon rate"
msgstr "Ráta cúpóin"

#: functions/financial.xml:739
#, kde-format
msgid "Coupons per year"
msgstr "Cúpóin sa bhliain"

#: functions/financial.xml:747
#, kde-format
msgid "Market interest rate"
msgstr "Ráta úis an mhargaidh"

#: functions/financial.xml:751
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The LEVEL_COUPON() function calculates the value of a level-coupon bond. For "
"example: if the interest rate is 10%, a $1000 bond with semi-annual coupons "
"at a rate of 13% that matures in 4 years is worth "
"LEVEL_COUPON(1000;.13;2;4;.1) or $1096.95."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm LEVEL_COUPON() luach banna cúpóin leibhéalta. Mar "
"shampla: más é 10% an ráta úis, is fiú LEVEL_COUPON(1000;.13;2;4;.1) nó "
"$1096.95 banna $1000 le cúpóin leathbhliantúla ag ráta 13% a aibíonn i "
"gceann 4 bliana."

#: functions/financial.xml:752
#, kde-format
msgid "LEVEL_COUPON(face value;coupon rate;coupons per year;years;market rate)"
msgstr ""
"LEIBHÉAL_CÚPÓN(luach aghaidhe;ráta cúpóin;cúpóin in aghaidh na bliana;"
"blianta;ráta margaidh)"

#: functions/financial.xml:753
#, kde-format
msgid "LEVEL_COUPON(1000;.13;2;4;.1) equals 1096.95"
msgstr "Is ionann LEIBHÉAL_CÚPÓN(1000;.13;2;4;.1) agus 1096.95"

#: functions/financial.xml:785
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MDURATION() function will calculate the modified Macauley duration of a "
"fixed interest security in years."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhfaidh an fheidhm MDURATION() fad modhnaithe Macaulay d'urrús úis "
"sheasta i mblianta."

#: functions/financial.xml:786
#, kde-format
msgid "MDURATION( Settlement; Maturity; Coupon; Yield; Frequency; [ Basis=0 ])"
msgstr "FAD( Socrú; Aibíocht; Cúpón; Toradh; Minicíocht; [ Bunús = 0 ])"

#: functions/financial.xml:787
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"MDURATION(\"2004-02-01\"; \"2004-05-31\"; 0.08; 0.09; 2; 0) returns "
"0.316321106"
msgstr ""
"Filleann MDURATION(\"2004-02-01\"; \"2004-05-31\"; 0.08; 0.09; 2; 0) é seo: "
"0.316321106"

#: functions/financial.xml:804
#, kde-format
msgid "Reinvestment"
msgstr "Athinfheistíocht"

#: functions/financial.xml:808
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MIRR() function will calculate the modified internal rate of return "
"(IRR) of a series of periodic investments."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhfaidh an fheidhm MIRR() an ráta inmheánach tuairisceáin mhodhnaithe "
"(IRR) de shraith infheistíochtaí tréimhsiúla."

#: functions/financial.xml:809
#, kde-format
msgid "MIRR(values; investment; reinvestment)"
msgstr "MIRR(luachanna; infheistíocht; athinfheistíocht)"

#: functions/financial.xml:810
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid "MIRR({100;200;-50;300;-200}, 5%, 6%) equals 34.2823387842%"
msgstr "Is ionann MIRR({100;200;-50;300;-200}, 5%, 6%) agus 34.2823387842%"

#: functions/financial.xml:819
#, kde-format
msgid "Effective interest rate"
msgstr "Fíor-ráta úis"

#: functions/financial.xml:827
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The NOMINAL() function calculates the nominal (stated) interest rate for an "
"effective (annualized) interest rate compounded at given intervals. For "
"example: to earn 8% on an account compounded monthly, you need a return of "
"NOMINAL(.08;12) or 7.72%."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm NOMINAL() an ráta úis ainmniúil (sonraithe) le haghaidh "
"ráta úis éifeachtach (bliantúil) atá comhdhéanta ag eatraimh áirithe. Mar "
"shampla: chun 8% a thuilleamh ar chuntas atá comhdhéanta go míosúil, "
"teastaíonn toradh NOMINAL(.08;12) nó 7.72% uait."

#: functions/financial.xml:828
#, kde-format
msgid "NOMINAL(effective;periods)"
msgstr "AINMNÍOCH(tréimhsí éifeachtacha)"

#: functions/financial.xml:829
#, kde-format
