msgstr "Is ionann NPER(0.1; -100; 1000) agus 11"

#: functions/financial.xml:861
#, kde-format
msgid "NPER(0.06; 0; -10000; 20000 ;0) returns 11.906"
msgstr "Filleann NPER(0.06; 0; -10000; 20000 ;0) é seo: 11.906"

#: functions/financial.xml:877
#, kde-format
msgid "Values (array)"
msgstr "Luachanna (eagar)"

#: functions/financial.xml:881
#, kde-format
msgid "The net present value (NPV) for a series of periodic cash flows."
msgstr "An glanluach láithreach (NPV) do shraith sreafaí airgid tréimhsiúla."

#: functions/financial.xml:885
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Computes the net present value for a series of periodic cash flows with the\n"
"               discount rate Rate. Values should be positive if they are "
"received as income, and\n"
"                   negative if the amounts are expenditure."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann sé an glanluach láithreach do shraith sreafaí airgid tréimhsiúla\n"
"               leis an ráta lascaine. Ba chóir go mbeadh luachanna dearfach "
"má fhaightear iad mar ioncam, agus \n"
"                   diúltach má tá na méideanna ina gcaiteachas."

#: functions/financial.xml:886
#, kde-format
msgid "NPV(Rate; Values)"
msgstr "NPV(Ráta; Luachanna)"

#: functions/financial.xml:887
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid "NPV(100%;4;5;7) = 4.125"
msgstr "NPV(100%;4;5;7) = 4.125"

#: functions/financial.xml:908 functions/financial.xml:951
#, kde-format
msgid "Last"
msgstr "Deiridh"

#: functions/financial.xml:916
#, kde-format
msgid "AnnualYield"
msgstr "Toradh Bliantúil"

#: functions/financial.xml:932
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ODDLPRICE function calculates the value of the security per 100 currency "
"units of face value. The security has an irregular last interest date."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm ODDLPRICE luach an urrúis in aghaidh gach 100 aonad "
"airgeadra den luach aghaidhe. Tá dáta úis deireanach neamhrialta ag an urrús."

#: functions/financial.xml:933
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"ODDLPRICE( Settlement; Maturity; Last; Rate; AnnualYield; Redemption; "
"Frequency [; Basis = 0 ] )"
msgstr ""
"ODDLPRICE( Socrú; Aibíocht; Deireanach; Ráta; Toradh Bliantúil; Fuascailt; "
"Minicíocht [; Bunús = 0 ] )"

#: functions/financial.xml:934
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"ODDLPRICE(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1995;12;31);DATE(1990;1;1);3%;5%;100;2) "
"returns 90.991042345"
msgstr ""
"Tugann ODDLPRICE(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1995;12;31);DATE(1990;1;1);3%;5%;100;2) "
"90.991042345 ar ais"

#: functions/financial.xml:959 functions/financial.xml:1373
#: functions/financial.xml:1449 functions/financial.xml:1487
#, kde-format
msgid "Price"
msgstr "Praghas"

#: functions/financial.xml:975
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ODDLYIELD function calculates the yield of the security which has an "
"irregular last interest date."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm ODDLYIELD toradh an urrúis a bhfuil dáta úis deireanach "
"neamhrialta aige."

#: functions/financial.xml:976
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"ODDLYIELD( Settlement; Maturity; Last; Rate; Price; Redemption; Frequency [; "
"Basis = 0 ] )"
msgstr ""
"ODDLYIELD( Socrú; Aibíocht; Deireanach; Ráta; Praghas; Fuascailt; Minicíocht "
"[; Bunús = 0 ] )"

#: functions/financial.xml:977
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"ODDLYIELD(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1995;12;31);DATE(1990;1;1);3%;91;100;2) "
"returns 4.997775351"
msgstr ""
"Tugann ODDLYIELD(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1995;12;31);DATE(1990;1;1);3%;91;100;2) "
"4.997775351 ar ais"

#: functions/financial.xml:991
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of periods (NPer)"
msgstr "Líon na dtréimhsí (NPer)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1007
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"PMT returns the amount of payment for a loan based on a constant interest "
"rate and constant payments (each payment is equal amount)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann PMT méid na híocaíochta le haghaidh iasachta ar ais bunaithe ar ráta "
"úis tairiseach agus íocaíochtaí tairiseacha (is ionann gach íocaíocht agus "
"méid)."

#: functions/financial.xml:1008
#, kde-format
msgid "PMT(rate; nper ; pv [; fv = 0 [; type = 0 ]] )"
msgstr ""
"PMT(ráta; líon in aghaidh an ráta; luach in aghaidh an ráta [; luach in "
"aghaidh an ráta = 0 [; cineál = 0]])"

#: functions/financial.xml:1009
#, kde-format
msgid "PMT(0.1; 4; 10000) equals -3154.71"
msgstr "Is ionann PMT(0.1; 4; 10000) agus -3154.71"

#: functions/financial.xml:1045
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"PPMT calculates the amount of a payment of an annuity going towards "
"principal."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann PPMT méid íocaíochta bliantúlachta atá ag dul i dtreo príomhshuime."

#: functions/financial.xml:1052
#, kde-format
msgid "PPMT(Rate; Period; NPer; PV [; FV = 9 [; Type = 0 ]] )"
msgstr "PPMT(Ráta; Tréimhse; NPer; PV [; FV = 9 [; Cineál = 0]])"

#: functions/financial.xml:1053
#, kde-format
msgid "PPMT(0.0875;1;36;5000;8000;1) equals -18.48"
msgstr "Is ionann PPMT(0.0875;1;36;5000;8000;1) agus -18.48"

#: functions/financial.xml:1072 functions/financial.xml:1479
#, kde-format
msgid "Issue"
msgstr "Eisiúint"

#: functions/financial.xml:1076 functions/financial.xml:1196
#: functions/financial.xml:1301 functions/financial.xml:1325
#: functions/financial.xml:1483
#, kde-format
msgid "Discount rate"
msgstr "Ráta lascaine"

#: functions/financial.xml:1088
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"PRICEMAT Calculate the price per 100 currency units of face value of the "
"security that pays interest on the maturity date."
msgstr ""
"PRAGHAS MAT Ríomh an praghas in aghaidh 100 aonad airgeadra de luach "
"aghaidhe an urrúis a íocann ús ar an dáta aibíochta."

#: functions/financial.xml:1089
#, kde-format
msgid "Basis     Calculation method"
msgstr "Modh Ríomha Bunúsach"

#: functions/financial.xml:1090
#, kde-format
msgid "  0       US method, 12 months, each month with 30 days"
msgstr "  0 modh SAM, 12 mhí, gach mí le 30 lá"

#: functions/financial.xml:1091
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"  1       Actual number of days in year, actual number of days in months "
msgstr ""
"  1       Líon iarbhír laethanta sa bhliain, líon iarbhír laethanta i míonna "

#: functions/financial.xml:1092
#, kde-format
msgid "  2       360 days in a year, actual number of days in months"
msgstr "  2       360 lá sa bhliain, líon iarbhír na laethanta i míonna"

#: functions/financial.xml:1093
#, kde-format
msgid "  4       365 days in a year,  actual number of days in months"
msgstr "  4       365 lá sa bhliain,  líon iarbhír na laethanta i míonna"

#: functions/financial.xml:1094
#, kde-format
msgid "  5       European method, 12 months, each month has 30 days"
msgstr "  5       mhodh Eorpach, 12 mhí, tá 30 lá i ngach mí"

#: functions/financial.xml:1095
#, kde-format
msgid "PRICEMAT(settlement; maturity; issue; rate; yield [; basis = 0 ] )"
msgstr "PRICEMAT(socraíocht; aibíocht; eisiúint; ráta; toradh [; bonn = 0])"

#: functions/financial.xml:1096
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"PRICEMAT(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1995;12;31);DATE(1990;1;1);6%;5%) returns "
"103.819218241"
msgstr ""
"Tugann PRICEMAT(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1995;12;31);DATE(1990;1;1);6%;5%) "
"103.819218241 ar ais"

#: functions/financial.xml:1106 functions/financial.xml:1162
#, kde-format
msgid "Future value"
msgstr "Luach cumaisc"

#: functions/financial.xml:1118
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The PV() function returns the present value of an investment -- the value "
"today of a sum of money in the future, given the rate of interest or "
"inflation. For example if you need $1166.40 for your new computer and you "
"want to buy it in two years while earning 8% interest, you need to start "
"with PV(1166.4;0.08;2) or $1000."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm PV() luach reatha infheistíochta ar ais -- luach inniu "
"suim airgid sa todhchaí, ag cur an ráta úis nó an boilscithe san áireamh. "
"Mar shampla, má theastaíonn $1166.40 uait do ríomhaire nua agus más mian "
"leat é a cheannach i gceann dhá bhliain agus 8% úis á thuilleamh agat, ní "
"mór duit tosú le PV(1166.4;0.08;2) nó $1000."

#: functions/financial.xml:1119
#, kde-format
msgid "PV(future value;rate;periods)"
msgstr "PV(luach cumaisc;ráta;tréimhsí)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1120
#, kde-format
msgid "PV(1166.4;0.08;2) equals 1000"
msgstr "Is ionann PV(1166.4;0.08;2) agus 1000"

#: functions/financial.xml:1140
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The PV_ANNUITY() function returns the present value of an annuity or stream "
"of payments. For example: a \"million dollar\" lottery ticket that pays "
"$50,000 a year for 20 years, with an interest rate of 5%, is actually worth "
"PV_ANNUITY(50000;0.05;20) or $623,111. This function assumes that payments "
"are made at the end of each period."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm PV_ANNUITY() luach reatha blianachta nó srutha íocaíochtaí "
"ar ais. Mar shampla: is fiú PV_ANNUITY(50000;0.05;20) nó $623,111 ticéad "
"crannchuir \"milliún dollar\" a íocann $50,000 sa bhliain ar feadh 20 "
"bliain, le ráta úis 5%. Glacann an fheidhm seo leis go ndéantar íocaíochtaí "
"ag deireadh gach tréimhse."

#: functions/financial.xml:1141
#, kde-format
msgid "PV_ANNUITY(amount;interest;periods)"
msgstr "PV_ANNUITY(méid;ús;tréimhsí)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1142
#, kde-format
msgid "PV_ANNUITY(1000;0.05;5) equals 4329.48"
msgstr "Is ionann PV_ANNUITY(1000;0.05;5) agus 4329.48"

#: functions/financial.xml:1150
#, kde-format
msgid "Payment period"
msgstr "Tréimhse íocaíochta"

#: functions/financial.xml:1154
#, kde-format
msgid "Regular payments"
msgstr "Íocaíochtaí rialta"

#: functions/financial.xml:1166 functions/reference.xml:63
#, kde-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Cineál"

#: functions/financial.xml:1174
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The RATE() function computes the constant interest rate per period of an "
"investment."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm RATE() an ráta úis tairiseach in aghaidh na tréimhse "
"infheistíochta."

#: functions/financial.xml:1175
#, kde-format
msgid "RATE(nper;pmt;pv;fv;type;guess)"
msgstr ""
"RÁTA(uimhir in aghaidh an lae;uimhir íocaíochta;uimhir luacha;uimhir luacha;"
"cineál;buille faoi thuairim)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1176
#, kde-format
msgid "RATE(4*12;-200;8000) equals 0.007701472"
msgstr "Is ionann RATE(4*12;-200;8000) agus 0.007701472"

#: functions/financial.xml:1204
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The RECEIVED function returns the amount received at the maturity date for a "
"invested security. Basis is the type of day counting you want to use: 0: US "
"30/360 (default), 1: real days, 2: real days/360, 3: real days/365 or 4: "
"European 30/360. The settlement date must be before maturity date."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm RECEIVED an méid a fuarthas ar an dáta aibíochta le "
"haghaidh urrúis infheistithe ar ais. Is é Basis an cineál comhairimh "
"laethanta is mian leat a úsáid: 0: SAM 30/360 (réamhshocraithe), 1: "
"laethanta fíor, 2: laethanta fíor/360, 3: laethanta fíor/365 nó 4: Eorpach "
"30/360. Ní mór don dáta socraíochta a bheith roimh an dáta aibíochta."

#: functions/financial.xml:1205
#, kde-format
msgid "RECEIVED(settlement; maturity; investment; discount; basis)"
msgstr "FAIGHTE(socraíocht; aibíocht; infheistíocht; lascaine; bonn)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1206
#, kde-format
msgid "RECEIVED(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 1000; 0.05; 0) returns 1,025.787"
msgstr ""
"Filleann RECEIVED(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 1000; 0.05; 0) é seo: "
"1,025.787"

#: functions/financial.xml:1226
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The RRI function calculates the interest rate resulting from the profit "
"(return) of an investment."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm RRI an ráta úis a eascraíonn as brabús (toradh) "
"infheistíochta."

#: functions/financial.xml:1227
#, kde-format
msgid "RRI( P; Pv; Fv)"
msgstr "RRI( P; Ll; Lc)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1228
#, kde-format
msgid "RRI(1;100;200) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann RRI(1;100;200) é seo: 1"

#: functions/financial.xml:1253
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SLN() function will determine the straight line depreciation of an asset "
"for a single period. Cost is the amount you paid for the asset. Salvage is "
"the value of the asset at the end of the period. Life is the number of "
"periods over which the asset is depreciated. SLN divides the cost evenly "
"over the life of an asset."
msgstr ""
"Cinnfidh an fheidhm SLN() díluacháil dhíreach sócmhainne le haghaidh "
"tréimhse aonair. Is é an costas an méid a d'íoc tú as an tsócmhainn. Is é an "
"tarrtháil luach na sócmhainne ag deireadh na tréimhse. Is é an saolré líon "
"na dtréimhsí a ndéantar díluacháil ar an tsócmhainn. Roinneann SLN an costas "
"go cothrom thar shaolré na sócmhainne."

#: functions/financial.xml:1254
#, kde-format
msgid "SLN(cost; salvage value; life)"
msgstr "SLN(costas; luach tarrthála; saolré)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1255
#, kde-format
msgid "SLN(10000;700;10) equals 930"
msgstr "Is ionann SLN(10000;700;10) agus 930"

#: functions/financial.xml:1281
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SYD() function will calculate the sum-of-years digits depreciation for "
"an asset based on its cost, salvage value, anticipated life, and a "
"particular period. This method accelerates the rate of the depreciation, so "
"that more depreciation expense occurs in earlier periods than in later ones. "
"The depreciable cost is the actual cost minus the salvage value. The useful "
"life is the number of periods (typically years) over which the asset is "
"depreciated."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhfaidh an fheidhm SYD() an luachlaghdú suim-na-blianta digití do "
"shócmhainn bunaithe ar a costas, a luach tarrthála, a saolré réamh-mheasta, "
"agus tréimhse áirithe. Luasghéadaíonn an modh seo ráta an luachlaghdaithe, "
"ionas go dtarlaíonn níos mó costais luachlaghdaithe i dtréimhsí níos luaithe "
"ná i dtréimhsí níos déanaí. Is é an costas luachlaghdaithe an costas iarbhír "
"lúide an luach tarrthála. Is é an saolré úsáideach líon na dtréimhsí (de "
"ghnáth blianta) a ndéantar luachlaghdú ar an tsócmhainn."

#: functions/financial.xml:1282
#, kde-format
msgid "SYD(cost; salvage value; life; period)"
msgstr "SYD(costas; luach tarrthála; saolré; tréimhse)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1283
#, kde-format
msgid "SYD(5000; 200; 5; 2) equals 1280"
msgstr "Is ionann SYD(5000; 200; 5; 2) agus 1280"

#: functions/financial.xml:1305
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TBILLEQ functions returns the bond equivalent for a treasury bill. The "
"maturity date must be after the settlement date but within 365 days."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm TBILLEQ coibhéis an bhanna ar ais i gcás bille cisteáin. "
"Ní mór don dáta aibíochta a bheith i ndiaidh an dáta socraíochta ach "
"laistigh de 365 lá."

#: functions/financial.xml:1306
#, kde-format
msgid "TBILLEQ(settlement; maturity; discount)"
msgstr "TBILLEQ(socraíocht; aibíocht; lascaine)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1307
#, kde-format
msgid "TBILLEQ(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 0.1) returns 0.1068"
msgstr "Filleann TBILLEQ(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 0.1) é seo: 0.1068"

#: functions/financial.xml:1329
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TBILLPRICE functions returns the price per $100 value for a treasury "
"bill. The maturity date must be after the settlement date but within 365 "
"days. The discount rate must be positive."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm TBILLPRICE an praghas in aghaidh luach $100 ar ais do "
"bhille cisteáin. Ní mór don dáta aibíochta a bheith i ndiaidh an dáta "
"socraíochta ach laistigh de 365 lá. Ní mór don ráta lascaine a bheith "
"dearfach."

#: functions/financial.xml:1330
#, kde-format
msgid "TBILLPRICE(settlement; maturity; discount)"
msgstr "PRAGHAS TBILL(socraíocht; aibíocht; lascaine)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1331
#, kde-format
msgid "TBILLPRICE(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 0.05) returns 97.4444"
msgstr "Filleann TBILLPRICE(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 0.05) é seo: 97.4444"

#: functions/financial.xml:1353
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TBILLYIELD functions returns the yield for a treasury bill. The maturity "
"date must be after the settlement date but within 365 days. The price must "
"be positive."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm TBILLYIELD toradh bille cisteáin ar ais. Ní mór don dáta "
"aibíochta a bheith i ndiaidh an dáta socraíochta ach laistigh de 365 lá. Ní "
"mór don phraghas a bheith dearfach."

#: functions/financial.xml:1354
#, kde-format
msgid "TBILLYIELD(settlement; maturity; price)"
msgstr "TBILLYIELD(socraíocht; aibíocht; praghas)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1355
#, kde-format
msgid "TBILLYIELD(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 600) returns -1.63"
msgstr "Filleann TBILLYIELD(\"2/28/2001\"; \"8/31/2001\"; 600) é seo: -1.63"

#: functions/financial.xml:1385
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"VDB calculates the depreciation allowance of an asset with an initial value, "
"an expected useful life, and a final value of salvage for a period "
"specified, using the variable-rate declining balance method."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann VDB an liúntas dímheasa i gcás sócmhainne le luach tosaigh, saolré "
"úsáideach ionchais, agus luach deiridh tarrthála ar feadh tréimhse "
"sonraithe, ag baint úsáide as an modh iarmhéid laghdaitheach ráta "
"athraitheach."

#: functions/financial.xml:1386
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"VDB(cost; salvage; life; start-period; end-period; [; depreciation-factor = "
"2 [; switch = false ]] )"
msgstr ""
"VDB(costas; tarrtháil; saol; tréimhse tosaigh; tréimhse deiridh; [; fachtóir "
"dímheasa = 2 [; lasc = bréagach]] )"

#: functions/financial.xml:1387
#, kde-format
msgid "VDB(10000;600;10;0;0.875;1.5) returns 1312.5"
msgstr "Filleann VDB(10000;600;10;0;0.875;1.5) é seo: 1312.5"

#: functions/financial.xml:1399 functions/financial.xml:1426
#, kde-format
msgid "Dates"
msgstr "Dátaí"

#: functions/financial.xml:1407
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The XIRR function calculates the internal rate of return for a non-periodic "
"series of cash flows."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm XIRR an ráta inmheánach tuairisceáin do shraith "
"neamhthréimhsiúil sreafaí airgid."

#: functions/financial.xml:1408
#, kde-format
msgid "XIRR( Values; Dates[; Guess = 0.1 ] )"
msgstr "XIRR(Luachanna; Dátaí[; Buille faoi thuairim = 0.1])"

#: functions/financial.xml:1409
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"XIRR(B1:B4;C1:C4) Suppose B1:B4 contains -20000, 4000, 12000, 8000 while C1:"
"C4 contains \"=DATE(2000;1;1)\", \"=DATE(2000;6;1)\", \"=DATE(2000;12;30)\", "
"\"=DATE(2001;3;1)\" returns 0.2115964"
msgstr ""
"XIRR(B1:B4;C1:C4) Abair go bhfuil -20000, 4000, 12000, 8000 i B1:B4 agus go "
"bhfuil \"=DATE(2000;1;1)\", \"=DATE(2000;6;1)\", \"=DATE(2000;12;30)\", agus "
"go dtugann \"=DATE(2001;3;1)\" 0.2115964 ar ais"

#: functions/financial.xml:1430
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The XNPV function calculates the net present value of a series of cash flows."
msgstr "Ríomhann an fheidhm XNPV glanluach reatha sraith sreafaí airgid."

#: functions/financial.xml:1431
#, kde-format
msgid "XNPV( Rate; Values; Dates )"
msgstr "XNPV( Ráta; Luachanna; Dátaí )"

#: functions/financial.xml:1432
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"XNPV(5%;B1:B4;C1:C4) suppose B1:B4 contains -20000, 4000, 12000, 8000 while "
"C1:C4 contains \"=DATE(2000;1;1)\", \"=DATE(2000;6;1)\", "
"\"=DATE(2000;12;30)\", \"=DATE(2001;3;1)\" returns 2907.83187"
msgstr ""
"XNPV(5%;B1:B4;C1:C4) glactar leis go bhfuil -20000, 4000, 12000, 8000 i B1:"
"B4 agus go bhfuil \"=DATE(2000;1;1)\", \"=DATE(2000;6;1)\", "
"\"=DATE(2000;12;30)\", \"=DATE(2001;3;1)\" ina bhfuil 2907.83187 i C1:C4"

#: functions/financial.xml:1461
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"YIELDDISC calculates the yield of a discounted security per 100 currency "
"units of face value."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann YIELDDISC toradh urrúis lascainithe in aghaidh gach 100 aonad "
"airgeadra d’aghaidhluach."

#: functions/financial.xml:1462
#, kde-format
msgid "YIELDDISC(settlement; maturity; price, redemp, basis)"
msgstr "DISC TORADH(socraíocht; aibíocht; praghas, fuascailt, bonn)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1463
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"YIELDDISC(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1990;12;31);941.66667;1000) returns 0.106194684"
msgstr ""
"Tugann YIELDDISC(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1990;12;31);941.66667;1000) 0.106194684 "
"ar ais"

#: functions/financial.xml:1495
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The YIELDMAT function calculates the yield of the security that pays "
"interest on the maturity date."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm YIELDMAT toradh an urrúis a íocann ús ar an dáta "
"aibíochta."

#: functions/financial.xml:1496
#, kde-format
msgid "YIELDMAT( Settlement; Maturity; Issue; Rate; Price; Basis )"
msgstr "TORADH MAT( Socrú; Aibíocht; Eisiúint; Ráta; Praghas; Bunús )"

#: functions/financial.xml:1497
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"YIELDMAT(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1995;12;31);DATE(1990; 1; 1); 6%;103.819218241) "
"returns 0.050000000"
msgstr ""
"Tugann YIELDMAT(DATE(1990;6;1);DATE(1995;12;31);"
"DATE(1990;1;1);6%;103.819218241) 0.050000000 ar ais"

#: functions/financial.xml:1520
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ZERO_COUPON() function calculates the value of a zero-coupon (pure "
"discount) bond. For example: if the interest rate is 10%, a $1000 bond that "
"matures in 20 years is worth ZERO_COUPON(1000;.1;20) or $148.64."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm ZERO_COUPON() luach banna nialasach-cúpóin (lascaine "
"íon). Mar shampla: má tá an ráta úis 10%, is fiú ZERO_COUPON(1000;.1;20) nó "
"$148.64 banna $1000 a aibíonn i gceann 20 bliain."

#: functions/financial.xml:1521
#, kde-format
msgid "ZERO_COUPON(face value;rate;years)"
msgstr "CÚPÓN_NIALAS(luach aghaidhe;ráta;blianta)"

#: functions/financial.xml:1522
#, kde-format
msgid "ZERO_COUPON(1000;.1;20) equals 148.64"
msgstr "Is ionann ZERO_COUPON(1000;.1;20) agus 148.64"

