#: functions/information.xml:44
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The N() function converts a value to a number. If value is or refers to a "
"number, this function returns the number. If value is True, this function "
"returns 1. If a value is a date, this function returns the serial number of "
"that date. Anything else will cause the function to return 0."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm N() luach a thiontú go huimhir. Má tá luach ina uimhir nó "
"má thagraíonn sí d'uimhir, tugann an fheidhm seo an uimhir ar ais. Má tá "
"luach fíor, tugann an fheidhm seo 1 ar ais. Más dáta é luach, tugann an "
"fheidhm seo uimhir sraitheach an dáta sin ar ais. Aon rud eile, cuirfidh an "
"fheidhm 0 ar ais."

#: functions/information.xml:45
#, kde-format
msgid "N(value)"
msgstr "N(luach)"

#: functions/information.xml:46
#, kde-format
msgid "N(3.14) returns 3.14"
msgstr "Filleann N(3.14) é seo: 3.14"

#: functions/information.xml:47
#, kde-format
msgid "N(\"7\") returns 0 (because \"7\" is text)"
msgstr "Filleann N(\"7\") é seo: 0 (because \"7\" is text)"

#: functions/information.xml:55
#, kde-format
msgid "Type of information"
msgstr "Cineál eolais"

#: functions/information.xml:59
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The INFO() function returns information about the current operating "
"environment. Parameter type specifies what type of information you want to "
"return. It is one of the following: \"directory\" returns the path of the "
"current directory, \"numfile\" returns the number of active documents, "
"\"release\" returns the version of Calligra Sheets as text, \"recalc\" "
"returns the current recalculation mode: \"Automatic\" or \"Manual\", \"system"
"\" returns the name of the operating environment, \"osversion\" returns the "
"current operating system."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm INFO() faisnéis faoin timpeallacht oibriúcháin reatha ar "
"ais. Sonraíonn cineál paraiméadair cén cineál faisnéise is mian leat a "
"thabhairt ar ais. Is ceann amháin díobh seo a leanas é: tugann \"directory\" "
"cosán an eolaire reatha ar ais, tugann \"numfile\" líon na ndoiciméad "
"gníomhach ar ais, tugann \"release\" leagan Calligra Sheets ar ais mar "
"théacs, tugann \"recalc\" an modh athríofa reatha ar ais: \"Automatic\" nó "
"\"Manual\", tugann \"system\" ainm an chomhshaoil oibriúcháin ar ais, tugann "
"\"osversion\" an córas oibriúcháin reatha ar ais."

#: functions/information.xml:60
#, kde-format
msgid "INFO(type)"
msgstr "INFO(cineál)"

