"Tugann an fheidhm OR() Fíor ar ais má tá ceann amháin ar a laghad de na "
"luachanna fíor. Seachas sin, tugann sí Bréagach ar ais (mura bhfuil aon "
"cheann de na luachanna ina earráid, ansin tugann sí earráid ar ais)."

#: functions/logic.xml:83
#, kde-format
msgid "OR(value;value;...)"
msgstr "OR(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/logic.xml:84
#, kde-format
msgid "OR(false;false;false) returns False"
msgstr "Filleann OR(false;false;false) é seo: False"

#: functions/logic.xml:85
#, kde-format
msgid "OR(true;false) returns True"
msgstr "Filleann OR(true;false) é seo: True"

#: functions/logic.xml:113
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The NAND() function returns True if at least one value is not true. "
"Otherwise it returns False."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm NAND() Fíor ar ais mura bhfuil luach amháin ar a laghad "
"fíor. Seachas sin, tugann sí Bréagach ar ais."

#: functions/logic.xml:114
#, kde-format
msgid "NAND(value;value;...)"
msgstr "NAND(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/logic.xml:115
#, kde-format
msgid "NAND(true;false;false) returns True"
msgstr "Filleann NAND(true;false;false) é seo: True"

#: functions/logic.xml:116
#, kde-format
msgid "NAND(true;true) returns False"
msgstr "Filleann NAND(true;true) é seo: False"

#: functions/logic.xml:144
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The NOR() function returns True if all the values given as parameters are of "
"boolean type and have the value false. Otherwise it returns False."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm NOR() Fíor ar ais má tá na luachanna uile a thugtar mar "
"pharaiméadair de chineál Booleánach agus má tá an luach bréagach acu. "
"Seachas sin, tugann sí Bréagach ar ais."

#: functions/logic.xml:145
#, kde-format
msgid "NOR(value;value;...)"
msgstr "NOR(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/logic.xml:146
#, kde-format
msgid "NOR(true;false;false) returns False"
msgstr "Filleann NOR(true;false;false) é seo: False"

#: functions/logic.xml:147
#, kde-format
msgid "NOR(false;false) returns True"
msgstr "Filleann NOR(false;false) é seo: True"

#: functions/logic.xml:175
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The XOR() function returns False if the number of True values is even. "
"Otherwise it returns True. It returns an error if any argument is an error."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm XOR() Bréagach ar ais má tá líon na luachanna Fíor "
"cothrom. Seachas sin, tugann sí Fíor ar ais. Tugann sí earráid ar ais má tá "
"aon argóint ina earráid."

#: functions/logic.xml:176
#, kde-format
msgid "XOR(value;value;...)"
msgstr "XOR(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/logic.xml:177
#, kde-format
msgid "XOR(false;false;false) returns True"
msgstr "Filleann XOR(false;false;false) é seo: True"

#: functions/logic.xml:178
#, kde-format
msgid "XOR(true;false) returns True"
msgstr "Filleann XOR(true;false) é seo: True"

#: functions/logic.xml:186
#, kde-format
msgid "Boolean value"
msgstr "Luach Boole"

#: functions/logic.xml:190
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The NOT() function returns True if the value is False and returns False if "
"the value is True. It returns an error if the input in an error."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm NOT() Fíor ar ais má tá an luach Bréagach agus tugann sí "
"Bréagach ar ais má tá an luach Fíor. Tugann sí earráid ar ais má tá earráid "
"san ionchur."

#: functions/logic.xml:191
#, kde-format
msgid "NOT(bool)"
msgstr "NACH(bool)"

#: functions/logic.xml:192
#, kde-format
msgid "NOT(false) returns True"
msgstr "Filleann NOT(false) é seo: True"

#: functions/logic.xml:193
#, kde-format
msgid "NOT(true) returns False"
msgstr "Filleann NOT(true) é seo: False"

#: functions/logic.xml:201
#, kde-format
msgid "Condition"
msgstr "Coinníoll"

#: functions/logic.xml:205
#, kde-format
msgid "If true"
msgstr "Más fíor"

#: functions/logic.xml:209
#, kde-format
msgid "If false"
msgstr "Más bréagach"

#: functions/logic.xml:213
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The IF() function is a conditional function. This function returns the "
"second parameter if the condition is True. Otherwise it returns the third "
"parameter (which defaults to being false)."
msgstr ""
"Is feidhm choinníollach í an fheidhm IF(). Seolann an fheidhm seo an dara "
"paraiméadar ar ais má tá an coinníoll fíor. Seachas sin, seolann sí an tríú "
"paraiméadar ar ais (a bhfuil an réamhshocrú bréagach air)."

#: functions/logic.xml:214
#, kde-format
msgid "IF(condition;if_true;if_false)"
msgstr "MÁ(coinníoll;más_fíor;más_bréagach)"

#: functions/logic.xml:215
#, kde-format
msgid "A1=4;A2=6;IF(A1>A2;5;3) returns 3"
msgstr "Filleann A1=4;A2=6;IF(A1>A2;5;3) é seo: 3"

#: functions/logic.xml:223 functions/logic.xml:241
#, kde-format
msgid "Any X"
msgstr "Aon X"

#: functions/logic.xml:227 functions/logic.xml:245
#, kde-format
msgid "Any Alternative"
msgstr "Aon Rogha Eile"

#: functions/logic.xml:231
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Return X unless it is an Error, in which case return an alternative value."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair X ar ais mura Earráid atá ann, agus sa chás sin cuir luach malartach "
"ar ais."

#: functions/logic.xml:232
#, kde-format
msgid "IFERROR(AnyX;AnyAlternative)"
msgstr "MASEARRÁID(AonX;AonRoghaEile)"

#: functions/logic.xml:233
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"IFERROR(A1;A2) returns the content of A1 if that content is not an error-"
"value else the content of A2 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Seolann IFERROR(A1;A2) ábhar A1 ar ais mura luach earráide é an t-ábhar sin "
"nó seoltar ábhar A2 ar ais."

#: functions/logic.xml:249
#, kde-format
msgid "Return X unless it is an NA, in which case return an alternative value."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair X ar ais mura NA é, agus sa chás sin tabhair luach malartach ar ais."

#: functions/logic.xml:250
#, kde-format
msgid "IFNA(AnyX;AnyAlternative)"
msgstr "IFNA(AonX;AonRoghaEile)"

#: functions/logic.xml:251
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"IFNA(A1;A2) returns the content of A1 if that content is not an #N/A error-"
"value else the content of A2 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Tugann IFNA(A1;A2 ábhar A1 ar ais mura luach earráide #N/A é an t-ábhar sin "
"nó cuirtear ábhar A2 ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Math"
msgstr "Matamaitic"

#: functions/math.xml:11
#, kde-format
msgid "Function"
msgstr "Feidhm"

#: functions/math.xml:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUBTOTAL() function returns a subtotal of a given list of arguments "
"ignoring other subtotal results in there. Function can be one of the "
"following numbers: 1 - Average, 2 - Count, 3 - CountA, 4 - Max, 5 - Min, 6 - "
"Product, 7 - StDev, 8 - StDevP, 9 - Sum, 10 - Var, 11 - VarP."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm SUBTOTAL() fo-iomlán liosta argóintí ar leith ar ais, ag "
"neamhaird a dhéanamh de thorthaí fo-iomlána eile atá ann. Is féidir leis an "
"bhfeidhm a bheith ar cheann de na huimhreacha seo a leanas: 1 - Meán, 2 - "
"Líon, 3 - LíonA, 4 - Uasmhéid, 5 - Íosmhéid, 6 - Táirge, 7 - StDev, 8 - "
"StDevP, 9 - Suim, 10 - Var, 11 - VarP."

#: functions/math.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBTOTAL(function; value)"
msgstr "FO-IOMLÁN(feidhm; luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:21
#, kde-format
msgid "If A1:A5 contains 7, 24, 23, 56 and 9:"
msgstr "Má tá 7, 24, 23, 56 agus 9 in A1:A5:"

#: functions/math.xml:22
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBTOTAL(1; A1:A5) returns 23.8"
msgstr "Filleann SUBTOTAL(1; A1:A5) é seo: 23.8"

#: functions/math.xml:23
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBTOTAL(4; A1:A5) returns 56"
msgstr "Filleann SUBTOTAL(4; A1:A5) é seo: 56"

#: functions/math.xml:24
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBTOTAL(9; A1:A5) returns 119"
msgstr "Filleann SUBTOTAL(9; A1:A5) é seo: 119"

#: functions/math.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBTOTAL(11; A1:A5) returns 307.76"
msgstr "Filleann SUBTOTAL(11; A1:A5) é seo: 307.76"

#: functions/math.xml:44
#, kde-format
msgid "X the independent variable of the power series"
msgstr "X an athróg neamhspleách den tsraith chumhachta"

#: functions/math.xml:48
#, kde-format
msgid "N the initial power to which X is to be raised"
msgstr "N an chumhacht tosaigh ar a bhfuil X le hardú"

#: functions/math.xml:52
#, kde-format
msgid "M the increment by which to increase N for each term in the series"
msgstr "M an méadú faoina méadófar N do gach téarma sa tsraith"

#: functions/math.xml:56
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Coefficients a set of coefficients by which each successive power of the "
"variable X is multiplied"
msgstr ""
"Comhéifeachtaí tacar comhéifeachtaí lena n-iolraítear gach cumhacht as a "
"chéile den athróg X"

#: functions/math.xml:60
#, kde-format
msgid "The SERIESSUM() function returns the sum of a power series."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm SERIESUM() suim shraith chumhachta ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:61
#, kde-format
msgid "SERIESSUM( X; N; M; Coefficients)"
msgstr "SERIESSUM( X; N; M; Comhéifeachtaí)"

#: functions/math.xml:62
#, kde-format
msgid "SERIESSUM(2;0;2;{1;2}) return 9"
msgstr "Filleann SERIESSUM(2;0;2;{1;2}) é seo: 9"

#: functions/math.xml:79
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The LCM() function returns the least common multiple for two or more float "
"values"
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm LCM() an t-iolraí coiteann is lú ar ais do dhá luach "
"snámhphointe nó níos mó"

#: functions/math.xml:80
#, kde-format
msgid "LCM(value; value)"
msgstr "LCM(luach; luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:81
#, kde-format
msgid "LCM(6;4) returns 12"
msgstr "Filleann LCM(6;4) é seo: 12"

#: functions/math.xml:82
#, kde-format
msgid "LCM(1.5;2.25) returns 4.5"
msgstr "Filleann LCM(1.5;2.25) é seo: 4.5"

#: functions/math.xml:83
#, kde-format
msgid "LCM(2;3;4) returns 12"
msgstr "Filleann LCM(2;3;4) é seo: 12"

#: functions/math.xml:100
#, kde-format
msgid "Third number"
msgstr "An tríú uimhir"

#: functions/math.xml:104
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The GCD() function returns the greatest common denominator for two or more "
"integer values."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm GCD() an comhainmneoir is mó ar ais do dhá luach "
"slánuimhir nó níos mó."

#: functions/math.xml:105
#, kde-format
msgid "GCD(value; value)"
msgstr "GCD(luach; luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:106
#, kde-format
msgid "GCD(6;4) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann GCD(6;4) é seo: 2"

#: functions/math.xml:107
#, kde-format
msgid "GCD(10;20) returns 10"
msgstr "Filleann GCD(10;20) é seo: 10"

#: functions/math.xml:108
#, kde-format
msgid "GCD(20;15;10) returns 5"
msgstr "Filleann GCD(20;15;10) é seo: 5"

#: functions/math.xml:117
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"EPS() returns the machine epsilon; this is the difference between 1 and the "
"next largest floating-point number. Because computers use a finite number of "
"digits, roundoff error is inherent (but usually insignificant) in all "
"calculations."
msgstr ""
"Filleann EPS() é seo: the machine epsilon; this is the difference between 1 "
"and the next largest floating-point number. Because computers use a finite "
"number of digits, roundoff error is inherent (but usually insignificant) in "
"all calculations."

#: functions/math.xml:118
#, kde-format
msgid "EPS()"
msgstr "EPS()"

#: functions/math.xml:119
#, kde-format
msgid "On most systems, this returns 2^-52=2.2204460492503131e-16"
msgstr ""
"Ar fhormhór na gcóras, tugann sé seo 2^-52=2.2204460492503131e-16 ar ais"

#: functions/math.xml:120
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"0.5*EPS() returns the \"unit round\"; this value is interesting because it "
"is the largest number x where (1+x)-1=0 (due to roundoff errors)."
msgstr ""
"Filleann 0.5*EPS() é seo: the \"unit round\"; this value is interesting "
"because it is the largest number x where (1+x)-1=0 (due to roundoff errors)."

#: functions/math.xml:121
#, kde-format
msgid "EPS() is so small that Calligra Sheets displays 1+eps() as 1"
msgstr "Tá EPS() chomh beag sin go dtaispeánann Calligra Sheets 1+eps() mar 1"

#: functions/math.xml:122
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Pick a number x between 0 and EPS(). Observe that 1+x rounds x to either 0 "
"or EPS() by using the equation (1+x)-1"
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh uimhir x idir 0 agus EPS(). Tabhair faoi deara go ndéanann 1+x "
"babhtú ar x go 0 nó EPS() trí úsáid a bhaint as an gcothromóid (1+x)-1"

#: functions/math.xml:138
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The POWER(x;y) function returns the value of x raised to the power of y."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm POWER(x;y) luach x ar ais ardaithe go cumhacht y."

#: functions/math.xml:139
#, kde-format
msgid "POWER(value;value)"
msgstr "POWER(luach;luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:140
#, kde-format
msgid "POWER(1.2;3.4) equals 1.8572"
msgstr "Is ionann POWER(1.2;3.4) agus 1.8572"

#: functions/math.xml:141
#, kde-format
msgid "POWER(2;3) equals 8"
msgstr "Is ionann POWER(2;3) agus 8"

#: functions/math.xml:158
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The POW(x;y) function returns the value of x raised to the power of y. It's "
"the same as POWER."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm POW(x;y) luach x ar ais ardaithe go dtí cumhacht y. Is "
"ionann é agus POWER."

#: functions/math.xml:159
#, kde-format
msgid "POW(value;value)"
msgstr "POW(luach;luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:160
#, kde-format
msgid "POW(1.2;3.4) equals 1.8572"
msgstr "Is ionann POW(1.2;3.4) agus 1.8572"

#: functions/math.xml:161
#, kde-format
msgid "POW(2;3) equals 8"
msgstr "Is ionann POW(2;3) agus 8"

#: functions/math.xml:174
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The EVEN() function returns the number rounded up to the nearest even "
"integer."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm EVEN() an uimhir shlánaithe suas go dtí an slánuimhir "
"chothrom is gaire ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:175
#, kde-format
msgid "EVEN(value)"
msgstr "EVEN(luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:176
#, kde-format
msgid "EVEN(1.2) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann EVEN(1.2) é seo: 2"

#: functions/math.xml:177
#, kde-format
msgid "EVEN(2) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann EVEN(2) é seo: 2"

#: functions/math.xml:190
#, kde-format
msgid "Precision"
msgstr "Beachtas"

#: functions/math.xml:194
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TRUNC() function truncates a numeric value to a certain precision. If "
"the precision is omitted 0 is assumed."
msgstr ""
"Gearrann an fheidhm TRUNC() luach uimhriúil go cruinneas áirithe. Má fhágtar "
"an cruinneas ar lár, glactar leis go bhfuil 0 ann."

#: functions/math.xml:195
#, kde-format
msgid "TRUNC(value; precision)"
msgstr "TRUNC(luach; beachtas)"

#: functions/math.xml:196
#, kde-format
msgid "TRUNC(1.2) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann TRUNC(1.2) é seo: 1"

#: functions/math.xml:197
#, kde-format
msgid "TRUNC(213.232; 2) returns 213.23"
msgstr "Filleann TRUNC(213.232; 2) é seo: 213.23"

#: functions/math.xml:212
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ODD() function returns the number rounded up (or down, for negative "
"values) to the nearest odd integer. By definition, ODD(0) is 1."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ODD() an uimhir ar ais atá slánaithe suas (nó síos, i gcás "
"luachanna diúltacha) go dtí an slánuimhir corr is gaire. De réir "
"sainmhínithe, is ionann ODD(0) agus 1."

#: functions/math.xml:213
#, kde-format
msgid "ODD(value)"
msgstr "ODD(luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:214
#, kde-format
msgid "ODD(1.2) returns 3"
msgstr "Filleann ODD(1.2) é seo: 3"

#: functions/math.xml:215
#, kde-format
msgid "ODD(2) returns 3"
msgstr "Filleann ODD(2) é seo: 3"

#: functions/math.xml:216
#, kde-format
msgid "ODD(-2) returns -3"
msgstr "Filleann ODD(-2) é seo: -3"

#: functions/math.xml:229
#, kde-format
msgid "The GAMMA() function returns the gamma function value."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm GAMMA() luach na feidhme gáma ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:230
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMA(value)"
msgstr "GAMMA(luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:231
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMA(1) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann GAMMA(1) é seo: 1"

#: functions/math.xml:248
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MOD() function returns the remainder after division. If the second "
"parameter is null the function returns #DIV/0."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm MOD() an fuílleach ar ais tar éis roinnte. Má tá an dara "
"paraiméadar nialasach, tugann an fheidhm #DIV/0 ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:249
#, kde-format
msgid "MOD(value;value)"
msgstr "MOD(luach;luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:250
#, kde-format
msgid "MOD(12;5) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann MOD(12;5) é seo: 2"

#: functions/math.xml:251
#, kde-format
msgid "MOD(5;5) returns 0"
msgstr "Filleann MOD(5;5) é seo: 0"

#: functions/math.xml:264
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This function returns -1 if the number is negative, 0 if the number is null "
"and 1 if the number is positive."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm seo -1 ar ais má tá an uimhir dhiúltach, 0 má tá an uimhir "
"nialasach agus 1 má tá an uimhir dhearfach."

#: functions/math.xml:265
#, kde-format
msgid "SIGN(value)"
msgstr "SIGN(luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:266
#, kde-format
msgid "SIGN(5) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann SIGN(5) agus 1"

#: functions/math.xml:267
#, kde-format
msgid "SIGN(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann SIGN(0) agus 0"

#: functions/math.xml:268
#, kde-format
msgid "SIGN(-5) equals -1"
msgstr "Is ionann SIGN(-5) agus -1"

#: functions/math.xml:280
#, kde-format
msgid "This function multiplies each value by -1."
msgstr "Déanann an fheidhm seo gach luach a iolrú faoi -1."

#: functions/math.xml:281
#, kde-format
msgid "INV(value)"
msgstr "INV(luach)"

#: functions/math.xml:282
#, kde-format
msgid "INV(-5) equals 5"
msgstr "Is ionann INV(-5) agus 5"

#: functions/math.xml:283
#, kde-format
msgid "INV(5) equals -5"
msgstr "Is ionann INV(5) agus -5"

#: functions/math.xml:284
#, kde-format
msgid "INV(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann INV(0) agus 0"

#: functions/math.xml:296
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This function returns the count of integer or floating arguments passed. You "
"can count using a range: COUNT(A1:B5) or using a list of values like "
"COUNT(12;5;12.5)."
msgstr ""
"Seolann an fheidhm seo líon na slánuimhreacha nó na n-argóintí snámhacha a "
"rithtear. Is féidir leat comhaireamh a dhéanamh trí raon a úsáid: COUNT(A1:"
"B5) nó trí liosta luachanna a úsáid cosúil le COUNT(12;5;12.5)."

#: functions/math.xml:297
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNT(value;value;value...)"
msgstr "COUNT(luach;luach;luach...)"

#: functions/math.xml:298
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNT(-5;\"KSpread\";2) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann COUNT(-5;\"KSpread\";2) é seo: 2"

#: functions/math.xml:299
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNT(5) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann COUNT(5) é seo: 1"

#: functions/math.xml:314
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This function returns the count of all non empty arguments passed. You can "
"count using a range: COUNTA(A1:B5) or using a list of values like "
"COUNTA(12;5;12.5)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm seo líon na n-argóintí neamhfholamh uile a ritheadh ar "
"ais. Is féidir leat comhaireamh a dhéanamh trí raon a úsáid: COUNTA(A1:B5) "
"nó trí liosta luachanna cosúil le COUNTA(12;5;12.5) a úsáid."

#: functions/math.xml:315
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNTA(value;value;value...)"
msgstr "COUNTA(luach;luach;luach...)"

#: functions/math.xml:316
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNTA(-5;\"KSpread\";2) returns 3"
msgstr "Filleann COUNTA(-5;\"KSpread\";2) é seo: 3"

#: functions/math.xml:317
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNTA(5) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann COUNTA(5) é seo: 1"

#: functions/math.xml:327
#, kde-format
msgid "Cell range"
msgstr "Raon cille"

#: functions/math.xml:331
#, kde-format
msgid "This function returns the count of all empty cells within the range."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm seo líon na gcealla folamh uile laistigh den raon ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:332
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNTBLANK(range)"
msgstr "COUNTBLANK(raon)"

#: functions/math.xml:333
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNTBLANK(A1:B5)"
msgstr "COUNTBLANK(A1:B5)"

#: functions/math.xml:344 functions/math.xml:1215
#, kde-format
msgid "Range"
msgstr "Raon"

#: functions/math.xml:348 functions/math.xml:433
#, kde-format
msgid "Criteria"
msgstr "Critéir"

#: functions/math.xml:352
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The COUNTIF() function returns the number of cells in the given range that "
"meet the given criteria."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm COUNTIF() líon na gcealla sa raon tugtha a chomhlíonann na "
"critéir tugtha ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:353
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNTIF(range;criteria)"
msgstr "COUNTIF(raon;critéir)"

#: functions/math.xml:354
#, kde-format
msgid "COUNTIF(A2:A3;\"14\") returns 1 if A2 is -4 and A3 is 14"
msgstr "Filleann COUNTIF(A2:A3;\"14\") é seo: 1 más -4 é A2 agus is 14 é A3"

