#: functions/math.xml:368
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FACT() function calculates the factorial of the parameter. The "
"mathematical expression is (value)!."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm FACT() fachtóir an pharaiméadair. Is é (luach)! an "
"abairt mhatamaiticiúil."

#: functions/math.xml:369
#, kde-format
msgid "FACT(number)"
msgstr "FACT(uimhir)"

#: functions/math.xml:370
#, kde-format
msgid "FACT(10) returns 3628800"
msgstr "Filleann FACT(10) é seo: 3628800"

#: functions/math.xml:371
#, kde-format
msgid "FACT(0) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann FACT(0) é seo: 1"

#: functions/math.xml:383
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FACTDOUBLE() function calculates the double factorial of a number, i.e. "
"x!!."
msgstr "Ríomhann an fheidhm FACTDOUBLE() fachtóir dúbailte uimhir, i.e. x!!."

#: functions/math.xml:384
#, kde-format
msgid "FACTDOUBLE(number)"
msgstr "FACTDOUBLE(uimhir)"

#: functions/math.xml:385
#, kde-format
msgid "FACTDOUBLE(6) returns 48"
msgstr "Filleann FACTDOUBLE(6) é seo: 48"

#: functions/math.xml:386
#, kde-format
msgid "FACTDOUBLE(7) returns 105"
msgstr "Filleann FACTDOUBLE(7) é seo: 105"

#: functions/math.xml:398
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUM() function calculates the sum of all the values given as parameters. "
"You can calculate the sum of a range SUM(A1:B5) or a list of values like "
"SUM(12;5;12.5)."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm SUM() suim na luachanna uile a thugtar mar "
"pharaiméadair. Is féidir leat suim raoin SUM(A1:B5) nó liosta luachanna "
"cosúil le SUM(12;5;12.5) a ríomh."

#: functions/math.xml:399 functions/math.xml:417
#, kde-format
msgid "SUM(value;value;...)"
msgstr "SUM(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:400
#, kde-format
msgid "SUM(12;5;7) equals 24"
msgstr "Is ionann SUM(12;5;7) agus 24"

#: functions/math.xml:401
#, kde-format
msgid "SUM(12.5;2) equals 14.5"
msgstr "Is ionann SUM(12.5;2) agus 14.5"

#: functions/math.xml:416
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUMA() function calculates the sum of all the values given as "
"parameters. You can calculate the sum of a range SUMA(A1:B5) or a list of "
"values like SUMA(12;5;12.5). If a parameter contains text or the boolean "
"value FALSE it is counted as 0, if a parameter evaluates to TRUE it is "
"counted as 1."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm SUMA() suim na luachanna uile a thugtar mar "
"pharaiméadair. Is féidir leat suim raoin SUMA(A1:B5) nó liosta luachanna "
"cosúil le SUMA(12;5;12.5) a ríomh. Má tá téacs nó an luach booléanach FALSE "
"i bparaiméadar, comhairtear é mar 0, má mheastar go FÍOR go paraiméadar, "
"comhairtear é mar 1."

#: functions/math.xml:418
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMA(12;5; 7) equals 24"
msgstr "Is ionann SUMA(12;5;7) agus 24"

#: functions/math.xml:419
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMA(12.5; 2; TRUE) equals 15.5"
msgstr "Is ionann SUMA(12.5; 2; TRUE) agus 15.5"

#: functions/math.xml:429
#, kde-format
msgid "Check range"
msgstr "Raon seiceála"

#: functions/math.xml:437
#, kde-format
msgid "Sum range"
msgstr "Raon suime"

#: functions/math.xml:441
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUMIF() function calculates the sum of all values given as parameters "
"which match the criteria. The sum range is optional. If not supplied, the "
"values in the check range are summed. The length of the check range should "
"be equal or less than the length of the sum range."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm SUMIF() suim na luachanna uile a thugtar mar "
"pharaiméadair a chomhlíonann na critéir. Tá an raon suime roghnach. Mura "
"soláthraítear é, déantar na luachanna sa raon seiceála a shuimiú. Ba chóir "
"go mbeadh fad an raoin seiceála cothrom le nó níos lú ná fad an raoin suime."

#: functions/math.xml:442
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMIF(checkrange;criteria;sumrange)"
msgstr "SUMIF(raon seiceála;critéir;raon suime)"

#: functions/math.xml:443
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMIF(A1:A4;\">1\") sums all values in range A1:A4 which match >1"
msgstr ""
"Suimíonn SUMIF(A1:A4;\">1\") na luachanna uile sa raon A1:A4 a mheaitseálann "
">1"

#: functions/math.xml:444
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"SUMIF(A1:A4;\"=0\";B1:B4) sums all values in range B1:B4 if the "
"corresponding value in A1:A4 matches =0"
msgstr ""
"Suimíonn SUMIF(A1:A4;\"=0\";B1:B4) na luachanna uile sa raon B1:B4 má tá an "
"luach comhfhreagrach in A1:A4 ag teacht le =0"

#: functions/math.xml:458
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The PRODUCT() function calculates the product of all the values given as "
"parameters. You can calculate the product of a range: PRODUCT(A1:B5) or a "
"list of values like product(12;5;12.5). If no numeric values are found 0 is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm PRODUCT() toradh na luachanna uile a thugtar mar "
"pharaiméadair. Is féidir leat toradh raoin a ríomh: PRODUCT(A1:B5) nó liosta "
"luachanna cosúil le product(12;5;12.5). Mura bhfuarthas aon luachanna "
"uimhriúla, cuirtear 0 ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:459
#, kde-format
msgid "PRODUCT(value;value;...)"
msgstr "PRODUCT(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:460
#, kde-format
msgid "PRODUCT(3;5;7) equals 105"
msgstr "Is ionann PRODUCT(3;5;7) agus 105"

#: functions/math.xml:461
#, kde-format
msgid "PRODUCT(12.5;2) equals 25"
msgstr "Is ionann PRODUCT(12.5;2) agus 25"

#: functions/math.xml:475
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The KPRODUCT() function calculates the product of all the values given as "
"parameters. You can calculate the product of a range: KPRODUCT(A1:B5) or a "
"list of values like KPRODUCT(12;5;12.5). If no numeric values are found 1 is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm KPRODUCT() toradh na luachanna uile a thugtar mar "
"pharaiméadair. Is féidir leat toradh raoin a ríomh: KPRODUCT(A1:B5) nó "
"liosta luachanna cosúil le KPRODUCT(12;5;12.5). Mura bhfuarthas aon "
"luachanna uimhriúla, cuirtear 1 ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:476
#, kde-format
msgid "KPRODUCT(value;value;...)"
msgstr "KPRODUCT(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:477
#, kde-format
msgid "KPRODUCT(3;5;7) equals 105"
msgstr "Is ionann KPRODUCT(3;5;7) agus 105"

#: functions/math.xml:478
#, kde-format
msgid "KPRODUCT(12.5;2) equals 25"
msgstr "Is ionann KPRODUCT(12.5;2) agus 25"

#: functions/math.xml:493
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The G_PRODUCT() function is the same as KPRODUCT. It is provided for "
"Gnumeric compatibility."
msgstr ""
"Is ionann an fheidhm G_PRODUCT() agus KPRODUCT. Cuirtear ar fáil í le "
"haghaidh comhoiriúnachta Gnumeric."

#: functions/math.xml:494
#, kde-format
msgid "G_PRODUCT(value;value;...)"
msgstr "G_PRODUCT(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:507
#, kde-format
msgid "The DIV() function divides the first value by the other values in turn."
msgstr ""
"Roinneann an fheidhm DIV() an chéad luach ar na luachanna eile ina dhiaidh "
"sin."

#: functions/math.xml:508
#, kde-format
msgid "DIV(value;value;...)"
msgstr "DIV(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:509
#, kde-format
msgid "DIV(20;2;2) returns 5"
msgstr "Filleann DIV(20;2;2) é seo: 5"

#: functions/math.xml:510
#, kde-format
msgid "DIV(25;2.5) returns 10"
msgstr "Filleann DIV(25;2.5) é seo: 10"

#: functions/math.xml:524
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUMSQ() function calculates the sum of all the squares of values given "
"as parameters. You can calculate the sum of a range SUMSQ(A1:B5) or a list "
"of values like SUMSQ(12;5;12.5)."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm SUMSQ() suim na gcearnóg luachanna uile a thugtar mar "
"pharaiméadair. Is féidir leat suim raon SUMSQ(A1:B5) nó liosta luachanna "
"cosúil le SUMSQ(12;5;12.5) a ríomh."

#: functions/math.xml:525
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMSQ(value;value;...)"
msgstr "SUMSQ(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:526
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMSQ(12;5;7) equals 218"
msgstr "Is ionann SUMSQ(12;5;7) agus 218"

#: functions/math.xml:527
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMSQ(12.5;2) equals 173"
msgstr "Is ionann SUMSQ(12.5;2) agus 173"

#: functions/math.xml:541
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MAX() function returns the largest value given in the parameters. String "
"and logical values are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm MAX() an luach is mó a thugtar sna paraiméadair ar ais. "
"Déantar neamhaird ar luachanna teaghrán agus loighciúla."

#: functions/math.xml:542
#, kde-format
msgid "MAX(value;value;...)"
msgstr "MAX(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:543
#, kde-format
msgid "MAX(12;5; 7) returns 12"
msgstr "Filleann MAX(12;5; 7) é seo: 12"

#: functions/math.xml:544
#, kde-format
msgid "MAX(12.5; 2) returns 12.5"
msgstr "Filleann MAX(12.5; 2) é seo: 12.5"

#: functions/math.xml:545
#, kde-format
msgid "MAX(0.5; 0.4; TRUE; 0.2) returns 0.5"
msgstr "Filleann MAX(0.5; 0.4; TRUE; 0.2) é seo: 0.5"

#: functions/math.xml:562
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MAXA() function returns the largest value given in the parameters. TRUE "
"evaluates to 1, FALSE evaluates to 0. String values are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm MAXA() an luach is mó a thugtar sna paraiméadair ar ais. "
"Meastar gurb é 1 an luach TRUE, meastar gurb é 0 an luach FALSE. Déantar "
"neamhaird de luachanna teaghrán."

#: functions/math.xml:563
#, kde-format
msgid "MAXA(value;value;...)"
msgstr "MAXA(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:564
#, kde-format
msgid "MAXA(12;5; 7) returns 12"
msgstr "Filleann MAXA(12;5; 7) é seo: 12"

#: functions/math.xml:565
#, kde-format
msgid "MAXA(12.5; 2) returns 12.5"
msgstr "Filleann MAXA(12.5; 2) é seo: 12.5"

#: functions/math.xml:566
#, kde-format
msgid "MAXA(0.5; 0.4; TRUE; 0.2) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann MAXA(0.5; 0.4; TRUE; 0.2) é seo: 1"

#: functions/math.xml:583
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MIN() function returns the smallest value given in the parameters. "
"String and logical values are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm MIN() an luach is lú a thugtar sna paraiméadair ar ais. "
"Déantar neamhaird ar luachanna teaghrán agus loighciúla."

#: functions/math.xml:584
#, kde-format
msgid "MIN(value;value;...)"
msgstr "MIN(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:585
#, kde-format
msgid "MIN(12;5; 7) returns 5"
msgstr "Filleann MIN(12;5; 7) é seo: 5"

#: functions/math.xml:586
#, kde-format
msgid "MIN(12.5; 2) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann MIN(12.5; 2) é seo: 2"

#: functions/math.xml:587
#, kde-format
msgid "MIN(0.4; 2; FALSE; 0.7) returns 0.4"
msgstr "Filleann MIN(0.4; 2; FALSE; 0.7) é seo: 0.4"

#: functions/math.xml:604
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MINA() function returns the smallest value given in the parameters. TRUE "
"evaluates to 1, FALSE to 0. String values are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm MINA() an luach is lú a thugtar sna paraiméadair ar ais. "
"Meastar go 1 é TRUE, go 0 é FALSE. Déantar neamhaird ar luachanna teaghrán."

#: functions/math.xml:605
#, kde-format
msgid "MINA(value;value;...)"
msgstr "MINA(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:606
#, kde-format
msgid "MINA(12;5; 7) returns 5"
msgstr "Filleann MINA(12;5; 7) é seo: 5"

#: functions/math.xml:607
#, kde-format
msgid "MINA(12.5; 2) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann MINA(12.5; 2) é seo: 2"

#: functions/math.xml:608
#, kde-format
msgid "MINA(0.4; 2; FALSE; 0.7) returns 0."
msgstr "Filleann MINA(0. 4; 2; FALSE; 0. 7) 0."

#: functions/math.xml:625
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MULTIPLY() function multiplies all the values given in the parameters. "
"You can multiply values given by a range MULTIPLY(A1:B5) or a list of values "
"like MULTIPLY(12;5;12.5). It's equivalent to PRODUCT."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm MULTIPLY() na luachanna uile a thugtar sna paraiméadair a "
"iolrú. Is féidir leat luachanna a thugtar a iolrú le raon MULTIPLY(A1:B5) nó "
"liosta luachanna cosúil le MULTIPLY(12;5;12.5). Is ionann é agus PRODUCT."

#: functions/math.xml:626
#, kde-format
msgid "MULTIPLY(value;value;...)"
msgstr "MULTIPLY(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:627
#, kde-format
msgid "MULTIPLY(12;5;7) equals 420"
msgstr "Is ionann IOLRAIGH(12;5;7) agus 420"

#: functions/math.xml:628
#, kde-format
msgid "MULTIPLY(12.5;2) equals 25"
msgstr "Is ionann IOLRAIGH(12.5;2) agus 25"

#: functions/math.xml:643
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MULTINOMIAL() function returns the multinomial of each number in the "
"parameters. It uses this formula for MULTINOMIAL(a,b,c):"
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm MULTINOMIAL() iltéarma gach uimhir sna paraiméadair ar "
"ais. Úsáideann sí an fhoirmle seo le haghaidh MULTINOMIAL(a,b,c):"

#: functions/math.xml:644
#, kde-format
msgid "(a+b+c)! / a!b!c!"
msgstr "(a+b+c)! / a!b!c!"

#: functions/math.xml:645
#, kde-format
msgid "MULTINOMIAL(value;value;...)"
msgstr "MULTINOMIAL(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/math.xml:646
#, kde-format
msgid "MULTINOMIAL(3;4;5) equals 27720"
msgstr "Is ionann MULTINOMIAL((3;4;5) agus 27720"

#: functions/math.xml:658
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SQRT() function returns the non-negative square root of the argument. It "
"is an error if the argument is negative."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm SQRT() fréamh chearnach neamh-dhiúltach an argóint ar ais. "
"Is earráid í má tá an argóint diúltach."

#: functions/math.xml:659
#, kde-format
msgid "SQRT(x)"
msgstr "SQRT(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:660
#, kde-format
msgid "SQRT(9) equals 3"
msgstr "Is ionann SQRT(9) agus 3"

#: functions/math.xml:661
#, kde-format
msgid "SQRT(-9) is an error"
msgstr "Filleann SQRT(-9) earráid"

#: functions/math.xml:674
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SQRTPI() function returns the non-negative square root of x * PI. It is "
"an error if the argument is negative."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm SQRTPI() fréamh chearnach neamh-dhiúltach x * PI ar ais. "
"Is earráid í má tá an argóint diúltach."

#: functions/math.xml:675
#, kde-format
msgid "SQRTPI(x)"
msgstr "SQRTPI(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:676
#, kde-format
msgid "SQRTPI(2) equals 2.506628"
msgstr "Is ionann SQRTPI(2) agus 2.506628"

#: functions/math.xml:688
#, kde-format
msgid "The LN() function returns the natural logarithm of x."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm LN() logartam nádúrtha x ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:689
#, kde-format
msgid "LN(x)"
msgstr "LN(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:690
#, kde-format
msgid "LN(0.8) equals -0.22314355"
msgstr "Is ionann LN(0.8) agus -0.22314355"

#: functions/math.xml:691
#, kde-format
msgid "LN(0) equals -inf"
msgstr "Is ionann LN(0) agus -inf"

#: functions/math.xml:710
#, kde-format
msgid "The LOGn() function returns the base n logarithm of x."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm LOGn() logartam bonn n de x ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:711
#, kde-format
msgid "LOGn(value;base)"
msgstr "LOGn(luach;bonn)"

#: functions/math.xml:712
#, kde-format
msgid "LOGn(12;10) equals 1.07918125"
msgstr "Is ionann LOGn(12;10) agus 1.07918125"

#: functions/math.xml:713
#, kde-format
msgid "LOGn(12;2) equals 3.5849625"
msgstr "Is ionann LOGn(12;2) agus 3.5849625"

#: functions/math.xml:733
#, kde-format
msgid "The ROOTN() function returns the non-negative nth root of x."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm ROOTN() an nú fréamh neamh-dhiúltach de x ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:734
#, kde-format
msgid "ROOTN(x;n)"
msgstr "ROOTN(x;n)"

#: functions/math.xml:735
#, kde-format
msgid "ROOTN(9;2) equals 3"
msgstr "Is ionann ROOTN(9;2) agus 3"

#: functions/math.xml:748
#, kde-format
msgid "The CUR() function returns the non-negative cube root of x."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm CUR() fréamh chiúbach neamh-dhiúltach x ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:749
#, kde-format
msgid "CUR(x)"
msgstr "CUR(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:750
#, kde-format
msgid "CUR(27) equals 3"
msgstr "Is ionann CUR(27) agus 3"

#: functions/math.xml:759
#, kde-format
msgid "A floating point value, greater than zero"
msgstr "Luach snámhphointe, níos mó ná náid"

#: functions/math.xml:763
#, kde-format
msgid "The LOG() function returns the base-10 logarithm of x."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm LOG() logartam bonn-10 x ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:764
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG(x)"
msgstr "LOG(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:765
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG(0.8) equals -0.09691001"
msgstr "Is ionann LOG(0.8) agus -0.09691001"

#: functions/math.xml:766
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG(0) is an error."
msgstr "Filleann LOG(0) earráid."

#: functions/math.xml:778
#, kde-format
msgid "A positive floating point value"
msgstr "Luach snámhphointe níos mó ná náid"

#: functions/math.xml:782
#, kde-format
msgid "The LOG10() function returns the base-10 logarithm of the argument."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm LOG10() logartam bonn-10 an argóint ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:783
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG10(x)"
msgstr "LOG10(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:784
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG10(10) equals 1."
msgstr "Is ionann LOG10(10) agus 1."

#: functions/math.xml:785
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG10(0) is an error."
msgstr "Filleann LOG10(0) earráid."

#: functions/math.xml:801
#, kde-format
msgid "The LOG2() function returns the base-2 logarithm of x."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm LOG2() logartam bonn-2 x ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:802
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG2(x)"
msgstr "LOG2(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:803
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG2(0.8) equals -0.32192809"
msgstr "Is ionann LOG2(0.8) agus -0.32192809"

#: functions/math.xml:804
#, kde-format
msgid "LOG2(0) equals -inf."
msgstr "Is ionann LOG2(0) agus -inf."

#: functions/math.xml:820
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The EXP() function returns the value of e (the base of natural logarithms) "
"raised to the power of x."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm EXP() luach e (bonn na logartam nádúrtha) ardaithe go dtí "
"cumhacht x ar ais."

#: functions/math.xml:821
#, kde-format
msgid "EXP(x)"
msgstr "EXP(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:822
#, kde-format
msgid "EXP(9) equals 8 103.08392758"
msgstr "Is ionann EXP(9) agus 8 103.08392758"

#: functions/math.xml:823
#, kde-format
msgid "EXP(-9) equals 0.00012341"
msgstr "Is ionann EXP(-9) agus 0.00012341"

#: functions/math.xml:836
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CEIL() function rounds x up to the nearest integer which is greater than "
"the input, returning that value as a double."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm CEIL() babhtú ar x suas go dtí an slánuimhir is gaire atá "
"níos mó ná an t-ionchur, ag tabhairt an luach sin ar ais mar dhúbailt."

#: functions/math.xml:837
#, kde-format
msgid "CEIL(x)"
msgstr "CEIL(x)"

#: functions/math.xml:838
#, kde-format
msgid "CEIL(12.5) equals 13"
msgstr "Is ionann CEIL(12.5) agus 13"

#: functions/math.xml:839
#, kde-format
msgid "CEIL(-12.5) equals -12"
msgstr "Is ionann CEIL(-12.5) agus -12"

#: functions/math.xml:855 functions/math.xml:884
#, kde-format
msgid "Significance (optional)"
msgstr "Bunuimhir (roghnach)"

#: functions/math.xml:859 functions/math.xml:888
#, kde-format
msgid "Mode (optional)"
msgstr "Mód (roghnach)"

#: functions/math.xml:863
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CEILING() function rounds x up (away from zero) to the nearest multiple "
"of Significance which is greater than the input. The default value for "
"Significance is 1 (or -1 if the value is negative), which means rounding up "
"to the nearest integer. If the Mode parameter is non-zero, the function "
"rounds away from zero, instead of up towards the positive infinity."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm CEILING() babhtú ar x suas (ar shiúl ó náid) go dtí an t-"
"iolraí is gaire de Significance atá níos mó ná an ionchur. Is é 1 an luach "
"réamhshocraithe do Significance (nó -1 má tá an luach diúltach), rud a "
"chiallaíonn babhtú suas go dtí an slánuimhir is gaire. Mura bhfuil an "
"paraiméadar Mode cothrom le náid, babhtaíonn an fheidhm ar shiúl ó náid, "
"seachas suas i dtreo an éigríoch dhearfaigh."

