msgstr "Is ionann CEILING(6.43; 4) agus 8"

#: functions/math.xml:867
#, kde-format
msgid "CEILING(-6.43; -4; 1) equals -8"
msgstr "Is ionann CEILING(-6.43; -4; 1) agus -8"

#: functions/math.xml:868
#, kde-format
msgid "CEILING(-6.43; -4; 0) equals -4"
msgstr "Is ionann CEILING(-6.43; -4; 0) agus -4"

#: functions/math.xml:892
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Round a number x down to the nearest multiple of the second parameter, "
"Significance."
msgstr ""
"Babhtaigh uimhir x síos go dtí an t-iolraí is gaire den dara paraiméadar, "
"Suntasacht."

#: functions/math.xml:899
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FLOOR() function rounds x down (towards zero) to the nearest multiple of "
"Significance which is smaller than the input.\n"
"                The default value for Significance is 1, if x is positive. "
"It is -1, if the value is negative,\n"
"                which means rounding up to the nearest integer.\n"
"                If mode is given and not equal to zero, the amount of x is "
"rounded toward zero to a multiple\n"
"                of significance and then the sign applied. Otherwise, it "
"rounds toward negative infinity.\n"
"                    If any of the two parameters x or Significance is zero, "
"the result is zero."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm FLOOR() babhtú ar x síos (i dtreo náid) go dtí an t-"
"iolraí is gaire de Suntasacht atá níos lú ná an ionchur.\n"
"                Is é 1 an luach réamhshocraithe do Suntasacht, má tá x "
"dearfach. Is é -1 é, má tá an luach diúltach,\n"
"                rud a chiallaíonn babhtú suas go dtí an slánuimhir is "
"gaire.\n"
"                Má thugtar mód agus mura bhfuil sé cothrom le náid, déantar "
"méid x a bhabhtú i dtreo náid go dtí iolraí de \n"
"                shuntasacht agus ansin cuirtear an comhartha i bhfeidhm. "
"Seachas sin, babhtaítear i dtreo éigríoch dhiúltach.\n"
"                    Más ionann aon cheann den dá pharaiméadar x nó "
"Suntasacht agus náid, is é náid an toradh."

