msgstr "Iolraí"

#: functions/math.xml:1098
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MROUND() function returns the value rounded to the specified multiple. "
"The value and the multiple must have the same sign"
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm MROUND() an luach slánaithe ar ais go dtí an t-iolraí "
"sonraithe. Ní mór don luach agus don iolraí an comhartha céanna a bheith acu"

#: functions/math.xml:1099
#, kde-format
msgid "MROUND(value; multiple)"
msgstr "MROUND(luach; iolraí)"

#: functions/math.xml:1100
#, kde-format
msgid "MROUND(1.252; 0.5) equals 1.5"
msgstr "Is ionann MROUND(1.252; 0.5) agus 1.5"

#: functions/math.xml:1101
#, kde-format
msgid "MROUND(-1.252; -0.5) equals -1.5"
msgstr "Is ionann MROUND(-1.252; -0.5) agus -1.5"

#: functions/math.xml:1114 functions/math.xml:1139 functions/math.xml:1162
#, kde-format
msgid "Digits"
msgstr "Digití"

#: functions/math.xml:1118
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ROUND(value;[digits]) function returns value rounded. Digits is the "
"number of digits to which you want to round that number. If digits is zero "
"or omitted, value is rounded up to the nearest integer. If digits is smaller "
"than zero, the corresponding integer part of the number is rounded."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ROUND(luach;[digití]) luach slánaithe ar ais. Is é digití "
"líon na ndigití ar mhaith leat an uimhir sin a shlánú chucu. Má tá digití "
"ina náid nó má fhágtar ar lár é, déantar an luach a shlánú suas go dtí an "
"slánuimhir is gaire. Má tá digití níos lú ná náid, déantar an chuid "
"shlánuimhir chomhfhreagrach den uimhir a shlánú."

#: functions/math.xml:1119
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUND(value;[digits])"
msgstr "ROUND(luach;[digití])"

#: functions/math.xml:1120
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUND(1.252;2) equals 1.25"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUND(1.252;2) agus 1.25"

#: functions/math.xml:1121
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUND(-1.252;2) equals -1.25"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUND(-1.252;2) agus -1.25"

#: functions/math.xml:1122
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUND(1.258;2) equals 1.26"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUND(1.258;2) agus 1.26"

#: functions/math.xml:1123
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUND(-12.25;-1) equals -10"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUND(-12.25;-1) agus -10"

#: functions/math.xml:1124
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUND(-1.252;0) equals -1"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUND(-1.252;0) cothrom le -1"

#: functions/math.xml:1143
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ROUNDUP(value;[digits]) function returns value rounded so that its "
"absolute value is greater. Digits is the number of digits to which you want "
"to round that number. If digits is zero or omitted, value is rounded up to "
"the nearest integer."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ROUNDUP(luach;[digití]) luach slánaithe ar ais ionas go "
"mbeidh a luach absalóideach níos mó. Is é digití líon na ndigití ar mhaith "
"leat an uimhir sin a shlánú chucu. Má tá digití nialasach nó má fhágtar ar "
"lár é, déantar an luach a shlánú suas go dtí an slánuimhir is gaire."

#: functions/math.xml:1144
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDUP(value;[digits])"
msgstr "ROUNDUP(luach;[digití])"

#: functions/math.xml:1145
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDUP(1.252) equals 2"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUNDUP(1.252) cothrom le 2"

#: functions/math.xml:1146
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDUP(1.252;2) equals 1.26"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUNDUP(1.252;2) agus 1.26"

#: functions/math.xml:1147
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDUP(-1.252;2) equals -1.26"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUNDUP(-1.252;2) agus -1.26"

#: functions/math.xml:1148
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDUP(-1.252) equals -2"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUNDUP(-1.252) agus -2"

#: functions/math.xml:1166
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ROUNDDOWN(value;[digits]) function returns value rounded so that its "
"absolute value is lesser. Digits is the number of digits to which you want "
"to round that number. If digits is zero or omitted, value is rounded down to "
"the nearest integer."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ROUNDDOWN(luach;[digití]) luach slánaithe ar ais sa chaoi "
"is go bhfuil a luach absalóideach níos lú. Is é digití líon na ndigití ar "
"mhaith leat an uimhir sin a shlánú chucu. Má tá digití ina náid nó má "
"fhágtar ar lár iad, déantar an luach a shlánú síos go dtí an slánuimhir is "
"gaire."

#: functions/math.xml:1167
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDDOWN(value;[digits])"
msgstr "ROUNDDOWN(luach;[digití])"

#: functions/math.xml:1168
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDDOWN(1.252) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUNDDOWN(1.252) agus 1"

#: functions/math.xml:1169
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDDOWN(1.252;2) equals 1.25"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUNDDOWN(1.252;2) agus 1.25"

#: functions/math.xml:1170
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDDOWN(-1.252;2) equals -1.25"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUNDDOWN(-1.252;2) agus -1.25"

#: functions/math.xml:1171
#, kde-format
msgid "ROUNDDOWN(-1.252) equals -1"
msgstr "Is ionann ROUNDDOWN(-1.252) agus -1"

#: functions/math.xml:1181
#, kde-format
msgid "Nth term"
msgstr "Téarma Nú"

#: functions/math.xml:1185
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Function FIB calculates the Nth term of a Fibonacci sequence (1, 1, 2, 3, 5, "
"8, 13, 21...), in which each number, after the first two, is the sum of the "
"two numbers immediately preceding it. FIB(0) is defined to be 0."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann feidhm FIB an Nú téarma de sheicheamh Fibonacci (1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, "
"13, 21...), ina bhfuil gach uimhir, i ndiaidh an chéad dá cheann, cothrom le "
"suim an dá uimhir díreach roimhe. Sainmhínítear FIB(0) mar 0."

