msgstr "Ainm na bileoige"

#: functions/reference.xml:31
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ADDRESS creates a cell address. Parameter Row is the row number and "
"Column is the column number."
msgstr ""
"Cruthaíonn an ADDRESS seoladh cille. Is é an Paraiméadar Row uimhir an ró "
"agus is é an Column uimhir an cholúin."

#: functions/reference.xml:32
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Absolute number specifies the type of reference: 1 or omitted = Absolute, 2 "
"= Absolute row, relative column,  3 = Relative row; absolute column and 4 = "
"Relative."
msgstr ""
"Sonraíonn uimhir absalóideach an cineál tagartha: 1 nó fágtha ar lár = "
"Absalóideach, 2 = Sraith absalóideach, colún coibhneasta, 3 = Sraith "
"choibhneasta; colún absalóideach agus 4 = Coibhneasta."

#: functions/reference.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A1 Style specifies the style of the address to return. If A1 is set to TRUE "
"(default) the address is returned in A1 style if it is set to FALSE in R1C1 "
"style."
msgstr ""
"Sonraíonn Stíl A1 stíl an seoladh atá le tabhairt ar ais. Má shocraítear A1 "
"go TRUE (réamhshocrú), cuirtear an seoladh ar ais i stíl A1 má shocraítear é "
"go FALSE i stíl R1C1."

#: functions/reference.xml:34
#, kde-format
msgid "Sheet name is the text specifying the name of the sheet."
msgstr "Is é ainm na bileoige an téacs a shonraíonn ainm na bileoige."

#: functions/reference.xml:35
#, kde-format
msgid "ADDRESS(row; col; absolute; style; sheet name)"
msgstr "SEOLLADH(sraith; col; absalóideach; stíl; ainm bileoige)"

#: functions/reference.xml:36
#, kde-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4) returns $D$6"
msgstr "Filleann ADDRESS(6; 4) é seo: $D$6"

#: functions/reference.xml:37
#, kde-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4; 2) returns D$6"
msgstr "Filleann ADDRESS(6; 4; 2) é seo: D$6"

#: functions/reference.xml:38
#, kde-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4; 2; FALSE; \"Sheet1\") returns Sheet1!R6C[4]"
msgstr "Filleann ADDRESS(6; 4; 2; FALSE; \"Sheet1\") é seo: Sheet1!R6C[4]"

#: functions/reference.xml:39
#, kde-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4; 1; FALSE; \"Sheet1\") returns Sheet1!R6C4"
msgstr "Filleann ADDRESS(6; 4; 1; FALSE; \"Sheet1\") é seo: Sheet1!R6C4"

#: functions/reference.xml:40
#, kde-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4; 4; TRUE; \"Sheet1\") returns Sheet1!D6"
msgstr "Filleann ADDRESS(6; 4; 4; TRUE; \"Sheet1\") é seo: Sheet1!D6"

#: functions/reference.xml:52
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Returns the number of areas in the reference string. An area can be asingle "
"cell or a set of cells."
msgstr ""
"Tugann sé seo líon na limistéar sa teaghrán tagartha ar ais. Is féidir "
"limistéar a bheith ina chill aonair nó ina shraith cealla."

#: functions/reference.xml:53
#, kde-format
msgid "AREAS(reference)"
msgstr "AREAS(tagairt)"

#: functions/reference.xml:54
#, kde-format
msgid "AREAS(A1) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann AREAS(A1) é seo: 1"

#: functions/reference.xml:55
#, kde-format
msgid "AREAS((A1; A2:A4)) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann AREAS((A1; A2:A4)) é seo: 2"

#: functions/reference.xml:71
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Returns information about position, formatting or contents in a reference."
msgstr ""
"Tugann sé seo faisnéis faoi shuíomh, formáidiú nó ábhar i dtagairt ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:72
#, kde-format
msgid "CELL(type; reference)"
msgstr "CELL(cineál; tagairt)"

#: functions/reference.xml:73
#, kde-format
msgid "CELL(\"COL\", C7) returns 3"
msgstr "Tugann CELL(\"COL\", C7) 3 ar ais"

#: functions/reference.xml:74
#, kde-format
msgid "CELL(\"ROW\", C7) returns 7"
msgstr "Tugann CELL(\"ROW\", C7) 7 ar ais"

#: functions/reference.xml:75
#, kde-format
msgid "CELL(\"ADDRESS\", C7) returns $C$7"
msgstr "Seolann CELL(\"ADDRESS\", C7) $C$7 ar ais"

#: functions/reference.xml:82
#, kde-format
msgid "Index"
msgstr "Innéacs"

#: functions/reference.xml:86
#, kde-format
msgid "Arguments"
msgstr "Argóintí"

#: functions/reference.xml:89
#, kde-format
msgid "Returns the parameter specified by the index."
msgstr "Tugann sé an paraiméadar atá sonraithe ag an innéacs ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:90
#, kde-format
msgid "CHOOSE(index; parameter1; parameter2;...)"
msgstr "ROGHNAIGH(innéacs; paraiméadar1; paraiméadar2;...)"

#: functions/reference.xml:91
#, kde-format
msgid "CHOOSE(1; \"1st\"; \"2nd\") returns \"1st\""
msgstr "Filleann CHOOSE(1; \"1st\"; \"2nd\") é seo: \"1st\""

#: functions/reference.xml:92
#, kde-format
msgid "CHOOSE(2; 3; 2; 4) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann CHOOSE(2; 3; 2; 4) é seo: 2"

#: functions/reference.xml:104
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The COLUMN function returns the column of given cell reference. If no "
"parameter is specified the column of the current cell gets returned."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm COLUMN colún na tagairte cille ar leith ar ais. Mura "
"sonraítear aon pharaiméadar, cuirtear colún na cille reatha ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:105
#, kde-format
msgid "COLUMN(reference)"
msgstr "COLUMN(tagairt)"

#: functions/reference.xml:106
#, kde-format
msgid "COLUMN(A1) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann COLUMN(A1) é seo: 1"

#: functions/reference.xml:107
#, kde-format
msgid "COLUMN(D2) returns 4"
msgstr "Filleann COLUMN(D2) é seo: 4"

#: functions/reference.xml:121
#, kde-format
msgid "The COLUMNS function returns the number of columns in a reference."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm COLUMNS líon na gcolún i dtagairt ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:122
#, kde-format
msgid "COLUMNS(reference)"
msgstr "COLUMNS(tagairt)"

#: functions/reference.xml:123
#, kde-format
msgid "COLUMNS(A1:C3) returns 3"
msgstr "Filleann COLUMNS(A1:C3) é seo: 3"

#: functions/reference.xml:124
#, kde-format
msgid "COLUMNS(D2) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann COLUMNS(D2) é seo: 1"

#: functions/reference.xml:137 functions/reference.xml:266
#, kde-format
msgid "Row"
msgstr "Ró"

#: functions/reference.xml:141 functions/reference.xml:292
#, kde-format
msgid "Column"
msgstr "Colún"

#: functions/reference.xml:145
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If a range is given, returns value stored in a given row/column. If one cell "
"is given, which contains an array, then one element of the array is returned."
msgstr ""
"Má thugtar raon, cuirtear luach ar ais atá stóráilte i ró/cholún ar leith. "
"Má thugtar cill amháin ina bhfuil eagar, cuirtear eilimint amháin den eagar "
"ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:146
#, kde-format
msgid "INDEX(cell, row, column)"
msgstr "INDEX(cill, ró, colún)"

#: functions/reference.xml:147
#, kde-format
msgid "INDEX(range, row, column)"
msgstr "INDEX(raon, ró, colún)"

#: functions/reference.xml:148
#, kde-format
msgid "INDEX(A1:C3;2;2), returns contents of B2"
msgstr "Tugann INDEX(A1:C3;2;2) ábhar B2 ar ais"

#: functions/reference.xml:149
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"INDEX(A1;2;2), if A1 is a result of array calculation, returns its (2,2) "
"element."
msgstr ""
"Má tá A1 mar thoradh ar ríomh eagar, tugann INDEX(A1;2;2) a eilimint (2,2) "
"ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:164
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Returns the content of the cell specified by the reference text. The second "
"parameter is optional."
msgstr ""
"Tugann sé seo ábhar na cille atá sonraithe ag an téacs tagartha ar ais. Tá "
"an dara paraiméadar roghnach."

#: functions/reference.xml:165
#, kde-format
msgid "INDIRECT(referenceText, a1 style)"
msgstr "INDÍREACH(Téacs tagartha, stíl a1)"

#: functions/reference.xml:166
#, kde-format
msgid "INDIRECT(A1), A1 contains \"B1\", and B1 1 => returns 1"
msgstr "INDIRECT(A1), tá \"B1\" in A1, agus tugann B1 1 => 1 ar ais"

#: functions/reference.xml:167
#, kde-format
msgid "INDIRECT(\"A1\"), returns content of A1"
msgstr "Tugann INDIRECT(\"A1\") ábhar A1 ar ais"

#: functions/reference.xml:179
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ROW function returns the row of given cell reference. If no parameter is "
"specified the row of the current cell gets returned."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ROW an tsraith den tagairt cille ar leith ar ais. Mura "
"sonraítear aon pharaiméadar, faightear sraith na cille reatha ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:180
#, kde-format
msgid "ROW(reference)"
msgstr "ROW(tagairt)"

#: functions/reference.xml:181
#, kde-format
msgid "ROW(A1) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann ROW(A1) é seo: 1"

#: functions/reference.xml:182
#, kde-format
msgid "ROW(D2) returns 2"
msgstr "Filleann ROW(D2) é seo: 2"

#: functions/reference.xml:196
#, kde-format
msgid "The ROWS function returns the number of rows in a reference."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm ROWS líon na sraitheanna i dtagairt ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:197
#, kde-format
msgid "ROWS(reference)"
msgstr "ROWS(tagairt)"

#: functions/reference.xml:198
#, kde-format
msgid "ROWS(A1:C3) returns 3"
msgstr "Filleann ROWS(A1:C3) é seo: 3"

#: functions/reference.xml:199
#, kde-format
msgid "ROWS(D2) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann ROWS(D2) é seo: 1"

#: functions/reference.xml:213
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Returns the sheet number of the reference or the string representing a sheet "
"name."
msgstr ""
"Tugann sé seo uimhir bhileoige an tagartha nó an teaghrán a léiríonn ainm "
"bileoige ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:214
#, kde-format
msgid "SHEET(reference)"
msgstr "BILEOG (tagairt)"

#: functions/reference.xml:215
#, kde-format
msgid "SHEET(Sheet1!C7) returns 1"
msgstr "Tugann SHEET(Bileog1!C7) 1 ar ais"

#: functions/reference.xml:216
#, kde-format
msgid "SHEET(Sheet2!C7) returns 2"
msgstr "Tugann SHEET(Bileog2!C7) 2 ar ais"

#: functions/reference.xml:228
#, kde-format
msgid "Returns the number of sheets in a reference or current document."
msgstr ""
"Tugann sé seo líon na mbileog i dtagairt nó i ndoiciméad reatha ar ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:229
#, kde-format
msgid "SHEETS(reference)"
msgstr "BILEOGA (tagairt)"

#: functions/reference.xml:236 functions/reference.xml:258
#: functions/reference.xml:284
#, kde-format
msgid "Lookup value"
msgstr "Luach féach-suas"

#: functions/reference.xml:240
#, kde-format
msgid "Lookup vector"
msgstr "Veicteoir cuardaigh"

#: functions/reference.xml:244
#, kde-format
msgid "Result vector"
msgstr "Veicteoir toraidh"

#: functions/reference.xml:248
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The LOOKUP function looks up the first parameter in the lookup vector. It "
"returns a value in the result Vector with the same index as the matching "
"value in the lookup vector. If value is not in the lookup vector it takes "
"the next lower one. If no value in the lookup vector matches an error is "
"returned. The lookup vector must be in ascending order and lookup and result "
"vector must have the same size. Numeric values, string and boolean values "
"are recognized. Comparison between strings is case-insensitive."
msgstr ""
"Cuardaíonn an fheidhm LOOKUP an chéad pharaiméadar sa veicteoir cuardaigh. "
"Tugann sí luach ar ais sa Veicteoir toraidh leis an innéacs céanna leis an "
"luach meaitseála sa veicteoir cuardaigh. Mura bhfuil an luach sa veicteoir "
"cuardaigh, tógann sí an chéad cheann eile níos ísle. Mura bhfuil aon luach "
"sa veicteoir cuardaigh meaitseála, cuirtear earráid ar ais. Caithfidh an "
"veicteoir cuardaigh a bheith in ord ardaitheach agus ní mór don veicteoir "
"cuardaigh agus don veicteoir toraidh an méid céanna a bheith acu. Aithnítear "
"luachanna uimhriúla, luachanna teaghrán agus luachanna Boole. Tá comparáid "
"idir teaghráin neamh-íogair ó thaobh cás de."

#: functions/reference.xml:249
#, kde-format
msgid "LOOKUP(value; lookup vector; result vector)"
msgstr "LOOKUP(luach; veicteoir cuardaigh; veicteoir toraidh)"

#: functions/reference.xml:250
#, kde-format
msgid "LOOKUP(1.232; A1:A6; B1:B6) for A1 = 1, A2 = 2 returns the value of B1."
msgstr ""
"Tugann LOOKUP(1.232; A1:A6; B1:B6) le haghaidh A1 = 1, A2 = 2 luach B1 ar "
"ais."

#: functions/reference.xml:262 functions/reference.xml:288
#, kde-format
msgid "Data source"
msgstr "Foinse sonraí"

#: functions/reference.xml:270 functions/reference.xml:296
#, kde-format
msgid "Sorted (optional)"
msgstr "Sórtáilte (roghnach)"

#: functions/reference.xml:274
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Look for a matching value in the first row of the given table, and return "
"the value of the indicated row."
msgstr ""
"Cuardaigh luach comhoiriúnach sa chéad ró den tábla tugtha, agus tabhair ar "
"ais luach na ró a léirítear."

#: functions/reference.xml:275
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Looks up the 'lookup value' in the first row of the 'data source'. If a "
"value matches, the value in the 'row' and the column, the value was found "
"in, is returned. If 'sorted' is true (default), the first row is assumed to "
"be sorted. The search will end, if the 'lookup value' is lower than the "
"value, currently compared to."
msgstr ""
"Cuardaíonn sé an 'luach cuardaigh' sa chéad ró den 'fhoinse sonraí'. Má "
"thagann luach leis, cuirtear an luach sa 'ró' agus sa cholún ina bhfuarthas "
"an luach ar ais. Má tá 'sorted' fíor (réamhshocrú), glactar leis go bhfuil "
"an chéad ró sórtáilte. Críochnóidh an cuardach, má tá an 'luach cuardaigh' "
"níos ísle ná an luach, i gcomparáid leis faoi láthair."

#: functions/reference.xml:276
#, kde-format
msgid "HLOOKUP(Lookup value; data source; Row; Sorted)"
msgstr "HLOOKUP(Luach cuardaigh; foinse sonraí; Ró; Sórtáilte)"

#: functions/reference.xml:300
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Look for a matching value in the first column of the given table, and return "
"the value of the indicated column."
msgstr ""
"Cuardaigh luach comhoiriúnach sa chéad cholún den tábla tugtha, agus tabhair "
"ar ais luach an cholúin léirithe."

#: functions/reference.xml:301
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Looks up the 'lookup value' in the first column of the 'data source'. If a "
"value matches, the value in the 'column' and the row, the value was found "
"in, is returned. If 'sorted' is true (default), the first column is assumed "
"to be sorted. The search will end, if the 'lookup value' is lower than the "
"value, currently compared to."
msgstr ""
"Cuardaíonn sé an 'luach cuardaigh' sa chéad cholún den 'fhoinse sonraí'. Má "
"thagann luach leis, cuirtear an luach sa 'cholún' agus sa tsraith ina "
"bhfuarthas an luach ar ais. Má tá 'sorted' fíor (réamhshocrú), glactar leis "
"go bhfuil an chéad cholún sórtáilte. Críochnóidh an cuardach, má tá an "
"'luach cuardaigh' níos ísle ná an luach, i gcomparáid leis faoi láthair."

#: functions/reference.xml:302
#, kde-format
msgid "VLOOKUP(Lookup value; data source; Column; Sorted)"
msgstr "VLOOKUP(Luach cuardaigh; foinse sonraí; Colún; Sórtáilte)"

#: functions/reference.xml:310
#, kde-format
msgid "Formula cell"
msgstr "Cill foirmle"

#: functions/reference.xml:314
#, kde-format
msgid "Row cell"
msgstr "Cill ró"

#: functions/reference.xml:318
#, kde-format
msgid "Row replacement"
msgstr "Athsholáthar sraithe"

#: functions/reference.xml:322
#, kde-format
msgid "Column cell (optional)"
msgstr "Cill cholúin (roghnach)"

#: functions/reference.xml:326
#, kde-format
msgid "Column replacement (optional)"
msgstr "Athsholáthar colún (roghnach)"

#: functions/reference.xml:330
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"MULTIPLE.OPERATIONS executes the formula expression pointed to by "
"FormulaCell and all formula expressions it depends on while replacing all "
"references to RowCell with references to RowReplacement respectively all "
"references to ColumnCell with references to ColumnReplacement. The function "
"may be used to easily create tables of expressions that depend on two input "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"Déanann MULTIPLE.OPERATIONS an abairt foirmle a bhfuil FormulaCell ag "
"tagairt di agus na habairtí foirmle uile a bhraitheann sé orthu a "
"fhorghníomhú agus gach tagairt do RowCell á hathsholáthar le tagairtí do "
"RowReplacement faoi seach le gach tagairt do ColumnCell le tagairtí do "
"ColumnReplacement. Is féidir an fheidhm a úsáid chun táblaí de nathanna a "
"chruthú go héasca a bhraitheann ar dhá pharaiméadar ionchuir."

#: functions/reference.xml:331
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"MULTIPLE.OPERATIONS(Formula cell; Row cell; Row replacement; Column cell; "
"Column replacement)"
msgstr ""
"OIBRÍOCHTAÍ IOLRAITHE(Cill foirmle; Cill ró; Athsholáthar ró; Cill colúin; "
"Athsholáthar colúin)"

#: functions/reference.xml:339
#, kde-format
msgid "Search value"
msgstr "Luach cuardaigh"

#: functions/reference.xml:343
#, kde-format
msgid "Search region"
msgstr "Réigiún cuardaigh"

#: functions/reference.xml:347
#, kde-format
msgid "Match type (optional)"
msgstr "Cineál cuardaigh (roghnach)"

#: functions/reference.xml:351
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Finds a search value in a search region, and returns its position (starting "
"from 1). Match type can be either -1, 0 or 1 and determines how is searched "
"for the value. If match type is 0, the index of the first value that equals "
"search value is returned. If match type is 1 (or omitted), the index of the "
"first value that is less than or equal to the search value is returned and "
"the values in the search region must be sorted in ascending order. If match "
"type is -1, the smallest value that is greater than or equal to the search "
"value is found, and the search region needs to be sorted in descending order."
msgstr ""
"Faightear luach cuardaigh i réigiún cuardaigh, agus tugann sé a shuíomh ar "
"ais (ag tosú ó 1). Is féidir leis an gcineál meaitseála a bheith -1, 0 nó 1 "
"agus cinneann sé conas a chuardaítear an luach. Más é 0 an cineál "
"meaitseála, cuirtear innéacs an chéad luacha atá cothrom leis an luach "
"cuardaigh ar ais. Más é 1 an cineál meaitseála (nó má fhágtar ar lár é), "
"cuirtear innéacs an chéad luacha atá níos lú ná nó cothrom leis an luach "
"cuardaigh ar ais agus ní mór na luachanna sa réigiún cuardaigh a shórtáil in "
"ord ardaitheach. Más é -1 an cineál meaitseála, aimsítear an luach is lú atá "
"níos mó ná nó cothrom leis an luach cuardaigh, agus ní mór an réigiún "
"cuardaigh a shórtáil in ord íslitheach."

#: functions/reference.xml:352
#, kde-format
msgid "MATCH(Search value; Search region; Match type)"
msgstr "MATCH(Luach cuardaigh; Réigiún cuardaigh; Cineál meaitseáil)"

#: functions/reference.xml:360
#, kde-format
msgid "Reference or range"
msgstr "Tagairt nó raon"

#: functions/reference.xml:364
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of rows to offset"
msgstr "Líon na sraitheanna le fritháireamh"

#: functions/reference.xml:368
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of columns to offset"
msgstr "Líon na gcolún le fritháireamh"

#: functions/reference.xml:372
#, kde-format
msgid "Height of the offset range (optional)"
msgstr "Airde an raoin fhritháireamh (roghnach)"

#: functions/reference.xml:376
#, kde-format
msgid "Width of the offset range (optional)"
msgstr "Leithead an raoin fhritháireamh (roghnach)"

#: functions/reference.xml:380
#, kde-format
msgid "Modifies a reference's position and dimension."
msgstr "Athraíonn sé suíomh agus toise tagartha."

#: functions/reference.xml:381
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"OFFSET(Reference reference; Integer rowOffset; Integer columnOffset; Integer "
"newHeight; Integer newWidth)"
msgstr ""
"FRÁIMHÍOCHÁN(TagairtTagairt; FritháireamhSraithSlánuimhir; "
"FritháireamhColúnSlánuimhir; AirdeNuaSlánuimhir; LeitheadNuaSlánuimhir)"

