#: functions/statistical.xml:31
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The AVEDEV() function calculates the average of the absolute deviations of a "
"data set from their mean."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm AVEDEV() meán na ndialltaí absalóideacha i dtacar sonraí "
"óna meán."

#: functions/statistical.xml:32
#, kde-format
msgid "AVEDEV(value;value;...)"
msgstr "AVEDEV(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid "AVEDEV(11.4;17.3;21.3;25.9;40.1) returns 7.84"
msgstr "Filleann AVEDEV(11.4;17.3;21.3;25.9;40.1) é seo: 7.84"

#: functions/statistical.xml:34
#, kde-format
msgid "AVEDEV(A1:A5) ..."
msgstr "AVEDEV(A1:A5) ..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:62
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The AVERAGE() function calculates the average of all the values given as "
"parameters. You can calculate the average of a range AVERAGE(A1:B5) or a "
"list of values like AVERAGE(12;5;12.5)."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm AVERAGE() meán na luachanna uile a thugtar mar "
"pharaiméadair. Is féidir leat meán raoin AVERAGE(A1:B5) nó liosta luachanna "
"cosúil le AVERAGE(12;5;12.5) a ríomh."

#: functions/statistical.xml:63
#, kde-format
msgid "AVERAGE(value;value;...)"
msgstr "AVERAGE(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:64
#, kde-format
msgid "AVERAGE(12;5;7) equals 8"
msgstr "Is ionann AVERAGE(12;5;7) agus 8"

#: functions/statistical.xml:65
#, kde-format
msgid "AVERAGE(12.5;2) equals 7.25"
msgstr "Filleann AVERAGE(12.5;2) é seo: 7.25"

#: functions/statistical.xml:77 functions/text.xml:447 functions/text.xml:451
#: functions/text.xml:455 functions/text.xml:459 functions/text.xml:463
#, kde-format
msgid "String values"
msgstr "Luachanna teaghráin"

#: functions/statistical.xml:81
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The AVERAGEA() calculates the average of the given arguments. Numbers, text "
"and logical values are included in the calculation too. If the cell contains "
"text or the argument evaluates to FALSE, it is counted as value zero (0). If "
"the argument evaluates to TRUE, it is counted as one (1). Note that empty "
"cells are not counted."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann AVERAGEA() meán na n-argóintí tugtha. Cuirtear uimhreacha, téacs "
"agus luachanna loighciúla san áireamh sa ríomh freisin. Má tá téacs sa chill "
"nó má mheastar go BRÉAGACH an argóint, meastar é mar luach nialasach (0). Má "
"mheastar go FÍOR an argóint, meastar é mar aon (1). Tabhair faoi deara nach "
"gcomhairtear cealla folamha."

#: functions/statistical.xml:82
#, kde-format
msgid "AVERAGEA(value;value;...)"
msgstr "AVERAGEA(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:83
#, kde-format
msgid "AVERAGEA(11.4;17.3;\"sometext\";25.9;40.1) equals 18.94"
msgstr "Is ionann AVERAGEA(11.4;17.3;\"sometext\";25.9;40.1) agus 18.94"

#: functions/statistical.xml:95 functions/statistical.xml:131
#: functions/statistical.xml:434 functions/statistical.xml:463
#: functions/statistical.xml:1679
#, kde-format
msgid "Alpha parameter"
msgstr "Paraiméadar Alfa"

#: functions/statistical.xml:99 functions/statistical.xml:135
#: functions/statistical.xml:438 functions/statistical.xml:467
#: functions/statistical.xml:1683
#, kde-format
msgid "Beta parameter"
msgstr "Paraiméadar béite"

#: functions/statistical.xml:103 functions/statistical.xml:139
#, kde-format
msgid "Start"
msgstr "Tosaigh"

#: functions/statistical.xml:107 functions/statistical.xml:143
#, kde-format
msgid "End"
msgstr "Deireadh"

#: functions/statistical.xml:111
#, kde-format
msgid "Cumulative"
msgstr "Carnach"

#: functions/statistical.xml:115
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BETADIST() function returns the cumulative beta probability density "
"function."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm BETADIST() an fheidhm dlús dóchúlachta béite carnach ar "
"ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:116
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The third and fourth parameters are optional. They set the lower and upper "
"bounds, otherwise defaulting to 0.0 and 1.0 respectively."
msgstr ""
"Is roghnacha an tríú agus an ceathrú paraiméadar. Socraíonn siad na "
"teorainneacha íochtaracha agus uachtaracha, agus murach sin bíonn siad "
"réamhshocraithe go 0.0 agus 1.0 faoi seach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:117
#, kde-format
msgid "BETADIST(number;alpha;beta;start;end;[cumulative=TRUE])"
msgstr "BETADIST(uimhir;alfa;béite;tosú;deireadh;[carnach=TRUE])"

#: functions/statistical.xml:118
#, kde-format
msgid "BETADIST(0.2859;0.2606;0.8105) equals 0.675444"
msgstr "Is ionann BETADIST(0.2859;0.2606;0.8105) agus 0.675444"

#: functions/statistical.xml:119
#, kde-format
msgid "BETADIST(0.2859;0.2606;0.8105;0.2;0.9) equals 0.537856"
msgstr "Is ionann BETADIST(0.2859;0.2606;0.8105;0.2;0.9) agus 0.537856"

#: functions/statistical.xml:147
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BETAINV() function returns the inverse of BETADIST(x;alpha;beta;a;b;"
"TRUE())."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm BETAINV() inbhéart BETADIST(x;alpha;beta;a;b;TRUE()) ar "
"ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:148
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The start and end parameters are optional. They set the lower and upper "
"bounds, otherwise defaulting to 0.0 and 1.0 respectively."
msgstr ""
"Is roghnacha iad na paraiméadair tosaigh agus deiridh. Socraíonn siad na "
"teorainneacha íochtaracha agus uachtaracha, agus murach sin bíonn siad "
"réamhshocraithe go 0.0 agus 1.0 faoi seach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:149
#, kde-format
msgid "BETAINV(number;alpha;beta [; start=0 [; end=1]])"
msgstr "BETAINV(uimhir;alfa;béite [; tosú=0 [;deireadh=1]])"

#: functions/statistical.xml:150
#, kde-format
msgid "BETADIST(BETAINV(0.1;3;4);3;4) equals 0.1"
msgstr "Is ionann BETADIST(BETAINV(0.1;3;4);3;4) agus 0.1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:151
#, kde-format
msgid "BETADIST(BETAINV(0.3;3;4);3;4) equals 0.3"
msgstr "Filleann BETADIST(BETAINV(0.3;3;4);3;4) é seo: 0.3"

#: functions/statistical.xml:164
#, kde-format
msgid "Degrees of freedom"
msgstr "Céimeanna saoirse"

#: functions/statistical.xml:168
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CHIDIST() function returns the probability value from the indicated Chi "
"square that a hypothesis is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm CHIDIST() an luach dóchúlachta ar ais ón gcearnóg Chi a "
"léirítear go bhfuil hipitéis deimhnithe."

#: functions/statistical.xml:169
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"CHIDIST compares the Chi square value to be given for a random sample that "
"is calculated from the sum of (observed value-expected value)^2/expected "
"value for all values with the theoretical Chi square distribution and "
"determines from this the probability of error for the hypothesis to be "
"tested."
msgstr ""
"Déanann CHIDIST comparáid idir an luach Chi-chearnógach atá le tabhairt do "
"shampla randamach a ríomhtar ó shuim (luach breathnaithe-luach ionchais)^2/"
"luach ionchais do na luachanna uile leis an dáileadh Chi-chearnógach "
"teoiriciúil agus cinneann sé ón méid seo an dóchúlacht earráide don hipitéis "
"atá le tástáil."

#: functions/statistical.xml:170
#, kde-format
msgid "CHIDIST(number;degrees_freedom)"
msgstr "CHIDIST(uimhir;céimeanna_saoirse)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:171
#, kde-format
msgid "CHIDIST(13.27;5) returns 0.021"
msgstr "Filleann CHIDIST(13.27;5) é seo: 0.021"

#: functions/statistical.xml:179 functions/statistical.xml:198
#: functions/statistical.xml:932 functions/statistical.xml:951
#, kde-format
msgid "Total number of elements"
msgstr "Líon iomlán na n-eilimintí"

#: functions/statistical.xml:183 functions/statistical.xml:202
#: functions/statistical.xml:955
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of elements to choose"
msgstr "Líon na n-eilimintí le roghnú"

#: functions/statistical.xml:187
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The COMBIN() function calculates the count of possible combinations. The "
"first parameter is the total count of elements. The second parameter is the "
"count of elements to choose. Both parameters should be positive and the "
"first parameter should not be less than the second. Otherwise the function "
"returns an error."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm COMBIN() líon na dteaglaim fhéideartha. Is é an chéad "
"pharaiméadar líon iomlán na n-eilimintí. Is é an dara paraiméadar líon na n-"
"eilimintí le roghnú. Ba chóir go mbeadh an dá pharaiméadar dearfach agus "
"níor chóir go mbeadh an chéad pharaiméadar níos lú ná an dara ceann. Seachas "
"sin, seolann an fheidhm earráid ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:188
#, kde-format
msgid "COMBIN(total;chosen)"
msgstr "COMBIN(iomlán;roghnaithe)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:189
#, kde-format
msgid "COMBIN(12;5) returns 792"
msgstr "Filleann COMBIN(12;5) é seo: 792"

#: functions/statistical.xml:190
#, kde-format
msgid "COMBIN(5;5) returns 1"
msgstr "Filleann COMBIN(5;5) é seo: 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:206
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The COMBINA() function calculates the count of possible combinations "
"allowing repetition. The first parameter is the total count of elements. The "
"second parameter is the count of elements to choose allowing repetition. "
"Both parameters should be positive and the first parameter should not be "
"less than the second. Otherwise the function returns an error."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm COMBINA() líon na dteaglaim fhéideartha a cheadaíonn "
"athrá. Is é an chéad pharaiméadar líon iomlán na n-eilimintí. Is é an dara "
"paraiméadar líon na n-eilimintí le roghnú a cheadaíonn athrá. Ba chóir go "
"mbeadh an dá pharaiméadar dearfach agus níor chóir go mbeadh an chéad "
"pharaiméadar níos lú ná an dara ceann. Seachas sin, seolann an fheidhm "
"earráid ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:207
#, kde-format
msgid "COMBINA(total;chosen)"
msgstr "COMBINA(iomlán;roghnaithe)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:208
#, kde-format
msgid "COMBINA(12;5) returns 4368"
msgstr "Tugann COMBINA(12;5) 4368 ar ais"

#: functions/statistical.xml:209
#, kde-format
msgid "COMBINA(5;5) returns 126"
msgstr "Tugann COMBINA(5;5) 126 ar ais"

#: functions/statistical.xml:217
#, kde-format
msgid "Level of the confidence interval"
msgstr "Leibhéal an eatraimh mhuiníne"

#: functions/statistical.xml:221
#, kde-format
msgid "Standard deviation for the total population"
msgstr "Diall caighdeánach don daonra iomlán"

#: functions/statistical.xml:225
#, kde-format
msgid "Size of the total population"
msgstr "Méid an daonra iomláin"

#: functions/statistical.xml:229
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CONFIDENCE() function returns the confidence interval for a population "
"mean."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm CONFIDENCE() an t-eatramh muiníne ar ais do mheán daonra."

#: functions/statistical.xml:230
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The alpha parameter must be between 0 and 1 (non-inclusive), stddev must be "
"positive and size must be greater or equal to 1."
msgstr ""
"Caithfidh an paraiméadar alfa a bheith idir 0 agus 1 (gan áireamh), "
"caithfidh stddev a bheith dearfach agus caithfidh an méid a bheith níos mó "
"ná nó cothrom le 1."

#: functions/statistical.xml:231
#, kde-format
msgid "CONFIDENCE(alpha;stddev;size)"
msgstr "MUINÍN(alfa;stddev;méid)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:232
#, kde-format
msgid "CONFIDENCE(0.05;1.5;100) equals 0.294059"
msgstr "Is ionann CONFIDENCE(0.05;1.5;100) agus 0.294059"

#: functions/statistical.xml:240 functions/statistical.xml:259
#: functions/statistical.xml:668 functions/statistical.xml:913
#: functions/statistical.xml:1144
#, kde-format
msgid "Cell range of values"
msgstr "Raon luachanna cealla"

#: functions/statistical.xml:244 functions/statistical.xml:263
#: functions/statistical.xml:917
#, kde-format
msgid "Second cell range of values"
msgstr "Dara raon cealla luachanna"

#: functions/statistical.xml:248
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CORREL() function calculates the correlation coefficient of two cell "
"ranges."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm CORREL() comhéifeacht comhghaolmhaireachta dhá raon "
"cealla."

#: functions/statistical.xml:249
#, kde-format
msgid "CORREL(range1; range2)"
msgstr "CORREL(raon1; raon2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:250
#, kde-format
msgid "CORREL(A1:A3; B1:B3)"
msgstr "CORREL(A1:A3; B1:B3)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:267
#, kde-format
msgid "The COVAR() function calculates the covariance of two cell ranges."
msgstr "Ríomhann an fheidhm COVAR() comhathraitheas dhá raon cealla."

#: functions/statistical.xml:268
#, kde-format
msgid "COVAR(range1; range2)"
msgstr "COVAR(raon1; raon2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:269
#, kde-format
msgid "COVAR(A1:A3; B1:B3)"
msgstr "COVAR(A1:A3; B1:B3)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:297
#, kde-format
msgid "The DEVSQ() function calculates the sum of squares of deviations."
msgstr "Ríomhann an fheidhm DEVSQ() suim chearnóg na ndialltachtaí."

#: functions/statistical.xml:298
#, kde-format
msgid "DEVSQ(value; value;...)"
msgstr "DEVSQ(luach; luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:299
#, kde-format
msgid "DEVSQ(A1:A5)"
msgstr "DEVSQ(A1:A5)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:300
#, kde-format
msgid "DEVSQ(21; 33; 54; 23) returns 684.75"
msgstr "Filleann DEVSQ(21; 33; 54; 23) é seo: 684.75"

#: functions/statistical.xml:312
#, kde-format
msgid "Lambda parameter"
msgstr "Paraiméadar lambda"

#: functions/statistical.xml:316 functions/statistical.xml:844
#: functions/statistical.xml:1011 functions/statistical.xml:1687
#, kde-format
msgid "0 = density, 1 = distribution"
msgstr "0 = dlús, 1 = dáileadh"

#: functions/statistical.xml:320
#, kde-format
msgid "The EXPONDIST() function returns the exponential distribution."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm EXPONDIST() an dáileadh easpónentach ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:321
#, kde-format
msgid "The lambda parameter must be positive."
msgstr "Caithfidh an paraiméadar lambda a bheith dearfach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:322 functions/statistical.xml:1017
#: functions/statistical.xml:1693
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Cumulative = 0 calculates the density function; cumulative = 1 calculates "
"the distribution."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann Carnach = 0 an fheidhm dlúis; ríomhann Carnach = 1 an dáileadh."

#: functions/statistical.xml:323
#, kde-format
msgid "EXPONDIST(number;lambda;cumulative)"
msgstr "EXPONDIST(uimhir;lambda;carnach)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:324
#, kde-format
msgid "EXPONDIST(3;0.5;0) equals 0.111565"
msgstr "Is ionann EXPONDIST(3;0.5;0) agus 0.111565"

#: functions/statistical.xml:325
#, kde-format
msgid "EXPONDIST(3;0.5;1) equals 0.776870"
msgstr "Is ionann EXPONDIST(3;0.5;1) agus 0.776870"

#: functions/statistical.xml:337 functions/statistical.xml:690
#, kde-format
msgid "Degrees of freedom 1"
msgstr "Céimeanna saoirse 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:341 functions/statistical.xml:694
#, kde-format
msgid "Degrees of freedom 2"
msgstr "Céimeanna saoirse 2"

#: functions/statistical.xml:345
#, kde-format
msgid "The FDIST() function returns the f-distribution."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm FDIST() an dáileadh-f ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:346
#, kde-format
msgid "FDIST(number;degrees_freedom_1;degrees_freedom_2)"
msgstr "FDIST(uimhir;céimeanna_saoirse_1;céimeanna_saoirse_2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:347
#, kde-format
msgid "FDIST(0.8;8;12) yields 0.61"
msgstr "Filleann FDIST(0.8;8;12) é seo: 0.61"

#: functions/statistical.xml:359
#, kde-format
msgid "Number r1"
msgstr "Uimhir r1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:363
#, kde-format
msgid "Number r2"
msgstr "Uimhir r2"

#: functions/statistical.xml:367
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FINV() function returns the unique non-negative number x such that "
"FDIST(x;r1;r2) = p."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm FINV() an uimhir uathúil neamh-dhiúltach x ar ais sa chaoi "
"is go mbeidh FDIST(x;r1;r2) = p."

#: functions/statistical.xml:368
#, kde-format
msgid "FINV(number; r1; r2)"
msgstr "FINV(uimhir; r1; r2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:369
#, kde-format
msgid "FDIST(FINV(0.1;3;4);3;4) equals 0.1"
msgstr "Is ionann FDIST(FINV(0.1;3;4);3;4) agus 0.1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:381
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FISHER() function returns the Fisher transformation for x and creates a "
"function close to a normal distribution."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm FISHER() an claochlú Fisher ar ais le haghaidh x agus "
"cruthaíonn sí feidhm atá gar do dháileadh gnáth."

#: functions/statistical.xml:382
#, kde-format
msgid "FISHER(number)"
msgstr "FISHER(uimhir)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:383
#, kde-format
msgid "FISHER(0.2859) equals 0.294096"
msgstr "Is ionann FISHER(0.2859) agus 0.294096"

#: functions/statistical.xml:384
#, kde-format
msgid "FISHER(0.8105) equals 1.128485"
msgstr "Is ionann FISHER(0.8105) agus 1.128485"

#: functions/statistical.xml:396
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FISHERINV() function returns the inverse of the Fisher transformation "
"for x and creates a function close to a normal distribution."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm FISHERINV() inbhéart an chlaochlaithe Fisher ar ais le "
"haghaidh x agus cruthaíonn sí feidhm atá gar do dháileadh gnáth."

#: functions/statistical.xml:397
#, kde-format
msgid "FISHERINV(number)"
msgstr "FISHERINV(uimhir)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:398
#, kde-format
msgid "FISHERINV(0.2859) equals 0.278357"
msgstr "Is ionann FISHERINV(0.2859) agus 0.278357"

#: functions/statistical.xml:399
#, kde-format
msgid "FISHERINV(0.8105) equals 0.669866"
msgstr "Is ionann FISHERINV(0.8105) agus 0.669866"

#: functions/statistical.xml:407
#, kde-format
msgid "Floating point values, that should be counted."
msgstr "Luachanna snámhphointe ba chóir a chur san áireamh."

#: functions/statistical.xml:411
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Floating point values, representing the upper boundaries of the intervals."
msgstr ""
"Luachanna snámhphointe, a léiríonn teorainneacha uachtaracha na n-eatramh."

#: functions/statistical.xml:415
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Counts the number of values for each interval given by the border values in "
"the second parameter."
msgstr ""
"Comhaireamhann sé líon na luachanna do gach eatramh a thugtar leis na "
"luachanna teorann sa dara paraiméadar."

#: functions/statistical.xml:420
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The values in the second parameter determine the upper boundaries of the "
"intervals.\n"
"               The intervals include the upper boundaries.\n"
"               The returned array is a column vector and has one more "
"element than the second parameter;\n"
"               the last element represents the number of all elements "
"greater than the last value in second parameter.\n"
"                   If the second parameter is empty, all values in the first "
"parameter are counted."
msgstr ""
"Cinneann na luachanna sa dara paraiméadar teorainneacha uachtaracha na n-"
"eatramh.\n"
"               Cuimsíonn na eatraimh na teorainneacha uachtaracha.\n"
"               Is veicteoir colún é an t-eagar a chuirtear ar ais agus tá "
"eilimint amháin níos mó ann ná an dara paraiméadar;\n"
"               Léiríonn an eilimint dheireanach líon na n-eilimintí uile atá "
"níos mó ná an luach deireanach sa dara paraiméadar.\n"
"                   Mura bhfuil an dara paraiméadar folamh, comhairtear na "
"luachanna uile sa chéad pharaiméadar."

#: functions/statistical.xml:421
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Note that the data must be in columns and since the result is a column-"
"array, use Ctrl+Alt+Enter (instead of just Enter) to display the array "
"elements in separate cells. "
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara go gcaithfidh na sonraí a bheith i gcolúin agus ós rud é "
"gur eagar colúin an toradh, bain úsáid as Ctrl+Alt+Enter (in ionad Enter "
"amháin) chun eilimintí an eagar a thaispeáint i gcealla ar leithligh. "

#: functions/statistical.xml:422
#, kde-format
msgid "FREQUENCY(Range data; Range bins)"
msgstr "MINICÍOCHT(Sonraí raoin; Boscaí raoin)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:442
#, kde-format
msgid "Cumulated flag"
msgstr "Bratach carntha"

#: functions/statistical.xml:446
#, kde-format
msgid "The GAMMADIST() function returns the gamma distribution."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm GAMMADIST() an dáileadh gáma ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:447
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If the last parameter (cumulated) is 0, it calculates the density function; "
"if it's 1, the distribution is returned."
msgstr ""
"Más ionann an paraiméadar deireanach (carnach) agus 0, ríomhann sé an "
"fheidhm dlúis; más ionann é agus 1, cuirtear an dáileadh ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:448
#, kde-format
msgid "The first three parameters must be positive."
msgstr "Caithfidh na chéad trí pharaiméadar a bheith dearfach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:449
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMADIST(number;alpha;beta;cumulated)"
msgstr "GAMMADIST(uimhir;alfa;béite;carnach)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:450
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMADIST(0.758;0.1;0.35;1) equals 0.995450"
msgstr "Is ionann GAMMADIST(0.758;0.1;0.35;1) agus 0.995450"

#: functions/statistical.xml:451
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMADIST(0.758;0.1;0.35;0) equals 0.017179"
msgstr "Is ionann GAMMADIST(0.758;0.1;0.35;0) agus 0.017179"

#: functions/statistical.xml:471
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The GAMMAINV() function returns the unique number x >= 0 such that "
"GAMMAINV(x;alpha;beta;TRUE()) = p."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm GAMMAINV() an uimhir uathúil x >= 0 ar ais sa chaoi is go "
"bhfuil GAMMAINV(x;alfa;béite;TRUE()) = p."

#: functions/statistical.xml:472
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMAINV(number;alpha;beta)"
msgstr "GAMMAINV(uimhir;alfa;béite)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:473
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMADIST(GAMMAINV(0.1;3;4);3;4) equals 0.1"
msgstr "Is ionann GAMMADIST(GAMMAINV(0.1;3;4);3;4) agus 0.1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:474
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMADIST(GAMMAINV(0.3;3;4);3;4) equals 0.3"
msgstr "Is ionann GAMMADIST(GAMMAINV(0.3;3;4);3;4) agus 0.3"

