"The GEOMEAN() function returns the geometric mean of the given arguments. "
"This is equal to the Nth root of the product of the terms."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm GEOMEAN() meán geoiméadrach na n-argóintí tugtha ar ais. "
"Is ionann é seo agus an fréamh N de thoradh na dtéarmaí."

