#, kde-format
msgid "Middle value in the normal distribution"
msgstr "Luach lár sa dáileadh gnáth"

#: functions/statistical.xml:871
#, kde-format
msgid "Standard deviation of the normal distribution"
msgstr "Diall caighdeánach an dáilte gnáth"

#: functions/statistical.xml:875
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The NORMINV() function returns the inverse of the normal cumulative "
"distribution. The number must be between 0 and 1 (non-inclusive) and STD "
"must be positive."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm NORMINV() inbhéart an dáilte charnaigh gnáth ar ais. "
"Caithfidh an uimhir a bheith idir 0 agus 1 (gan áireamh) agus caithfidh STD "
"a bheith dearfach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:876
#, kde-format
msgid "NORMINV(number;MV;STD)"
msgstr "NORMINV(uimhir;MV;STD)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:877
#, kde-format
msgid "NORMINV(0.9;63;5) equals 69.41"
msgstr "Is ionann NORMINV(0.9;63;5) agus 69.41"

#: functions/statistical.xml:885
#, kde-format
msgid "Value to which the standard normal distribution is calculated"
msgstr "Luach a ríomhtar an dáileadh gnáth caighdeánach chuige"

#: functions/statistical.xml:889
#, kde-format
msgid "The NORMSDIST() function returns the standard normal distribution."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm NORMSDIST() an dáileadh gnáth caighdeánach ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:890
#, kde-format
msgid "NORMSDIST(Number)"
msgstr "NORMSDIST(Uimhir)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:891
#, kde-format
msgid "NORMSDIST(1) equals 0.84"
msgstr "Is ionann NORMSDIST(1) agus 0.84"

#: functions/statistical.xml:903
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The NORMSINV() function returns the inverse of the standard normal "
"cumulative distribution. The number must be between 0 and 1 (non-inclusive)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm NORMSINV() inbhéart an dáilte carnaigh gnáth "
"chaighdeánaigh ar ais. Caithfidh an uimhir a bheith idir 0 agus 1 "
"(neamhchuimsitheach)."

#: functions/statistical.xml:904
#, kde-format
msgid "NORMSINV(Number)"
msgstr "NORMSINV(Uimhir)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:905
#, kde-format
msgid "NORMSINV(0.908789) returns 1.3333"
msgstr "Filleann NORMSINV(0.908789) é seo: 1.3333"

#: functions/statistical.xml:921
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The PEARSON() function calculates the correlation coefficient of two cell "
"ranges. It is the same as the CORREL function."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm PEARSON() comhéifeacht comhghaolmhaireachta dhá raon "
"cealla. Tá sé mar an gcéanna leis an fheidhm CORREL."

#: functions/statistical.xml:922
#, kde-format
msgid "PEARSON(range1; range2)"
msgstr "PEARSON(raon1; raon2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:923
#, kde-format
msgid "PEARSON(A1:A3; B1:B3)"
msgstr "PEARSON(A1:A3; B1:B3)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:936
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of elements to permutate"
msgstr "Líon na n-eilimintí le hathrú"

#: functions/statistical.xml:940
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The PERMUT() function returns the number of permutations. The first "
"parameter is the number of elements, and the second parameter is the number "
"of elements used in the permutation."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm PERMUT() líon na n-iomlaoidí ar ais. Is é an chéad "
"pharaiméadar líon na n-eilimintí, agus is é an dara paraiméadar líon na n-"
"eilimintí a úsáidtear sa iomlaoid."

#: functions/statistical.xml:941
#, kde-format
msgid "PERMUT(total;permutated)"
msgstr "PERMUT(iomlán;permutated)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:942
#, kde-format
msgid "PERMUT(8;5) equals 6720"
msgstr "Is ionann PERMUT(8;5) agus 6720"

#: functions/statistical.xml:943
#, kde-format
msgid "PERMUT(1;1) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann PERMUT(1;1) agus 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:959
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The PERMUTATIONA() function returns the number of ordered permutations when "
"allowing repetition. The first parameter is the number of elements, and the "
"second parameter is the number of elements to choose. Both parameters must "
"be positive."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm PERMUTATIONA() líon na n-iomlaoidí ordaithe ar ais nuair a "
"cheadaítear athrá. Is é an chéad pharaiméadar líon na n-eilimintí, agus is é "
"an dara paraiméadar líon na n-eilimintí le roghnú. Ní mór don dá "
"pharaiméadar a bheith dearfach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:960
#, kde-format
msgid "PERMUTATIONA(total;chosen)"
msgstr "PERMUTATIONA(iomlán;roghnaithe)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:961
#, kde-format
msgid "PERMUTATIONA(2,3) returns 8"
msgstr "Tugann PERMUTATIONA(2,3) 8 ar ais"

#: functions/statistical.xml:962
#, kde-format
msgid "PERMUTATIONA(0,0) returns 1"
msgstr "Tugann PERMUTATIONA(0,0) 1 ar ais"

#: functions/statistical.xml:970
#, kde-format
msgid "Range of values"
msgstr "Raon luachanna"

#: functions/statistical.xml:974
#, kde-format
msgid "The percentile value between 0 and 1, inclusive."
msgstr "An luach céatadáin idir 0 agus 1, san áireamh."

#: functions/statistical.xml:978
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The PERCENTILE() function returns the x-th sample percentile of data values "
"in Data. A percentile returns the scale value for a data series which goes "
"from the smallest (alpha=0) to the largest value (alpha=1) of a data series. "
"For alpha = 25%, the percentile means the first quartile; alpha = 50% is the "
"MEDIAN. Blank cells will be considered as a zero, and cells with text will "
"be ignored."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm PERCENTILE() an x-ú peircintíl samplach de luachanna "
"sonraí i Data ar ais. Tugann peircintíl an luach scála ar ais do shraith "
"sonraí a théann ón luach is lú (alfa=0) go dtí an luach is mó (alfa=1) de "
"shraith sonraí. I gcás alfa = 25%, ciallaíonn an peircintíl an chéad "
"cheathrú; is é alfa = 50% an MEÁN. Measfar cealla bána mar nialas, agus "
"déanfar neamhaird de chealla ina bhfuil téacs."

#: functions/statistical.xml:979
#, kde-format
msgid "PERCENTILE(data;alpha)"
msgstr "PERCENTÍL(sonraí;alfa)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:989
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The number for which the standard normal distribution is to be calculated"
msgstr "An uimhir a bhfuil an dáileadh gnáth caighdeánach le ríomh ina leith"

#: functions/statistical.xml:993
#, kde-format
