"The PHI() function returns value of the distribution function for a standard "
"normal distribution."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm PHI() luach na feidhme dáilte ar ais i gcás dáileadh gnáth "
"caighdeánach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:994
#, kde-format
msgid "PHI(value)"
msgstr "PHI(luach)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:995
#, kde-format
msgid "PHI(0.25) equals 0.386668"
msgstr "Is ionann PHI(0.25) agus 0.386668"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1007
#, kde-format
msgid "Lambda parameter (the middle value)"
msgstr "Paraiméadar lambda (luach láir)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1015
#, kde-format
msgid "The POISSON() function returns the Poisson distribution."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm POISSON() an dáileadh Poisson ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1016
#, kde-format
msgid "The lambda and number parameters must be positive."
msgstr "Caithfidh na paraiméadair lambda agus uimhreach a bheith dearfach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1018
#, kde-format
msgid "POISSON(number;lambda;cumulative)"
msgstr "POISSON(uimhir;lambda;carnach)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1019
#, kde-format
msgid "POISSON(60;50;0) equals 0.020105"
msgstr "Is ionann POISSON(60;50;0) agus 0.020105"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1020
#, kde-format
msgid "POISSON(60;50;1) equals 0.927840"
msgstr "Is ionann POISSON(60;50;1) agus 0.927840"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1032
#, kde-format
msgid "Data (array)"
msgstr "Sonraí (eagar)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1036
#, kde-format
msgid "Order"
msgstr "Ord"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1040
#, kde-format
msgid "The RANK() function returns the rank of a number in a list of numbers."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm RANK() rang uimhir i liosta uimhreacha ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1041
#, kde-format
msgid "Order specifies how to rank the numbers:"
msgstr "Sonraíonn an t-ord conas na huimhreacha a rangú:"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1042
#, kde-format
msgid "If 0 or omitted, Data is ranked in descending order."
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil 0 ann nó má fhágtar ar lár é, déantar na Sonraí a rangú in ord "
"íslitheach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1043
#, kde-format
msgid "If not 0, Data is ranked in ascending order."
msgstr "Mura 0 é, déantar Sonraí a rangú in ord ardaitheach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1044
#, kde-format
msgid "RANK(Value; Data; Order)"
msgstr "RANG(Luach; Sonraí; Ord)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1045
#, kde-format
msgid "RANK (2;{1;2;3}) equals 2"
msgstr "Is ionann RANK (2;{1;2;3}) agus 2"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1053
#, kde-format
msgid "known Y (array)"
msgstr "Y aitheanta (eagar)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1057
#, kde-format
msgid "known X (array)"
msgstr "X aitheanta (eagar)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1061
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The RSQ() function returns the square of the Pearson product moment "
"correlation coefficient through data points in known_y's and known_x's."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm RSQ() cearnóg chomhéifeacht comhghaolúcháin mhóimint "
"táirge Pearson ar ais trí phointí sonraí i known_y agus known_x."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1062
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If \"arrayY\" and \"arrayX\" are empty or have a different number of data "
"points, then #N/A is returned."
msgstr ""
"Más folamh iad \"array\" agus \"array\" nó má tá líon difriúil pointí sonraí "
"acu, cuirtear #N/A ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1063
#, kde-format
msgid "RSQ(known Y; known X)"
msgstr "RSQ(Y ar eolas; X ar eolas)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1087
#, kde-format
msgid "The SKEW() function returns an estimate for skewness of a distribution"
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm SKEW() meastachán ar ais ar chlaonadh dáilte"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1088
#, kde-format
msgid "SKEW(number; number2; ...)"
msgstr "SKEW(uimhir; uimhir2; ...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1089
#, kde-format
msgid "SKEW(range)"
msgstr "SKEW(raon)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1090
#, kde-format
msgid "SKEW(11.4; 17.3; 21.3; 25.9; 40.1) returns 0.9768"
msgstr "Filleann SKEW(11.4; 17.3; 21.3; 25.9; 40.1) é seo: 0.9768"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1115
#, kde-format
msgid "The SKEWP() function returns the population skewness of a distribution"
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm SKEWP() claonadh daonra dáilte ar ais"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1116
#, kde-format
msgid "SKEWP(number; number2; ...)"
msgstr "SKEWP(uimhir; uimhir2; ...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1117
#, kde-format
msgid "SKEWP(range)"
msgstr "SKEWP(raon)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1118
#, kde-format
msgid "SKEWP(11.4; 17.3; 21.3; 25.9; 40.1) returns 0.6552"
msgstr "Filleann SKEWP(11.4; 17.3; 21.3; 25.9; 40.1) é seo: 0.6552"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1135
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SLOPE() function calculates the slope of the linear regression line."
msgstr "Ríomhann an fheidhm SLOPE() fána na líne aischéimnithe líneach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1136
#, kde-format
msgid "SLOPE(y;x)"
msgstr "SLOPE(y;x)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1148
#, kde-format
msgid "Position (from the smallest)"
msgstr "Seasamh (ón gceann is lú)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1152
#, kde-format
msgid "The SMALL() function returns the k-th smallest value from the data set."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm SMALL() an k-ú luach is lú ón tacar sonraí ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1153
#, kde-format
msgid "SMALL(range; k)"
msgstr "SMALL(raon; k)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1154
#, kde-format
msgid "A1: 3, A2: 1, A3: 5 => SMALL(A1:A3; 1) returns 1"
msgstr "A1: 3, A2: 1, A3: 5 => Filleann SMALL(A1:A3; 1) é seo: 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1162
#, kde-format
msgid "Number to be normalized"
msgstr "Uimhir le normalú"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1166
#, kde-format
msgid "Mean of the distribution"
msgstr "Meán an dáilte"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1170
#, kde-format
msgid "Standard deviation"
msgstr "Diall caighdeánach"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1174
#, kde-format
msgid "The STANDARDIZE() function calculates a normalized value."
msgstr "Ríomhann an fheidhm STANDARDIZE() luach normalaithe."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1175
#, kde-format
msgid "STANDARDIZE(x; mean, stdev)"
msgstr "CAIGHDEÁNÚ(x; meán, stdev)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1176
#, kde-format
msgid "STANDARDIZE(4; 3; 7) returns 0.1429"
msgstr "Filleann STANDARDIZE(4; 3; 7) é seo: 0.1429"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1204
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The STDEV() function returns the estimate standard deviation based on a "
"sample. The standard deviation is a measure of how widely values are "
"dispersed from the average value."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm STDEV() an diall caighdeánach measta ar ais bunaithe ar "
"shampla. Is tomhas é an diall caighdeánach ar cé chomh leathan agus atá "
"luachanna scaipthe ón meánluach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1205
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEV(value;value;...)"
msgstr "STDEV(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1206
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEV(6;7;8) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann STDEV(6;7;8) agus 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1235
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The STDEVA() function returns the estimate standard deviation based on a "
"sample. The standard deviation is a measure of how widely values are "
"dispersed from the average value. If a referenced cell contains text or "
"contains the boolean value FALSE, it is counted as 0. If the boolean value "
"is TRUE it is counted as 1."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm STDEVA() an diall caighdeánach measta ar ais bunaithe ar "
"shampla. Is tomhas é an diall caighdeánach ar cé chomh leathan agus atá "
"luachanna scaipthe ón meánluach. Má tá téacs i gcill tagartha nó má tá an "
"luach booléanach FALSE inti, comhairtear é mar 0. Má tá an luach booléanach "
"FÍOR, comhairtear é mar 1."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1236
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVA(value;value;...)"
msgstr "STDEVA(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1237
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVA(6; 7; A1; 8) equals 1, if A1 is empty"
msgstr "Is ionann STDEVA(6; 7; A1; 8) agus 1, má tá A1 folamh"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1238
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVA(6; 7; A1; 8) equals 3.109, if A1 is TRUE"
msgstr "Is ionann STDEVA(6; 7; A1; 8) agus 3.109, má tá A1 fíor"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1268
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The STDEVP() function returns the standard deviation based on an entire "
"population"
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm STDEVP() an diall caighdeánach ar ais bunaithe ar dhaonra "
"iomlán"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1269
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVP(value;value;...)"
msgstr "STDEVP(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1270
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVP(6;7;8) equals 0.816497..."
msgstr "Is ionann STDEVP(6;7;8) agus 0.816497..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1299
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The STDEVPA() function returns standard deviation based on an entire "
"population. If a referenced cell contains text or contains the boolean value "
"FALSE, it is counted as 0. If the boolean value is TRUE it is counted as 1."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm STDEVPA() diall caighdeánach ar ais bunaithe ar dhaonra "
"iomlán. Má tá téacs i gcill tagartha nó má tá an luach booléanach FALSE "
"inti, meastar é mar 0. Má tá an luach booléanach FÍOR, meastar é mar 1."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1300
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVPA(value;value;...)"
msgstr "STDEVPA(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1301
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVPA(6; 7; A1; 8) equals 0.816497..., if A1 is empty"
msgstr "Is ionann STDEVPA(6; 7; A1; 8) agus 0.816497..., má tá A1 folamh"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1302
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVPA(6; 7; A1; 8) equals 2.69..., if A1 is TRUE"
msgstr "Is ionann STDEVPA(6; 7; A1; 8) agus 2.69..., más fíor A1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1303
#, kde-format
msgid "STDEVPA(6; 7; A1; 8) equals 3.11..., if A1 is FALSE"
msgstr "Is ionann STDEVPA(6; 7; A1; 8) agus 3.11..., má tá A1 BRÉAGACH"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1321
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The STEYX() function calculates the standard error of the predicted y value "
"for each x in the regression."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm STEYX() an earráid chaighdeánach den luach y tuartha do "
"gach x san aischéimniú."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1322
#, kde-format
msgid "STEYX(y;x)"
msgstr "STEYX(y;x)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1338 functions/statistical.xml:1342
#: functions/statistical.xml:1356 functions/statistical.xml:1360
#: functions/statistical.xml:1374 functions/statistical.xml:1378
#: functions/statistical.xml:1783 functions/statistical.xml:1787
#, kde-format
msgid "Value (array)"
msgstr "Luach (eagar)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1346
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUMPRODUCT() function (SUM(X*Y)) returns the sum of the product of these "
"values. The number of values in the two arrays should be equal. Otherwise "
"this function returns Err."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm SUMPRODUCT() (SUM(X*Y)) suim thoradh na luachanna seo ar "
"ais. Ba chóir go mbeadh líon na luachanna sna dhá eagar cothrom. Seachas "
"sin, tugann an fheidhm seo Err ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1347
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMPRODUCT(array1;array2)"
msgstr "SUMPRODUCT(eagar1;eagar2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1348
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMPRODUCT(A1:A2;B1:B2) with A1=2, A2=5, B1=3 and B2=5, returns 31"
msgstr ""
"Le A1=2, A2=5, B1=3 agus B2=5, filleann SUMPRODUCT(A1:A2;B1:B2) é seo: 31"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1364
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUMX2PY2() function (SUM(X^2+Y^2)) returns the sum of the squares of "
"these values. The number of values in the two arrays should be equal. "
"Otherwise this function returns Err."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm SUMX2PY2() (SUM(X^2+Y^2)) suim chearnóg na luachanna seo "
"ar ais. Ba chóir go mbeadh líon na luachanna sna dhá eagar cothrom. Seachas "
"sin, tugann an fheidhm seo Err ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1365
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMX2PY2(array1;array2)"
msgstr "SUMX2PY2(eagar1;eagar2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1366
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMX2PY2(A1:A2;B1:B2) with A1=2, A2=5, B1=3 and B2=5, returns 63"
msgstr ""
"Le A1=2, A2=5, B1=3 agus B2=5, filleann SUMX2PY2(A1:A2;B1:B2) é seo: 63"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1382
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUMX2MY2() function (SUM(X^2-Y^2)) returns the difference of the squares "
"of these values. The number of values in the two arrays should be equal. "
"Otherwise this function returns Err."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm SUMX2MY2() (SUM(X^2-Y^2)) difríocht chearnóg na luachanna "
"seo ar ais. Ba chóir go mbeadh líon na luachanna sna dhá eagar cothrom. "
"Seachas sin, tugann an fheidhm seo Err ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1383
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMX2MY2(array1;array2)"
msgstr "SUMX2MY2(eagar1;eagar2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1384
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMX2MY2(A1:A2;B1:B2) with A1=2, A2=5, B1=3 and B2=5, returns -5"
msgstr ""
"Le A1=2, A2=5, B1=3 agus B2=5, filleann SUMX2MY2(A1:A2;B1:B2) é seo: -5"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1396
#, kde-format
msgid "Degrees of freedom for the t-distribution"
msgstr "Céimeanna saoirse don dáileadh-t"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1400
#, kde-format
msgid "Mode (1 or 2)"
msgstr "Mód (1 nó 2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1404
#, kde-format
msgid "The TDIST() function returns the t-distribution."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm TDIST() an dáileadh-t ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1405
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Mode = 1 returns the one-tailed test, Mode = 2 returns the two-tailed test."
msgstr ""
"Tugann Mód = 1 an tástáil aontaobhach ar ais, tugann Mód = 2 an tástáil "
"dhétaobhach ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1406
#, kde-format
msgid "TDIST(number;degrees_freedom;mode)"
msgstr "TDIST(uimhir;céimeanna_saoirse;mód)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1407
#, kde-format
msgid "TDIST(12;5;1) returns 0.000035"
msgstr "Filleann TDIST(12;5;1) é seo: 0.000035"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1415
#, kde-format
msgid "KnownY"
msgstr "AitheantaY"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1419
#, kde-format
msgid "KnownX"
msgstr "AitheantaX"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1423
#, kde-format
msgid "NumberSequence newX"
msgstr "Nuacht Seicheamh Uimhreacha"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1427
#, kde-format
msgid "allowOffset"
msgstr "ceadaighFritháireamh"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1431
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TREND() function calculates a sequence of Y-values based on a linear "
"regression of known X- and Y-value pairs. For the input parameters, the user "
"must firstly select a cell-range containing the Y-values, followed by the "
"cell-range of the corresponding X-values. "
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm TREND() seicheamh de luachanna Y bunaithe ar aischéimniú "
"líneach péirí luachanna X agus Y aitheanta. Maidir leis na paraiméadair "
"ionchuir, ní mór don úsáideoir raon cealla ina bhfuil na luachanna Y a "
"roghnú ar dtús, agus ansin raon cealla na luachanna X comhfhreagracha. "

#: functions/statistical.xml:1432
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The line of best fit may be extrapolated to a different X-range, which is "
"specified as the 3rd parameter. However, the input X-range should be given "
"again if no extrapolation is required. "
msgstr ""
"Féadfar an líne is fearr a oireann a eastóscadh chuig raon-X difriúil, atá "
"sonraithe mar an 3ú paraiméadar. Mar sin féin, ba cheart an raon-X ionchuir "
"a thabhairt arís mura bhfuil aon eastóscadh ag teastáil. "

#: functions/statistical.xml:1433
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The regression line can be forced to intersect the origin (X=0, Y=0) by "
"setting the 4th parameter, allowOffset, to FALSE or 0. Setting this "
"parameter to TRUE or 1 (the default) allows the best-fit line to intersect "
"the vertical axis at a non-zero value of Y. "
msgstr ""
"Is féidir an líne aischéimnithe a chur iallach chun an bunús (X=0, Y=0) a "
"thrasnú tríd an 4ú paraiméadar, allowOffset, a shocrú go FALSE nó 0. Trí an "
"paraiméadar seo a shocrú go TRUE nó 1 (an réamhshocrú), ceadaítear don líne "
"is fearr a oireann an ais ingearach a thrasnú ag luach neamh-nialasach de Y. "

#: functions/statistical.xml:1434
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Note that since the result of this function is a row of calculated Y-values, "
"plotting the data will be facilitated if the X- and Y- values are also in "
"rows, rather than columns."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara, ós rud é gur sraith de luachanna Y ríofa toradh na "
"feidhme seo, go mbeidh sé níos éasca na sonraí a phlotaáil má tá na "
"luachanna X agus Y i sraitheanna seachas i gcolúin freisin."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1435
#, kde-format
msgid "Constraints: COUNT(knownY) = COUNT(knownX)."
msgstr "Srianta: COUNT(ar a dtugtarY) = COUNT(ar a dtugtarX)."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1436
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Since the result is an array, use Ctrl+Alt+Enter (instead of just Enter) to "
"display the values in separate cells."
msgstr ""
"Ós rud é gur eagar an toradh, bain úsáid as Ctrl+Alt+Enter (in ionad Enter "
"amháin) chun na luachanna a thaispeáint i gcealla ar leithligh."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1437
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"TREND(known Y-range; [known X-range; [new X-range; [allowOffset=TRUE/"
"FALSE]]])"
msgstr ""
"TREND(raon Y aitheanta; [raon X aitheanta; [raon X nua; [allowOffset=FÍOR/"
"BRÉAGACH]]])"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1448
#, kde-format
msgid "dataSet"
msgstr "tacarSonraí"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1452
#, kde-format
msgid "cutOffFraction"
msgstr "codánScoite"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1456
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TRIMMEAN() function calculates the mean of a data set with the smallest "
"and largest values omitted to eliminate possible outliers. The total "
"fraction of measurements which are to be excluded is set by the second "
"parameter (cutOffFraction)."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm TRIMMEAN() meán tacair sonraí agus na luachanna is lú "
"agus is mó fágtha ar lár chun eisceachtaí féideartha a dhíchur. Socraítear "
"an codán iomlán de na tomhais atá le heisiamh leis an dara paraiméadar "
"(cutOffFraction)."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1457
#, kde-format
msgid "TRIMMEAN(dataSet; cutOffFraction)"
msgstr "TRIMMEAN(tacarSonraí; codánScoite)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1468
#, kde-format
msgid "x (array) The set of observed data for the first condition."
msgstr "x (eagar) An tacar sonraí breathnaithe don chéad choinníoll."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1472
#, kde-format
msgid "y (array) The set of observed data for the second condition."
msgstr "y (eagar) An tacar sonraí breathnaithe don dara coinníoll."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1476
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"mode Whether to look up 1-tailed (mode = 1) or 2-tailed (mode = 2) "
"probability for t."
msgstr ""
"mód Cibé acu ar cheart dóchúlacht aon-taobhach (mód = 1) nó dóchúlacht dhá-"
"taobhach (mód = 2) a chuardach le haghaidh t."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1480
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"type The type of t-test to perform. Set this to 1 for a paired t-test, 2 or "
"3 for an unpaired t-test."
msgstr ""
"cineál An cineál tástála-t atá le déanamh. Socraigh seo go 1 le haghaidh "
"tástála-t péireáilte, 2 nó 3 le haghaidh tástála-t neamhphéireáilte."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1484
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TTEST() function calculates the probability of a t-test given two ranges "
"of data to compare."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm TTEST() dóchúlacht tástála-t nuair a thugtar dhá raon "
"sonraí le comparáid."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1485
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A t-test compares two sets of data and establishes the likelihood that any "
"difference between the two is caused by some variable having an effect. For "
"example, given two sets of data, one containing the speed at which 30 tall "
"people can run and the other containing the speed at which 30 short people "
"can run, a t-test can tell you how likely it is that any speed difference "
"between the two groups of people is due to their height."
msgstr ""
"Déanann tástáil-t comparáid idir dhá shraith sonraí agus socraíonn sé an "
"dóchúlacht go bhfuil aon difríocht eatarthu mar gheall ar athróg éigin a "
"bhfuil tionchar aici. Mar shampla, i gcás dhá shraith sonraí, ceann ina "
"bhfuil an luas ag a bhféadfadh 30 duine ard rith agus an ceann eile ina "
"bhfuil an luas ag a bhféadfadh 30 duine gearr rith, is féidir le tástáil-t a "
"insint duit cé chomh dóchúil is atá sé go bhfuil aon difríocht luais idir an "
"dá ghrúpa daoine mar gheall ar a n-airde."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1486
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The mode parameter is used to indicate whether you require the difference "
"between the two data sets to be in a specific direction or not. For example, "
"if we are predicting that tall people will be able to run faster than short "
"people, we would use a one-tailed test (mode = 1); however, if we are "
"predicting that one group will be able to run faster than the other but not "
"which one will actually be fastest, we would use a two-tailed test (mode = "
"2)."
msgstr ""
"Úsáidtear an paraiméadar mód chun a léiriú an bhfuil gá agat leis an "
"difríocht idir an dá shraith sonraí a bheith i dtreo ar leith nó nach "
"bhfuil. Mar shampla, má táimid ag tuar go mbeidh daoine arda in ann rith "
"níos tapúla ná daoine gearra, úsáidfimis tástáil aontaobhach (mód = 1); "
"áfach, má táimid ag tuar go mbeidh grúpa amháin in ann rith níos tapúla ná "
"an grúpa eile ach ní cé acu is tapúla i ndáiríre, úsáidfimis tástáil "
"dhétaobhach (mód = 2)."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1487
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Paired tests (type = 1, see Syntax below) are only suitable when both sets "
"of data values are drawn from the same source (i.e. each source of data has "
"provided an item in the first data range and an item in the second data "
"range). In the running speed example, this is impossible since one person "
"cannot be both short and tall: each person can only provide data for one "
"group or the other. In such cases, where the values in each data set are "
"drawn from different sources, an unpaired t-test is appropriate (type = 2 or "
"type = 3). For unpaired t-tests, the two data ranges need not be equally "
"sized; for paired t-tests the two ranges are required to contain the same "
"number of cells."
msgstr ""
"Ní bhíonn tástálacha péireáilte (cineál = 1, féach Comhréir thíos) oiriúnach "
"ach amháin nuair a tharraingítear an dá shraith luachanna sonraí ón bhfoinse "
"chéanna (i.e. tá mír sa chéad raon sonraí agus mír sa dara raon sonraí "
"curtha ar fáil ag gach foinse sonraí). Sa sampla luas reatha, ní féidir é "
"seo a dhéanamh ós rud é nach féidir le duine amháin a bheith gearr agus ard "
"araon: ní féidir le gach duine sonraí a sholáthar ach do ghrúpa amháin nó "
"don ghrúpa eile. I gcásanna den sórt sin, áit a dtarraingítear na luachanna "
"i ngach sraith sonraí ó fhoinsí éagsúla, is iomchuí tástáil-t "
"neamhphéireáilte (cineál = 2 nó cineál = 3). I gcás tástálacha-t "
"neamhphéireáilte, ní gá go mbeadh an dá raon sonraí den mhéid chéanna; i "
"gcás tástálacha-t péireáilte, ní mór go mbeadh an líon céanna cealla sa dá "
"raon."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1488
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When your sets of data values are not drawn from the same source, choosing "
"the appropriate type of unpaired test depends upon the variance within each "
"of your two samples. If the variances of the two samples are similar, you "
"can use an unpaired t-test for samples with similar variances (type = 2); "
"where the variances are not sufficiently similar you must use an unpaired t-"
"test for samples with differing variances (type = 3)."
msgstr ""
"Nuair nach bhfuil do shraitheanna luachanna sonraí tarraingthe ón bhfoinse "
"chéanna, braitheann rogha an chineáil chuí tástála neamhphéireáilte ar an "
"athraitheas laistigh de gach ceann de do dhá shampla. Má tá athraitheas an "
"dá shampla cosúil, is féidir leat tástáil-t neamhphéireáilte a úsáid le "
"haghaidh samplaí a bhfuil athraitheas comhchosúil acu (cineál = 2); i gcás "
"nach bhfuil na hathruithe sách cosúil, ní mór duit tástáil-t "
"neamhphéireáilte a úsáid le haghaidh samplaí a bhfuil athraitheas difriúla "
"acu (cineál = 3)."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1489
#, kde-format
msgid "TTEST(x; y; mode; type)"
msgstr "TTEST(x; y; mód; cineál)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1518
#, kde-format
msgid "The VAR() function calculates the variance based on a sample."
msgstr "Ríomhann an fheidhm VAR() an athraitheas bunaithe ar shampla."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1519
#, kde-format
msgid "VAR(value;value;...)"
msgstr "VAR(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1520
#, kde-format
msgid "VAR(12;5;7) equals 13"
msgstr "Is ionann VAR(12;5;7) agus 13"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1521
#, kde-format
msgid "VAR(15;80;3) equals 1716.333..."
msgstr "Is ionann VAR(15;80;3) agus 1716.333..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1522
#, kde-format
msgid "VAR(6;7;8) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann VAR(6;7;8) agus 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1554
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The VARA() function calculates the variance based on a sample allowing "
"numbers, text and logical values to be included in the calculation, too. If "
"the cell contains text or the argument evaluates to FALSE, it is counted as "
"value zero (0). If the argument evaluates to TRUE, it is counted as one (1). "
"Note that empty cells are not counted."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm VARA() an athraitheas bunaithe ar shampla a cheadaíonn "
"uimhreacha, téacs agus luachanna loighciúla a áireamh sa ríomh freisin. Má "
"tá téacs sa chill nó má mheastar go BRÉAGACH an argóint, comhairtear é mar "
"luach nialas (0). Má mheastar go FÍOR an argóint, comhairtear é mar aon (1). "
"Tabhair faoi deara nach gcomhairtear cealla folamha."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1555
#, kde-format
msgid "VARA(value;value;...)"
msgstr "VARA(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1556
#, kde-format
msgid "VARA(12;5;7) equals 13"
msgstr "Is ionann VARA(12;5;7) agus 13"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1557
#, kde-format
msgid "VARA(15;80;3) equals 1716.333..."
msgstr "Is ionann VARA(15;80;3) agus 1716.333..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1558
#, kde-format
msgid "VARA(6;7;8) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann VARA(6;7;8) agus 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1589
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The VARIANCE() function calculates the variance based on a sample. It is the "
"same as the VAR function."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm VARIANCE() an athraitheas bunaithe ar shampla. Tá sé mar "
"an gcéanna leis an fheidhm VAR."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1590
#, kde-format
msgid "VARIANCE(value;value;...)"
msgstr "VARIANCE(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1591
#, kde-format
msgid "VARIANCE(12;5;7) equals 13"
msgstr "Is ionann VARIANCE(12;5;7) agus 13"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1592
#, kde-format
msgid "VARIANCE(15;80;3) equals 1716.333..."
msgstr "Is ionann VARIANCE(15;80;3) agus 1716.333..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1593
#, kde-format
msgid "VARIANCE(6;7;8) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann VARIANCE(6;7;8) agus 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1625
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The VARP() function calculates the variance based on an entire population."
msgstr "Ríomhann an fheidhm VARP() an athraitheas bunaithe ar dhaonra iomlán."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1626
#, kde-format
msgid "VARP(value;value;...)"
msgstr "VARP(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1627
#, kde-format
msgid "VARP(12;5;7) equals 8.666..."
msgstr "Is ionann VARP(12;5;7) agus 8.666..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1628
#, kde-format
msgid "VARP(15;80;3) equals 1144.22..."
msgstr "Is ionann VARP(15;80;3) agus 1144.22..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1629
#, kde-format
msgid "VARP(6;7;8) equals 0.6666667..."
msgstr "Is ionann VARP(6;7;8) agus 0.6666667..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1660
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The VARPA() function calculates the variance based on an entire population. "
"Text and boolean values that evaluate to FALSE are counted as 0, boolean "
"value that evaluate to TRUE are counted as 1. Empty cells are not counted."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm VARPA() an athraitheas bunaithe ar dhaonra iomlán. "
"Comhairtear luachanna téacs agus booléacha a mheastar a bheith BRÉAGACH mar "
"0, agus comhairtear luachanna booléacha a mheastar a bheith FÍOR mar 1. Ní "
"chomhairtear cealla folamha."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1661
#, kde-format
msgid "VARPA(value;value;...)"
msgstr "VARPA(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1662
#, kde-format
msgid "VARPA(12;5;7) equals 8.666..."
msgstr "Is ionann VARPA(12;5;7) agus 8.666..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1663
#, kde-format
msgid "VARPA(15;80;3) equals 1144.22..."
msgstr "Is ionann VARPA(15;80;3) agus 1144.22..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1664
#, kde-format
msgid "VARPA(6;7;8) equals 0.6666667..."
msgstr "Is ionann VARPA(6;7;8) agus 0.6666667..."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1691
#, kde-format
msgid "The WEIBULL() function returns the Weibull distribution."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm WEIBULL() an dáileadh Weibull ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1692
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The alpha and beta parameters must be positive, the number (first parameter) "
"must be non-negative."
msgstr ""
"Ní mór do na paraiméadair alfa agus béite a bheith dearfach, ní mór don "
"uimhir (an chéad pharaiméadar) a bheith neamh-dhiúltach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1694
#, kde-format
msgid "WEIBULL(number;alpha;beta;cumulative)"
msgstr "WEIBULL(uimhir;alfa;béite;carnach)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1695
#, kde-format
msgid "WEIBULL(2;1;1;0) equals 0.135335"
msgstr "Is ionann WEIBULL(2;1;1;0) agus 0.135335"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1696
#, kde-format
msgid "WEIBULL(2;1;1;1) equals 0.864665"
msgstr "Is ionann WEIBULL(2;1;1;1) agus 0.864665"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1704
#, kde-format
msgid "x (array)"
msgstr "x (eagar)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1708
#, kde-format
msgid "mean"
msgstr "meán"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1712
#, kde-format
msgid "standardDeviation"
msgstr "diallCaighdeánach"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1716
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ZTEST() function calculates the two tailed probability of a z-test with "
"normal distribution."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm ZTEST() an dóchúlacht dhá thaobhach de thástáil z le "
"dáileadh gnáth."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1717
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Performs a test of the null hypothesis, that the sample is a true sample of "
"a normally distributed random variable with mean, mean, and standard "
"deviation, sigma (standardDeviation). A return value of 1 indicates, that "
"the null hypothesis is rejected, i.e. the sample is not a random sample of "
"the normal distribution. If sigma is omitted, it is estimated from sample, "
"using STDEV."
msgstr ""
"Déanann tástáil ar an hipitéis nialasach, go bhfuil an sampla ina "
"fhíorshampla d'athróg randamach dáilte go gnáth le meán, meán, agus diall "
"caighdeánach, sigma (standardDeviation). Léiríonn luach fillte de 1 go "
"ndiúltaítear don hipitéis nialasach, i.e. nach sampla randamach den dáileadh "
"gnáth an sampla. Mura gcuirtear sigma san áireamh, meastar é ón sampla, ag "
"baint úsáide as STDEV."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1719
#, kde-format
msgid "ZTEST(x; mean; standardDeviation)"
msgstr "ZTEST(x; meán; diallCaighdeánach)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1772
#, kde-format
msgid "The BINO() function returns the binomial distribution."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm BINO() an dáileadh déthéarmach ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1773
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The first parameter is the number of trials, the second parameter is the "
"number of successes, and the third is the probability of success. The number "
"of trials should be greater than the number of successes and the probability "
"should be smaller or equal to 1."
msgstr ""
"Is é an chéad pharaiméadar líon na dtrialacha, is é an dara paraiméadar líon "
"na rath, agus is é an tríú paraiméadar dóchúlacht an rath. Ba chóir go "
"mbeadh líon na dtrialacha níos mó ná líon na rath agus ba chóir go mbeadh an "
"dóchúlacht níos lú ná nó cothrom le 1."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1774
#, kde-format
msgid "BINO(trials;success;prob_of_success)"
msgstr "BINO(trialacha;rath;dóchúlacht_rathúlachta)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1775
#, kde-format
msgid "BINO(12;9;0.8) returns 0.236223201"
msgstr "Filleann BINO(12;9;0.8) é seo: 0.236223201"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1791
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUMXMY2() function (SUM((X-Y)^2)) returns the square of the differences "
"of these values. The number of values in the two arrays should be equal. "
"Otherwise this function returns Err."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm SUMXMY2() (SUM((X-Y)^2)) cearnóg na ndifríochtaí idir na "
"luachanna seo ar ais. Ba chóir go mbeadh líon na luachanna sna dhá eagar "
"cothrom. Seachas sin, tugann an fheidhm seo Err ar ais."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1792
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMXMY2(array1;array2)"
msgstr "SUMXMY2(eagar1;eagar2)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1793
#, kde-format
msgid "SUMXMY2(A1:A2;B1:B2) with A1=2, A2=5, B1=3 and B2=5, returns 1"
msgstr "Le A1=2, A2=5, B1=3 agus B2=5, filleann SUMXMY2(A1:A2;B1:B2) é seo: 1"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1809
#, kde-format
msgid "Probability of failure"
msgstr "Dóchúlacht teipe"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1813
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The INVBINO() function returns the negative binomial distribution. The first "
"parameter is the number of trials, the second parameter is the number of "
"failures, and the third is the probability of failure. The number of trials "
"should be larger than the number of failures and the probability should be "
"smaller or equal to 1."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm INVBINO() an dáileadh déthéarmach diúltach ar ais. Is é an "
"chéad pharaiméadar líon na dtrialacha, is é an dara paraiméadar líon na "
"dteipeanna, agus is é an tríú paraiméadar dóchúlacht teipe. Ba chóir go "
"mbeadh líon na dtrialacha níos mó ná líon na dteipeanna agus ba chóir go "
"mbeadh an dóchúlacht níos lú ná nó cothrom le 1."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1814
#, kde-format
msgid "INVBINO(trials;failure;prob_of_failure)"
msgstr "INVBINO(trialacha;teip;dóchúlacht teipe)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1815
#, kde-format
msgid "INVBINO(12;3;0.2) returns 0.236223201"
msgstr "Filleann INVBINO(12;3;0.2) é seo: 0.236223201"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1827
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The GAMMALN() function returns the natural logarithm of the gamma function: "
"G(x). The number parameter must be positive."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm GAMMALN() logartam nádúrtha na feidhme gama ar ais: G(x). "
"Caithfidh an paraiméadar uimhreach a bheith dearfach."

#: functions/statistical.xml:1828
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMALN(Number)"
msgstr "GAMMALN(Uimhir)"

#: functions/statistical.xml:1829
#, kde-format
msgid "GAMMALN(2) returns 0"
msgstr "Filleann GAMMALN(2) é seo: 0"

#: functions/text.xml:15 functions/text.xml:34
#, kde-format
msgid "Decimals"
msgstr "Deachúlacha"

#: functions/text.xml:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The DOLLAR() function converts a number to text using currency format, with "
"the decimals rounded to the specified place. Although the name is DOLLAR, "
"this function will do the conversion according to the current locale."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm DOLLAR() uimhir a thiontú go téacs ag baint úsáide as "
"formáid airgeadra, agus na deachúlacha slánaithe go dtí an áit shonraithe. "
"Cé gurb é DOLLAR an t-ainm, déanfaidh an fheidhm seo an tiontú de réir an "
"tslí reatha."

#: functions/text.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid "DOLLAR(number;decimals)"
msgstr "DOLLAR(uimhir;deachúlacha)"

#: functions/text.xml:21
#, kde-format
msgid "DOLLAR(1403.77) returns \"$ 1,403.77\""
msgstr "Filleann DOLLAR(1403.77) é seo: \"$ 1,403.77\""

#: functions/text.xml:22
#, kde-format
msgid "DOLLAR(-0.123;4) returns \"$-0.1230\""
msgstr "Filleann DOLLAR(-0.123;4) é seo: \"$-0.1230\""

#: functions/text.xml:38
#, kde-format
msgid "No_commas"
msgstr "Gan_comhóga"

#: functions/text.xml:42
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FIXED() function rounds a number to the specified number of decimals, "
"formats the number in decimal format string, and returns the result as text. "
"If decimals is negative, number is rounded to the left of the decimal point. "
"If you omit decimals, it is assumed to be 2. If optional parameter no_commas "
"is True, thousand separators will not show up."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm FIXED() uimhir a shlánú go dtí an líon deachúlacha "
"sonraithe, formáidíonn sí an uimhir i bhformáid deachúlach teaghrán, agus "
"tugann sí an toradh ar ais mar théacs. Más diúltach an deachúlacha, déantar "
"an uimhir a shlánú go dtí an taobh clé den phointe deachúlach. Má fhágann tú "
"deachúlacha ar lár, glactar leis go bhfuil sé 2. Mura bhfuil an paraiméadar "
"roghnach no_commas fíor, ní thaispeánfar deighilteoirí míle."

#: functions/text.xml:43
#, kde-format
msgid "FIXED(number;decimals;no_commas)"
msgstr "SOCRAITHE(uimhir;deachúlacha;gan_comhaí)"

#: functions/text.xml:44
#, kde-format
msgid "FIXED(1234.567;1) returns \"1,234.6\""
msgstr "Filleann FIXED(1234.567;1) é seo: \"1,234.6\""

#: functions/text.xml:45
#, kde-format
msgid "FIXED(1234.567;1;FALSE) returns \"1234.6\""
msgstr "Filleann FIXED(1234.567;1;FALSE) é seo: \"1234.6\""

#: functions/text.xml:46
#, kde-format
msgid "FIXED(44.332) returns \"44.33\""
msgstr "Filleann FIXED(44.332) é seo: \"44.33\""

#: functions/text.xml:54
#, kde-format
msgid "Text for which you want to substitute"
msgstr "Téacs ar mhaith leat a chur ina ionad"

#: functions/text.xml:58
#, kde-format
msgid "Part of text you want to replace"
msgstr "Cuid den téacs is mian leat a ionadú"

#: functions/text.xml:62
#, kde-format
msgid "New text which will be replacement"
msgstr "Téacs le cur ina ionad"

#: functions/text.xml:66
#, kde-format
msgid "Which occurrence to replace"
msgstr "Cén teagmhas le cur ina áit"

#: functions/text.xml:70
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SUBSTITUTE() substitutes new_text for old_text in a text string. If "
"instance_num is specified, only that instance of old_text is replaced. "
"Otherwise, every occurrence of old_text is changed to new_text. Use "
"SUBSTITUTE when you want to replace specific text, use REPLACE when you want "
"to replace any text that occurs in a specific location."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an SUBSTITUTE() téacs_nua in ionad sean_théacs i dtéacs. Má "
"shonraítear uimhir_instance, ní chuirtear ach an sampla sin de shean_théacs "
"ina áit. Seachas sin, athraítear gach uair a tharlaíonn sean_théacs go "
"téacs_nua. Bain úsáid as SUBSTITUTE nuair is mian leat téacs ar leith a "
"athsholáthar, bain úsáid as REPLACE nuair is mian leat aon téacs a "
"tharlaíonn i suíomh ar leith a athsholáthar."

#: functions/text.xml:71
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBSTITUTE(text; old_text; new_text; instance_num)"
msgstr "IONADAIGH(téacs; seantéacs; téacs nua; uimhir_chás)"

#: functions/text.xml:72
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBSTITUTE(\"Cost Data\";\"Cost\";\"Sales\") returns \"Sales Data\""
msgstr ""
"Filleann SUBSTITUTE(\"Cost Data\";\"Cost\";\"Sales\") é seo: \"Sales Data\""

#: functions/text.xml:73
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBSTITUTE(\"Qtr 1, 2001\";\"1\";\"3\";1) returns \"Qtr 3, 2001\""
msgstr ""
"Filleann SUBSTITUTE(\"Qtr 1, 2001\";\"1\";\"3\";1) é seo: \"Qtr 3, 2001\""

#: functions/text.xml:74
#, kde-format
msgid "SUBSTITUTE(\"Qtr 1, 2001\";\"1\";\"3\";4) returns \"Qtr 3, 2003\""
msgstr ""
"Filleann SUBSTITUTE(\"Qtr 1, 2001\";\"1\";\"3\";4) é seo: \"Qtr 3, 2003\""

#: functions/text.xml:86 functions/text.xml:114 functions/text.xml:289
#: functions/text.xml:320
#, kde-format
msgid "The text you want to find"
msgstr "Téacs le lorg"

#: functions/text.xml:90 functions/text.xml:118 functions/text.xml:293
#: functions/text.xml:324
#, kde-format
msgid "The text which may contain find_text"
msgstr "An téacs a d'fhéadfadh aimsigh_téacs a bheith ann"

#: functions/text.xml:94
#, kde-format
msgid "Specified index to start the search"
msgstr "Innéacs sonraithe chun an cuardach a thosú"

#: functions/text.xml:98
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SEARCH() function finds one text string (find_text) within another text "
"string (within_text) and returns the number of the starting point of "
"find_text, from the leftmost character of within_text."
msgstr ""
"Aimsíonn an fheidhm SEARCH() teaghrán téacs amháin (find_text) laistigh de "
"theaghrán téacs eile (within_text) agus tugann sí uimhir phointe tosaigh "
"find_text ar ais, ón gcarachtar is faide ar chlé de within_text."

#: functions/text.xml:99 functions/text.xml:127
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can use wildcard characters, question mark (?) and asterisk (*). A "
"question mark matches any single character, an asterisk matches any "
"sequences of characters."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat carachtair fhiáine, comhartha ceiste (?) agus réalta (*) a "
"úsáid. Comhfhreagraíonn comhartha ceiste d’aon charachtar aonair, agus "
"comhfhreagraíonn réalta d’aon seicheamh carachtar."

#: functions/text.xml:100
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Parameter start_num specifies the character at which to start the search. "
"The first character is character number 1. If start_num is omitted, it is "
"assumed to be 1. SEARCH does not distinguish between uppercase and lowercase "
"letters."
msgstr ""
"Sonraíonn an paraiméadar start_num an carachtar ag a dtosófar an cuardach. "
"Is é an chéad charachtar uimhir charachtair 1. Mura bhfágtar start_num ar "
"lár, glactar leis gurb é 1 é. Ní dhéanann SEARCH idirdhealú idir litreacha "
"móra agus beaga."

#: functions/text.xml:101
#, kde-format
msgid "SEARCH(find_text;within_text;start_num)"
msgstr "CUARDAIGH(aimsigh_téacs;laistigh_téacs;uimhir_túsaigh)"

#: functions/text.xml:102
#, kde-format
msgid "SEARCH(\"e\";\"Statements\";6) returns 7"
msgstr "Filleann SEARCH(\"e\";\"Statements\";6) é seo: 7"

#: functions/text.xml:103
#, kde-format
msgid "SEARCH(\"margin\";\"Profit Margin\") returns 8"
msgstr "Filleann SEARCH(\"margin\";\"Profit Margin\") é seo: 8"

#: functions/text.xml:122
#, kde-format
msgid "Specified byte position to start the search"
msgstr "Suíomh beart sonraithe chun an cuardach a thosú"

#: functions/text.xml:126
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SEARCHB() function finds one text string (find_text) within another text "
"string (within_text) and returns the number of the starting point of "
"find_text, from the leftmost character of within_text using byte positions."
msgstr ""
"Aimsíonn an fheidhm SEARCHB() teaghrán téacs amháin (find_text) laistigh de "
"theaghrán téacs eile (within_text) agus tugann sí uimhir phointe tosaigh "
"find_text ar ais, ón gcarachtar is faide ar chlé de within_text ag baint "
"úsáide as suíomhanna beart."

#: functions/text.xml:128
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Parameter BytePosition specifies the character at which to start the search. "
"The first character is character number 2. If BytePosition is omitted, it is "
"assumed to be 2. SEARCHB does not distinguish between uppercase and "
"lowercase letters."
msgstr ""
"Sonraíonn an paraiméadar BytePosition an carachtar ag a dtosófar an "
"cuardach. Is é an chéad charachtar uimhir 2. Mura bhfágtar BytePosition ar "
"lár, glactar leis gurb é 2 é. Ní dhéanann SEARCHB idirdhealú idir litreacha "
"móra agus beaga."

#: functions/text.xml:129
#, kde-format
msgid "SEARCHB(find_text;within_text;BytePosition Start)"
msgstr "CUARDAIGHB(aimsigh_téacs;laistigh_téacs;Tús_SuíomhBíte)"

#: functions/text.xml:144
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The T() function returns the text referred to by value. If value is, or "
"refers to, text then T returns value. If value does not refer to text then T "
"returns empty text."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm T() an téacs dá dtagraítear le luach ar ais. Más téacs é "
"luach, nó má thagraíonn sé do théacs, tugann T luach ar ais. Mura dtagraíonn "
"luach do théacs, tugann T téacs folamh ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:145
#, kde-format
msgid "T(value)"
msgstr "T(luach)"

#: functions/text.xml:146
#, kde-format
msgid "T(\"Calligra\") returns \"Calligra\""
msgstr "Tugann T(\"Calligra\") \"Calligra\" ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:147
#, kde-format
msgid "T(1.2) returns \"\" (empty text)"
msgstr "Filleann T(1.2) é seo: \"\" (empty text)"

#: functions/text.xml:159
#, kde-format
msgid "The TEXT() function converts a value to text."
msgstr "Déanann an fheidhm TEXT() luach a thiontú go téacs."

#: functions/text.xml:160
#, kde-format
msgid "TEXT(value)"
msgstr "TEXT(luach)"

#: functions/text.xml:161
#, kde-format
msgid "TEXT(1234.56) returns \"1234.56\""
msgstr "Filleann TEXT(1234.56) é seo: \"1234.56\""

#: functions/text.xml:162
#, kde-format
msgid "TEXT(\"KSpread\") returns \"KSpread\""
msgstr "Filleann TEXT(\"KSpread\") é seo: \"KSpread\""

#: functions/text.xml:170 functions/text.xml:209 functions/text.xml:213
#: functions/text.xml:404 functions/text.xml:420 functions/text.xml:433
#, kde-format
msgid "String"
msgstr "Teaghrán"

#: functions/text.xml:174
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The PROPER() function converts the first letter of each word to uppercase "
"and the rest of the letters to lowercase."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm PROPER() an chéad litir de gach focal a thiontú go "
"litreacha móra agus an chuid eile de na litreacha go litreacha beaga."

#: functions/text.xml:175
#, kde-format
msgid "PROPER(string)"
msgstr "PROPER(teaghrán)"

#: functions/text.xml:176
#, kde-format
msgid "PROPER(\"this is a title\") returns \"This Is A Title\""
msgstr "Filleann PROPER(\"this is a title\") é seo: \"This Is A Title\""

#: functions/text.xml:184
#, kde-format
msgid "First string"
msgstr "An chéad teaghrán"

#: functions/text.xml:188
#, kde-format
msgid "String to compare with"
msgstr "Teaghrán le comparáid a dhéanamh leis"

#: functions/text.xml:192
#, kde-format
msgid "Compare case-sensitive (true/false)"
msgstr "Déan comparáid idir cás-íogair (fíor/bréagach)"

#: functions/text.xml:196
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The COMPARE() function returns 0 if the two strings are equal; -1 if the "
"first one is lower in value than the second one; otherwise it returns 1."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm COMPARE() 0 ar ais má tá an dá theaghrán cothrom; -1 má tá "
"luach níos ísle ag an gcéad cheann ná an dara ceann; murach sin tugann sí 1 "
"ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:197
#, kde-format
msgid "COMPARE(string1; string2; true|false)"
msgstr "COMPARE(teaghrán1; teaghrán2; true|false)"

#: functions/text.xml:198
#, kde-format
msgid "COMPARE(\"Calligra\"; \"Calligra\"; true) returns 0"
msgstr "Tugann COMPARE(\"Calligra\"; \"Calligra\"; fíor) 0 ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:199
#, kde-format
msgid "COMPARE(\"calligra\"; \"Calligra\"; true) returns 1"
msgstr "Tugann COMPARE(\"calligra\"; \"Calligra\"; fíor) 1 ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:200
#, kde-format
msgid "COMPARE(\"kspread\"; \"Calligra\"; false) returns 1"
msgstr "Tugann COMPARE(\"kspread\"; \"Calligra\"; bréagach) 1 ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:217
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The EXACT() function returns True if these two strings are equal. Otherwise, "
"it returns False."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm EXACT() True ar ais má tá an dá theaghrán seo cothrom. "
"Seachas sin, tugann sí Bréagach ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:218
#, kde-format
msgid "EXACT(string1;string2)"
msgstr "EXACT(teaghrán1;teaghrán2)"

#: functions/text.xml:219
#, kde-format
msgid "EXACT(\"Calligra\";\"Calligra\") returns True"
msgstr "Tugann EXACT(\"Calligra\";\"Calligra\") Fíor ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:220
#, kde-format
msgid "EXACT(\"KSpread\";\"Calligra\") returns False"
msgstr "Tugann EXACT(\"KSpread\";\"Calligra\") Bréagach ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:229
#, kde-format
msgid "Text which you want to replace some characters"
msgstr "Téacs ar mhaith leat roinnt carachtar a athsholáthar"

#: functions/text.xml:233
#, kde-format
msgid "Position of the characters to replace"
msgstr "Suíomh na gcarachtar le hathsholáthar"

#: functions/text.xml:237
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of characters to replace"
msgstr "Líon na gcarachtar le hathsholáthar"

#: functions/text.xml:241 functions/text.xml:272
#, kde-format
msgid "The text that will replace characters in old text"
msgstr "An téacs a chuirfear in ionad carachtair sa seanthéacs"

#: functions/text.xml:245
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The REPLACE() function replaces part of a text string with a different text "
"string."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an fheidhm REPLACE() cuid de shreangán téacs in ionad cuid de "
"shreangán téacs le sreangán téacs difriúil."

#: functions/text.xml:246
#, kde-format
msgid "REPLACE(text;position;length;new_text)"
msgstr "REPLACE(téacs;ionad;fad;téacs_nua)"

#: functions/text.xml:247
#, kde-format
msgid "REPLACE(\"abcdefghijk\";6;5;\"-\") returns \"abcde-k\""
msgstr "Filleann REPLACE(\"abcdefghijk\";6;5;\"-\") é seo: \"abcde-k\""

#: functions/text.xml:248
#, kde-format
msgid "REPLACE(\"2002\";3;2;\"03\") returns \"2003\""
msgstr "Filleann REPLACE(\"2002\";3;2;\"03\") é seo: \"2003\""

#: functions/text.xml:260
#, kde-format
msgid "Text which you want to replace some characters using byte position"
msgstr ""
"Téacs ar mhaith leat roinnt carachtar a athsholáthar ag baint úsáide as "
"suíomh beart"

#: functions/text.xml:264
#, kde-format
msgid "Byte position of the characters to replace"
msgstr "Suíomh beart na gcarachtar le hathsholáthar"

#: functions/text.xml:268
#, kde-format
msgid "The byte length of characters to replace"
msgstr "Fad beart na gcarachtar le hathsholáthar"

#: functions/text.xml:276
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The REPLACEB() function replaces part of a text string with a different text "
"string using byte positions."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an fheidhm REPLACEB() cuid de shreang téacs in ionad cuid de "
"shreang téacs le sreang téacs dhifriúil ag baint úsáide as suíomhanna beart."

#: functions/text.xml:277
#, kde-format
msgid "REPLACEB(text;BytePosition;ByteLength Len;new_text)"
msgstr "IONADAIGHB(téacs;SuíomhBíte;FadBíte Fad;téacs_nua)"

#: functions/text.xml:297
#, kde-format
msgid "Specifies index to start the search"
msgstr "Sonraíonn sé innéacs chun an cuardach a thosú"

#: functions/text.xml:301
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FIND() function finds one text string (find_text) within another text "
"string (within_text) and returns the number of the starting point of "
"find_text, from the leftmost character of within_text."
msgstr ""
"Aimsíonn an fheidhm FIND() teaghrán téacs amháin (find_text) laistigh de "
"theaghrán téacs eile (within_text) agus tugann sí uimhir phointe tosaigh "
"find_text ar ais, ón gcarachtar is faide ar chlé de within_text."

#: functions/text.xml:302
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Parameter start_num specifies the character at which to start the search. "
"The first character is character number 1. If start_num is omitted, it is "
"assumed to be 1."
msgstr ""
"Sonraíonn an paraiméadar start_num an carachtar ag a dtosófar an cuardach. "
"Is é an chéad charachtar uimhir 1. Mura bhfágtar start_num ar lár, glactar "
"leis gurb é 1 é."

#: functions/text.xml:303
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can also use function SEARCH, but unlike SEARCH, FIND is case-sensitive "
"and does not allow wildcard characters."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an fheidhm SEARCH a úsáid freisin, ach murab ionann agus "
"SEARCH, tá FIND íogair ó thaobh cás de agus ní cheadaítear carachtair "
"fhiáine."

#: functions/text.xml:304
#, kde-format
msgid "FIND(find_text;within_text;start_num)"
msgstr "FIND(téacs_aimsithe;laistigh_téacs;uimhir_túsaigh)"

#: functions/text.xml:305
#, kde-format
msgid "FIND(\"Cal\";\"Calligra\") returns 1"
msgstr "Tugann FIND(\"Cal\";\"Calligra\") 1 ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:306
#, kde-format
msgid "FIND(\"i\";\"Calligra\") returns 5"
msgstr "Tugann FIND(\"i\";\"Calligra\") 5 ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:307
#, kde-format
msgid "FIND(\"a\";\"Sheets in Calligra\";4) returns 12"
msgstr "Tugann FIND(\"a\";\"Bileoga i Calligra\";4) 12 ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:328
#, kde-format
msgid "Specifies byte position to start the search"
msgstr "Sonraíonn sé suíomh an bheart chun an cuardach a thosú"

#: functions/text.xml:332
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The FINDB() function finds one text string (find_text) within another text "
"string (within_text) and returns the number of the starting point of "
"find_text, from the leftmost character of within_text using byte positions."
msgstr ""
"Aimsíonn an fheidhm FINDB() teaghrán téacs amháin (find_text) laistigh de "
"theaghrán téacs eile (within_text) agus tugann sí uimhir phointe tosaigh "
"find_text ar ais, ón gcarachtar is faide ar chlé de within_text ag baint "
"úsáide as suíomhanna beart."

#: functions/text.xml:333
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Parameter BytePosition specifies the character at which to start the search. "
"The first character is character number 2. If start_num is omitted, it is "
"assumed to be 2."
msgstr ""
"Sonraíonn an paraiméadar BytePosition an carachtar ag a dtosófar an "
"cuardach. Is é an chéad charachtar uimhir 2. Mura bhfágtar start_num ar lár, "
"glactar leis gurb é 2 é."

#: functions/text.xml:335
#, kde-format
msgid "FINDB(find_text;within_text;BytePosition Start)"
msgstr "FINDB(téacs_aimsithe;laistigh_téacs;Tús_SuíomhBeart)"

#: functions/text.xml:348 functions/text.xml:377 functions/text.xml:477
#: functions/text.xml:501 functions/text.xml:522 functions/text.xml:546
#: functions/text.xml:567 functions/text.xml:602 functions/text.xml:620
#: functions/text.xml:634 functions/text.xml:649 functions/text.xml:666
#, kde-format
msgid "Source string"
msgstr "Teaghrán foinseach"

#: functions/text.xml:352 ui/dialogs/LayoutDialog.cpp:144
#, kde-format
msgid "Position"
msgstr "Seasamh"

#: functions/text.xml:356
#, kde-format
msgid "Length"
msgstr "Fad"

#: functions/text.xml:360
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MID() function returns a substring that contains 'length' characters of "
"the string, starting at 'position' index."
msgstr ""
"Seolann an fheidhm MID() fo-theaghrán ina bhfuil carachtair 'fad' na "
"teaghrán, ag tosú ag innéacs 'suíomh'."

#: functions/text.xml:361
#, kde-format
msgid "MID(text;position;length)"
msgstr "MID(téacs;ionad;fad)"

#: functions/text.xml:362
#, kde-format
msgid "MID(text;position)"
msgstr "MID(téacs;ionad)"

#: functions/text.xml:363
#, kde-format
msgid "MID(\"Calligra\";2;3) returns \"all\""
msgstr "Filleann MID (\"Calligra\"; 2; 3) \"all\""

#: functions/text.xml:364
#, kde-format
msgid "MID(\"Calligra\";2) returns \"alligra\""
msgstr "Filleann MID (\"Calligra\"; 2) \"alligra\""

#: functions/text.xml:381
#, kde-format
msgid "Byte Position"
msgstr "Seasamh Beart"

#: functions/text.xml:385 functions/text.xml:505 functions/text.xml:550
#, kde-format
msgid "Byte Length"
msgstr "Fad na mBeart"

#: functions/text.xml:389
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The MIDB() function returns a substring that contains 'length' characters of "
"the string, starting at 'position' index using byte positions."
msgstr ""
"Seolann an fheidhm MIDB() fo-theaghrán ina bhfuil carachtair 'fad' na "
"teaghrán, ag tosú ag innéacs 'position' ag baint úsáide as suíomhanna beart."

#: functions/text.xml:390
#, kde-format
msgid "MIDB(text;BytePosition Start;ByteLength)"
msgstr "MIDB(téacs;TúsSeasamhBeart;FadBeart)"

#: functions/text.xml:391
#, kde-format
msgid "MIDB(text;BytePosition Start)"
msgstr "MIDB(téacs;Tosaigh Seasamh na mBeart)"

#: functions/text.xml:408
#, kde-format
msgid "The LEN() function returns the length of the string."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm LEN() fad an teaghráin ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:409
#, kde-format
msgid "LEN(text)"
msgstr "LEN(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:410
#, kde-format
msgid "LEN(\"hello\") returns 5"
msgstr "Filleann LEN(\"hello\") é seo: 5"

#: functions/text.xml:411
#, kde-format
msgid "LEN(\"KSpread\") returns 7"
msgstr "Filleann LEN(\"KSpread\") é seo: 7"

#: functions/text.xml:424
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The LENB() function returns the length of the string using byte positions."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm LENB() fad an teaghráin ar ais ag baint úsáide as "
"suíomhanna beart."

#: functions/text.xml:425
#, kde-format
msgid "LENB(text)"
msgstr "LENB(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:437
#, kde-format
msgid "The TRIM() function returns text with only single spaces between words."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm TRIM() téacs ar ais ina bhfuil spásanna aonair idir focail."

#: functions/text.xml:438
#, kde-format
msgid "TRIM(text)"
msgstr "TRIM(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:439
#, kde-format
msgid "TRIM(\" hello    KSpread   \") returns \"hello KSpread\""
msgstr "Filleann TRIM(\" hello    KSpread   \") é seo: \"hello KSpread\""

#: functions/text.xml:467
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CONCATENATE() function returns a string which is the concatenation of "
"the strings passed as parameters."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm CONCATENATE() teaghrán ar ais arb é atá ann ná nascadh na "
"dteaghrán a chuirtear ar aghaidh mar pharaiméadair."

#: functions/text.xml:468
#, kde-format
msgid "CONCATENATE(value;value;...)"
msgstr "CONCATENATE(luach;luach;...)"

#: functions/text.xml:469
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"CONCATENATE(\"Sheets\";\"Calligra\";\"KDE\") returns \"SheetsCalligraKDE\""
msgstr ""
"Tugann CONCATENATE(\"Bileoga\";\"Calligra\";\"KDE\") \"BileogaCalligraKDE\" "
"ar ais"

#: functions/text.xml:481 functions/text.xml:526
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of characters"
msgstr "Líon na gcarachtar"

#: functions/text.xml:485
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The RIGHT() function returns a substring that contains the 'length' "
"rightmost characters of the string. The whole string is returned if 'length' "
"exceeds the length of the string."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm RIGHT() fo-theaghrán ar ais ina bhfuil na carachtair "
"'length' is faide ar dheis den teaghrán. Tugtar an teaghrán iomlán ar ais má "
"sháraíonn 'length' fad an teaghráin."

#: functions/text.xml:486
#, kde-format
msgid "RIGHT(text;length)"
msgstr "RIGHT(téacs;fad)"

#: functions/text.xml:487
#, kde-format
msgid "RIGHT(\"hello\";2) returns \"lo\""
msgstr "Filleann RIGHT(\"hello\";2) é seo: \"lo\""

#: functions/text.xml:488
#, kde-format
msgid "RIGHT(\"KSpread\";10) returns \"KSpread\""
msgstr "Filleann RIGHT(\"KSpread\";10) é seo: \"KSpread\""

#: functions/text.xml:489
#, kde-format
msgid "RIGHT(\"KSpread\") returns \"d\""
msgstr "Filleann RIGHT(\"KSpread\") é seo: \"d\""

#: functions/text.xml:509
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The RIGHTB() function returns a substring that contains the 'length' "
"rightmost characters of the string using byte positions. The whole string is "
"returned if 'length' exceeds the length of the string."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm RIGHTB() fo-theaghrán ar ais ina bhfuil na carachtair "
"'length' is faide ar dheis den teaghrán ag baint úsáide as suíomhanna beart. "
"Cuirtear an teaghrán iomlán ar ais má sháraíonn 'length' fad an teaghráin."

#: functions/text.xml:510
#, kde-format
msgid "RIGHTB(text;ByteLength)"
msgstr "DEISTB(téacs;FadBheit)"

#: functions/text.xml:530
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The LEFT() function returns a substring that contains the 'length' leftmost "
"characters of the string. The whole string is returned if 'length' exceeds "
"the length of the string. It is an error for the number of characters to be "
"less than 0."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm LEFT() fo-theaghrán ar ais ina bhfuil na carachtair is "
"faide ar chlé den teaghrán 'length'. Cuirtear an teaghrán iomlán ar ais má "
"sháraíonn 'length' fad an teaghráin. Is earráid í má bhíonn líon na "
"gcarachtar níos lú ná 0."

#: functions/text.xml:531
#, kde-format
msgid "LEFT(text;length)"
msgstr "LEFT(téacs;fad)"

#: functions/text.xml:532
#, kde-format
msgid "LEFT(\"hello\";2) returns \"he\""
msgstr "Filleann LEFT(\"hello\";2) é seo: \"he\""

#: functions/text.xml:533
#, kde-format
msgid "LEFT(\"KSpread\";10) returns \"KSpread\""
msgstr "Filleann LEFT(\"KSpread\";10) é seo: \"KSpread\""

#: functions/text.xml:534
#, kde-format
msgid "LEFT(\"KSpread\") returns \"K\""
msgstr "Filleann LEFT(\"KSpread\") é seo: \"K\""

#: functions/text.xml:554
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The LEFTB() function returns a substring that contains the 'length' leftmost "
"characters of the string using byte positions. The whole string is returned "
"if 'length' exceeds the length of the string. It is an error for the number "
"of characters to be less than 0."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm LEFTB() fo-theaghrán ar ais ina bhfuil na carachtair 'fad' "
"is faide ar chlé den teaghrán ag baint úsáide as suíomhanna beart. Téann an "
"teagrán iomlán ar ais má bhíonn 'fad' níos faide ná an teagrán féin.. Is "
"earráid í má bhíonn líon na gcarachtar níos lú ná 0."

#: functions/text.xml:555
#, kde-format
msgid "LEFTB(text;ByteLength)"
msgstr "LEFTB(téacs;FadBeart)"

#: functions/text.xml:571
#, kde-format
msgid "Count of repetitions"
msgstr "Líon na n-athrá"

#: functions/text.xml:575
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The REPT() function repeats the first parameter as many times as by the "
"second parameter. The second parameter must not be negative, and this "
"function will return an empty string if the second parameter is zero (or "
"rounds down to zero)."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm REPT() an chéad pharaiméadar a athrá an oiread uaireanta "
"agus a dhéanann an dara paraiméadar. Ní mór don dara paraiméadar a bheith "
"diúltach, agus cuirfidh an fheidhm seo teaghrán folamh ar ais má tá an dara "
"paraiméadar ina náid (nó má shlánaíonn sé síos go náid)."

#: functions/text.xml:576
#, kde-format
msgid "REPT(text;count)"
msgstr "REPT(téacs;líon)"

#: functions/text.xml:577
#, kde-format
msgid "REPT(\"KSpread\";3) returns \"KSpreadKSpreadKSpread\""
msgstr "Filleann REPT(\"KSpread\";3) é seo: \"KSpreadKSpreadKSpread\""

#: functions/text.xml:578
#, kde-format
msgid "REPT(\"KSpread\";0) returns \"\""
msgstr "Filleann REPT(\"KSpread\";0) é seo: \"\""

#: functions/text.xml:590
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ROT13() function encrypts text by replacing each letter with the one 13 "
"places along in the alphabet. If the 13th position is beyond the letter Z, "
"it begins again at A (rotation)."
msgstr ""
"Criptíonn an fheidhm ROT13() téacs trí gach litir a athsholáthar leis an "
"gceann atá 13 áit níos faide síos san aibítir. Má tá an 13ú háit taobh thiar "
"den litir Z, tosaíonn sé arís ag A (rothlú)."

#: functions/text.xml:591
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"By applying the encryption function again to the resulting text, you can "
"decrypt the text."
msgstr ""
"Trí an fheidhm chriptithe a chur i bhfeidhm arís ar an téacs a eascraíonn "
"as, is féidir leat an téacs a dhíchriptiú."

#: functions/text.xml:592
#, kde-format
msgid "ROT13(Text)"
msgstr "ROT13(Téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:593
#, kde-format
msgid "ROT13(\"KSpread\") returns \"XFcernq\""
msgstr "Filleann ROT13(\"KSpread\") é seo: \"XFcernq\""

#: functions/text.xml:594
#, kde-format
msgid "ROT13(\"XFcernq\") returns \"KSpread\""
msgstr "Filleann ROT13(\"XFcernq\") é seo: \"KSpread\""

#: functions/text.xml:606
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TOGGLE() function changes lowercase characters to uppercase and "
"uppercase characters to lowercase."
msgstr ""
"Athraíonn an fheidhm TOGGLE() carachtair bheaga go mór agus carachtair mhóra "
"go mór."

#: functions/text.xml:607
#, kde-format
msgid "TOGGLE(text)"
msgstr "TOGGLE(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:608
#, kde-format
msgid "TOGGLE(\"hello\") returns \"HELLO\""
msgstr "Filleann TOGGLE(\"hello\") é seo: \"HELLO\""

#: functions/text.xml:609
#, kde-format
msgid "TOGGLE(\"HELLO\") returns \"hello\""
msgstr "Filleann TOGGLE(\"HELLO\") é seo: \"hello\""

#: functions/text.xml:610
#, kde-format
msgid "TOGGLE(\"HeLlO\") returns \"hElLo\""
msgstr "Filleann TOGGLE(\"HeLlO\") é seo: \"hElLo\""

#: functions/text.xml:624
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CLEAN() function removes every non-printable character from the string"
msgstr ""
"Baintear gach carachtar neamh-inphriontáilte as an teaghrán leis an bhfeidhm "
"CLEAN()"

#: functions/text.xml:625
#, kde-format
msgid "CLEAN(text)"
msgstr "CLEAN(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:626
#, kde-format
msgid "CLEAN(AsciiToChar(7) + \"HELLO\") returns \"HELLO\""
msgstr "Filleann CLEAN(AsciiToChar(7) + \"DIA DUIT\") é seo: \"DIA DUIT\""

#: functions/text.xml:638
#, kde-format
msgid "The SLEEK() function removes all spaces from the string."
msgstr "Baintear gach spás as an teaghrán leis an bhfeidhm SLEEK()."

#: functions/text.xml:639
#, kde-format
msgid "SLEEK(text)"
msgstr "SLEEK(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:640
#, kde-format
msgid "SLEEK(\"This is   some  text \") returns \"Thisissometext\""
msgstr "Filleann SLEEK(\"This is   some  text \") é seo: \"Thisissometext\""

#: functions/text.xml:653
#, kde-format
msgid "The UPPER() function converts a string to upper case."
msgstr "Athraíonn an fheidhm UPPER() teaghrán go cás uachtair."

#: functions/text.xml:654
#, kde-format
msgid "UPPER(text)"
msgstr "UPPER(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:655
#, kde-format
msgid "UPPER(\"hello\") returns \"HELLO\""
msgstr "Filleann UPPER(\"hello\") é seo: \"HELLO\""

#: functions/text.xml:656
#, kde-format
msgid "UPPER(\"HELLO\") returns \"HELLO\""
msgstr "Filleann UPPER(\"HELLO\") é seo: \"HELLO\""

#: functions/text.xml:670
#, kde-format
msgid "The LOWER() function converts a string to lower case."
msgstr "Athraíonn an fheidhm LOWER() teaghrán go cás beag."

#: functions/text.xml:671
#, kde-format
msgid "LOWER(text)"
msgstr "LOWER(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:672
#, kde-format
msgid "LOWER(\"hello\") returns \"hello\""
msgstr "Filleann LOWER(\"hello\") é seo: \"hello\""

#: functions/text.xml:673
#, kde-format
msgid "LOWER(\"HELLO\") returns \"hello\""
msgstr "Filleann LOWER(\"HELLO\") é seo: \"hello\""

#: functions/text.xml:683 functions/text.xml:794
#, kde-format
msgid "Character code"
msgstr "Cód carachtar"

#: functions/text.xml:687
#, kde-format
msgid "The CHAR() function returns the character specified by a number."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm CHAR() an carachtar a shonraítear le huimhir ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:688
#, kde-format
msgid "CHAR(code)"
msgstr "CHAR(cód)"

#: functions/text.xml:689
#, kde-format
msgid "CHAR(65) returns \"A\""
msgstr "Filleann CHAR(65) é seo: \"A\""

#: functions/text.xml:702
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CODE() function returns a numeric code for the first character in a text "
"string."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm CODE() cód uimhriúil ar ais don chéad charachtar i dtéacs "
"téacs."

#: functions/text.xml:703
#, kde-format
msgid "CODE(text)"
msgstr "CODE(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:704
#, kde-format
msgid "CODE(\"KDE\") returns 75"
msgstr "Filleann CODE(\"KDE\") é seo: 75"

#: functions/text.xml:717
#, kde-format
msgid "Converts text string that represents a value to the real value.  "
msgstr "Tiontaíonn sé teaghrán téacs a léiríonn luach go dtí an fíorluach.  "

#: functions/text.xml:718
#, kde-format
msgid "VALUE(text)"
msgstr "VALUE(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:719
#, kde-format
msgid "VALUE(\"14.03\") returns 14.03"
msgstr "Filleann VALUE(\"14.03\") é seo: 14.03"

#: functions/text.xml:727 functions/text.xml:756
#, kde-format
msgid "Searched text"
msgstr "Téacs cuardaithe"

#: functions/text.xml:731 functions/text.xml:760
#, kde-format
msgid "Regular expression"
msgstr "Slonn ionadaíochta"

#: functions/text.xml:735
#, kde-format
msgid "Default value (optional)"
msgstr "Luach réamhshocraithe (roghnach)"

#: functions/text.xml:739
#, kde-format
msgid "Back-reference (optional)"
msgstr "Cúltagairt (roghnach)"

#: functions/text.xml:743
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Returns a part of the string that matches a regular expression. If the "
"string does not match the given regular expression, value specified as "
"default is returned."
msgstr ""
"Tugann sé seo cuid den teaghrán ar ais a mheaitseálann slonn rialta. Mura "
"bhfuil an teaghrán ag teacht leis an slonn rialta tugtha, cuirtear an luach "
"a shonraítear mar luach réamhshocraithe ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:744
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If a back-reference is provided, then the value of that back-reference is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"Má chuirtear tagairt siar ar fáil, cuirtear luach na tagairt siar sin ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:745
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If no default value is given, an empty string is assumed. If no back-"
"reference is given, 0 is assumed (so that entire matching part is returned)."
msgstr ""
"Mura dtugtar aon luach réamhshocraithe, glactar leis go bhfuil teaghrán "
"folamh ann. Mura dtugtar aon tagairt ar ais, glactar leis go bhfuil 0 ann "
"(ionas go bhfilleann an chuid iomlán a chomhfhreagraíonn don chuid sin)."

#: functions/text.xml:746
#, kde-format
msgid "REGEXP(text; regexp; default; backref)"
msgstr "REGEXP(téacs; slonn; réamhshocrú; cúltagairt)"

#: functions/text.xml:747
#, kde-format
msgid "REGEXP(\"Number is   15.\";\"[0-9]+\") = \"15\" "
msgstr "REGEXP(\"Uimhir    15.\";\"[0-9]+\") = \"15\" "

#: functions/text.xml:748
#, kde-format
msgid "REGEXP(\"15, 20, 26, 41\";\"([0-9]+), *[0-9]+$\";\"\";1) = \"26\" "
msgstr "REGEXP(\"15, 20, 26, 41\";\"([0-9]+), *[0-9]+$\";\"\";1) = \"26\" "

#: functions/text.xml:764
#, kde-format
msgid "Replacement"
msgstr "Ionadaí"

#: functions/text.xml:768
#, kde-format
msgid "Replaces all matches of a regular expression with the replacement text"
msgstr ""
"Cuireann sé téacs athsholáthair in ionad gach meaitseáil de ghnáthléiriú"

#: functions/text.xml:769
#, kde-format
msgid "REGEXPRE(text; regexp; replacement)"
msgstr "REGEXPRE(téacs; slonn; ionadaí)"

#: functions/text.xml:770
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"REGEXPRE(\"14 and 15 and 16\";\"[0-9]+\";\"num\") returns \"num and num and "
"num\""
msgstr ""
"Filleann REGEXPRE(\"14 and 15 and 16\";\"[0-9]+\";\"num\") é seo: \"num and "
"num and num\""

#: functions/text.xml:782
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The UNICODE() function returns a unicode code point for the first character "
"in a text string."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm UNICODE() pointe cód unicode ar ais don chéad charachtar i "
"dtéacs téacs."

#: functions/text.xml:783
#, kde-format
msgid "UNICODE(text)"
msgstr "UNICODE(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:784
#, kde-format
msgid "UNICODE(\"KDE\") returns 75"
msgstr "Filleann UNICODE(\"KDE\") é seo: 75"

#: functions/text.xml:798
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The UNICHAR() function returns the character specified by a unicode code "
"point."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm UNICHAR() an carachtar a shonraítear le pointe cóid "
"unicode ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:799
#, kde-format
msgid "UNICHAR(code)"
msgstr "UNICHAR(cód)"

#: functions/text.xml:800
#, kde-format
msgid "UNICHAR(65) returns \"A\""
msgstr "Filleann UNICHAR(65) é seo: \"A\""

#: functions/text.xml:810
#, kde-format
msgid "Full width characters"
msgstr "Carachtair lánleithid"

#: functions/text.xml:814
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ASC() function returns the half-width characters corresponding to the "
"full-width argument."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ASC() na carachtair leathleithid a fhreagraíonn don "
"argóint lánleithid ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:815
#, kde-format
msgid "ASC(text)"
msgstr "ASC(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:824
#, kde-format
msgid "Half-width characters"
msgstr "Carachtair leathleithid"

#: functions/text.xml:828
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The JIS() function returns the full-width characters corresponding to the "
"half-width argument."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm JIS() na carachtair lánleithid a fhreagraíonn don argóint "
"leathleithid ar ais."

#: functions/text.xml:829
#, kde-format
msgid "JIS(text)"
msgstr "JIS(téacs)"

#: functions/text.xml:842
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BAHTTEXT() function converts a number to a text in Thai characters "
"(baht)."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fheidhm BAHTTEXT() uimhir a thiontú go téacs i gcarachtair "
"Téalainnis (baht)."

#: functions/text.xml:843
#, kde-format
msgid "BAHTTEXT(number)"
msgstr "BAHTTEXT(uimhir)"

#: functions/text.xml:844
#, kde-format
msgid "BAHTTEXT(23) returns \"ยี่สิบสามบาทถ้วน\""
msgstr "Filleann BAHTTEXT(23) \"ยี่สิบสามบาทถ้วน\""

#: functions/trig.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Trigonometric"
msgstr "Triantánúil"

#: functions/trig.xml:14
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The COS() function returns the cosine of x, where x is given in radians."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm COS() cosíneas x ar ais, áit a dtugtar x i raidiain."

#: functions/trig.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid "COS(Float)"
msgstr "COS(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:16
#, kde-format
msgid "COS(0) equals 1.0"
msgstr "Is ionann COS(0) agus 1.0"

#: functions/trig.xml:17
#, kde-format
msgid "COS(PI()/2) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann COS(PI()/2) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:31
#, kde-format
msgid "The ACOT() function returns the inverse cotangent of a number."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm ACOT() cotangán inbhéartach uimhir ar ais."

#: functions/trig.xml:32
#, kde-format
msgid "ACOT(Float)"
msgstr "ACOT(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid "ACOT(0) equals 1.57079633"
msgstr "Is ionann ACOT(0) agus 1.57079633"

#: functions/trig.xml:46
#, kde-format
msgid "The SIN() function returns the sine of x, where x is given in radians."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm SIN() sine x ar ais, áit a dtugtar x i raidiain."

#: functions/trig.xml:47
#, kde-format
msgid "SIN(Float)"
msgstr "SIN(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:48
#, kde-format
msgid "SIN(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann SIN(0) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:49
#, kde-format
msgid "SIN(PI()/2) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann SIN(PI()/2) agus 1"

#: functions/trig.xml:63
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TAN() function returns the tangent of x, where x is given in radians."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm TAN() tadhlaí x ar ais, áit a dtugtar x i raidiain."

#: functions/trig.xml:64
#, kde-format
msgid "TAN(Float)"
msgstr "TAN(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:65
#, kde-format
msgid "TAN(0.7) equals 0.84228838"
msgstr "Is ionann TAN(0.7) agus 0.84228838"

#: functions/trig.xml:66
#, kde-format
msgid "TAN(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann TAN(0) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:79
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ACOS() function returns the arc cosine in radians and the value is "
"mathematically defined to be 0 to PI (inclusive)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ACOS() an cosíneas stua ar ais i raidiain agus "
"sainmhínítear an luach go matamaiticiúil mar 0 go PI (san áireamh)."

#: functions/trig.xml:80
#, kde-format
msgid "ACOS(Float)"
msgstr "ACOS(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:81
#, kde-format
msgid "ACOS(0.8) equals 0.6435011"
msgstr "Is ionann ACOS(0.8) agus 0.6435011"

#: functions/trig.xml:82
#, kde-format
msgid "ACOS(0) equals 1.57079633"
msgstr "Is ionann ACOS(0) agus 1.57079633"

#: functions/trig.xml:95
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ASIN() function returns the arc sine in radians and the value is "
"mathematically defined to be -PI/2 to PI/2 (inclusive)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ASIN() an sine stua ar ais i raidiain agus sainmhínítear "
"an luach go matamaiticiúil mar -PI/2 go PI/2 (san áireamh)."

#: functions/trig.xml:96
#, kde-format
msgid "ASIN(Float)"
msgstr "ASIN(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:97
#, kde-format
msgid "ASIN(0.8) equals 0.92729522"
msgstr "Is ionann ASIN(0.8) agus 0.92729522"

#: functions/trig.xml:98
#, kde-format
msgid "ASIN(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann ASIN(0) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:111
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ATAN() function returns the arc tangent in radians and the value is "
"mathematically defined to be -PI/2 to PI/2 (inclusive)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm ATAN() tadhlaí an stua ar ais i raidiain agus "
"sainmhínítear an luach go matamaiticiúil mar -PI/2 go PI/2 (san áireamh)."

#: functions/trig.xml:112
#, kde-format
msgid "ATAN(Float)"
msgstr "ATAN(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:113
#, kde-format
msgid "ATAN(0.8) equals 0.67474094"
msgstr "Is ionann ATAN(0.8) agus 0.67474094"

#: functions/trig.xml:114
#, kde-format
msgid "ATAN(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann ATAN(0) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:128
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The COSH() function returns the hyperbolic cosine of x, which is defined "
"mathematically as (exp(x) + exp(-x)) / 2."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm COSH() cosíneas hipearbólach x ar ais, atá sainmhínithe go "
"matamaiticiúil mar (exp(x) + exp(-x)) / 2."

#: functions/trig.xml:129
#, kde-format
msgid "COSH(Float)"
msgstr "COSH(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:130
#, kde-format
msgid "COSH(0.8) equals 1.33743495"
msgstr "Is ionann COSH(0.8) agus 1.33743495"

#: functions/trig.xml:131
#, kde-format
msgid "COSH(0) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann COSH(0) agus 1"

#: functions/trig.xml:144
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SINH() function returns the hyperbolic sine of x, which is defined "
"mathematically as (exp(x) - exp(-x)) / 2."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm SINH() an sine hipearbóileach de x ar ais, atá "
"sainmhínithe go matamaiticiúil mar (exp(x) - exp(-x)) / 2."

#: functions/trig.xml:145
#, kde-format
msgid "SINH(Float)"
msgstr "SINH(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:146
#, kde-format
msgid "SINH(0.8) equals 0.88810598"
msgstr "Is ionann SINH(0.8) agus 0.88810598"

#: functions/trig.xml:147
#, kde-format
msgid "SINH(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann SINH(0) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:160
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The TANH() function returns the hyperbolic tangent of x, which is defined "
"mathematically as sinh(x)/cosh(x)."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm TANH() tadhlaí hipearbólach x ar ais, atá sainmhínithe go "
"matamaiticiúil mar sinh(x)/cosh(x)."

#: functions/trig.xml:161
#, kde-format
msgid "TANH(Float)"
msgstr "TANH(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:162
#, kde-format
msgid "TANH(0.8) equals 0.66403677"
msgstr "Is ionann TANH(0.8) agus 0.66403677"

#: functions/trig.xml:163
#, kde-format
msgid "TANH(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann TANH(0) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:176
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ACOSH() function calculates the inverse hyperbolic cosine of x. That is "
"the value whose hyperbolic cosine is x. If x is less than 1.0, acosh() "
"returns not-a-number (NaN) and errno is set."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm ACOSH() an cósín hipearbóileach inbhéartach de x. Is é "
"sin an luach a bhfuil a chósín hipearbóileach cothrom le x. Más lú ná 1.0 "
"atá x, tugann acosh() uimhir nach uimhir í (NaN) ar ais agus socraítear "
"errno."

#: functions/trig.xml:177
#, kde-format
msgid "ACOSH(Float)"
msgstr "ACOSH(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:178
#, kde-format
msgid "ACOSH(5) equals 2.29243167"
msgstr "Is ionann ACOSH(5) agus 2.29243167"

#: functions/trig.xml:179
#, kde-format
msgid "ACOSH(0) equals NaN"
msgstr "Is ionann ACOSH(0) agus NaN"

#: functions/trig.xml:192
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ASINH() function calculates the inverse hyperbolic sine of x; that is "
"the value whose hyperbolic sine is x."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm ASINH() an sine hipearbóileach inbhéartach de x; is é "
"sin an luach a bhfuil a sine hipearbóileach cothrom le x."

#: functions/trig.xml:193
#, kde-format
msgid "ASINH(Float)"
msgstr "ASINH(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:194
#, kde-format
msgid "ASINH(0.8) equals 0.73266826"
msgstr "Is ionann ASINH(0.8) agus 0.73266826"

#: functions/trig.xml:195
#, kde-format
msgid "ASINH(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann ASINH(0) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:208
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The ATANH() function calculates the inverse hyperbolic tangent of x; that is "
"the value whose hyperbolic tangent is x. If the absolute value of x is "
"greater than 1.0, ATANH() returns not-a-number (NaN)."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm ATANH() an tadhlaí hipearbóileach inbhéartach de x; is é "
"sin an luach a bhfuil a thadhlaí hipearbóileach cothrom le x. Más mó ná 1.0 "
"luach absalóideach x, tugann ATANH() uimhir nach uimhir í (NaN) ar ais."

#: functions/trig.xml:209
#, kde-format
msgid "ATANH(Float)"
msgstr "ATANH(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:210
#, kde-format
msgid "ATANH(0.8) equals 1.09861229"
msgstr "Is ionann ATANH(0.8) agus 1.09861229"

#: functions/trig.xml:211
#, kde-format
msgid "ATANH(0) equals 0"
msgstr "Is ionann ATANH(0) agus 0"

#: functions/trig.xml:228
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This function calculates the arc tangent of the two variables x and y. It is "
"similar to calculating the arc tangent of y/x, except that the signs of both "
"arguments are used to determine the quadrant of the result."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann an fheidhm seo tadhlaí stua an dá athróg x agus y. Tá sé cosúil le "
"tadhlaí stua y/x a ríomh, ach amháin go n-úsáidtear comharthaí an dá argóint "
"chun ceathrú an toraidh a chinneadh."

#: functions/trig.xml:229
#, kde-format
msgid "ATAN2(value;value)"
msgstr "ATAN2(luach;luach)"

#: functions/trig.xml:230
#, kde-format
msgid "ATAN2(0.5;1.0) equals 1.107149"
msgstr "Is ionann ATAN2(0.5;1.0) agus 1.107149"

#: functions/trig.xml:231
#, kde-format
msgid "ATAN2(-0.5;2.0) equals 1.815775"
msgstr "Is ionann ATAN2(-0.5;2.0) agus 1.815775"

#: functions/trig.xml:244
#, kde-format
msgid "This function transforms a radian angle to a degree angle."
msgstr "Claochlaíonn an fheidhm seo uillinn raidiáin go huillinn céime."

#: functions/trig.xml:245
#, kde-format
msgid "DEGREES(Float)"
msgstr "DEGREES(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:246
#, kde-format
msgid "DEGREES(0.78) equals 44.69"
msgstr "Is ionann DEGREES(0.78) agus 44.69"

#: functions/trig.xml:247
#, kde-format
msgid "DEGREES(1) equals 57.29"
msgstr "Is ionann DEGREES (1) agus 57.29"

#: functions/trig.xml:256
#, kde-format
msgid "Angle (degrees)"
msgstr "Uillinn (céimeanna)"

#: functions/trig.xml:260
#, kde-format
msgid "This function transforms a degree angle to a radian angle."
msgstr "Athraíonn an fheidhm seo uillinn céime go huillinn radian."

#: functions/trig.xml:261
#, kde-format
msgid "RADIANS(Float)"
msgstr "RADIANS(Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:262
#, kde-format
msgid "RADIANS(75) equals 1.308"
msgstr "Is ionann RADIANS(75) agus 1.308"

#: functions/trig.xml:263
#, kde-format
msgid "RADIANS(90) equals 1.5707"
msgstr "Is ionann RADIANS(90) agus 1.5707"

#: functions/trig.xml:272
#, kde-format
msgid "The PI() function returns the value of PI."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm PI() luach PI ar ais."

#: functions/trig.xml:273
#, kde-format
msgid "PI()"
msgstr "PI()"

#: functions/trig.xml:274
#, kde-format
msgid "PI() equals 3.141592654..."
msgstr "Is ionann PI() agus 3.141592654..."

#: functions/trig.xml:286
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CSC() function returns the cosecant of x, where x is given in radians."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm CSC() cosecant x ar ais, áit a dtugtar x i raidiain."

#: functions/trig.xml:287
#, kde-format
msgid "CSC(Float)"
msgstr "CSC (Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:288
#, kde-format
msgid "CSC(PI()/2) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann CSC(PI()/2) agus 1"

#: functions/trig.xml:300
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The CSCH() function returns the hyperbolic cosecant of x, where x is given "
"in radians."
msgstr ""
"Tugann an fheidhm CSCH() an cósecant hipearbóileach de x ar ais, áit a "
"dtugtar x i raidiain."

#: functions/trig.xml:301
#, kde-format
msgid "CSCH(Float)"
msgstr "CSCH (Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:302
#, kde-format
msgid "CSCH(PI()/2) equals 0.434537208..."
msgstr "Is ionann CSCH(PI()/2) agus 0.434537208..."

#: functions/trig.xml:314
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The SEC() function returns the secant of x, where x is given in radians."
msgstr "Tugann an fheidhm SEC() secant x ar ais, áit a dtugtar x i raidiain."

#: functions/trig.xml:315
#, kde-format
msgid "SEC(Float)"
msgstr "SEC (Snámhphointe)"

#: functions/trig.xml:316
#, kde-format
msgid "SEC(0) equals 1"
msgstr "Is ionann SEC(0) agus 1"

#: functions/trig.xml:328
#, kde-format
