#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QWidget, FontWidget)
#: ui/dialogs/FontWidget.ui:33
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can select here the font style, size and color, including some "
"additional options like underlined or stroke out text for the current cell "
"text. The lower part of the page gives a preview of the selected text "
"format.\n"
"The default font is set for all cells in the Format -> Style Manager menu "
"with the currently used style."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat stíl, méid agus dath an chló a roghnú anseo, lena n-áirítear "
"roinnt roghanna breise cosúil le téacs faoi líne nó stróc amach don téacs "
"atá sa chill reatha. Tugann an chuid íochtarach den leathanach réamhamharc "
"ar an bhformáid téacs roghnaithe.\n"
"Socraítear an cló réamhshocraithe do gach cill sa roghchlár Formáid -> "
"Bainisteoir Stíle leis an stíl atá in úsáid faoi láthair."

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QComboBox, style_combo)
#: ui/dialogs/FontWidget.ui:41
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Choose the style for your font for the currently selected cells. When you "
"select several cells with different styles, the displayed style is set to "
"Varying (No Change) and leaving it that way will keep all your current style "
"settings for each cell. Changing to Roman for example will change all the "
"selected cells style text to Roman."
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh an stíl chun do chló do na cealla atá roghnaithe faoi láthair. "
"Nuair a roghnaíonn tú roinnt cealla le stíleanna difriúla, socraítear an "
"stíl a thaispeántar go Éagsúil (Gan Athrú) agus má fhágtar mar sin í "
"coinneofar do shocruithe stíl reatha go léir do gach cill. Mar shampla, "
"athrófar stíl téacs na gcealla roghnaithe go léir go Rómhánach."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, style_combo)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, weight_combo)
#. i18n: ectx: property (specialValueText), widget (QSpinBox, size_spinner)
