msgstr "Cló Iodálach"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QComboBox, weight_combo)
#: ui/dialogs/FontWidget.ui:66
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Choose the weight for your font for the currently selected cells. When you "
"select several cells with different font weight, the displayed weight is set "
"to Varying (No Change) and leaving it that way will keep all your current "
"weight settings for each cell. Changing to Bold for example will change all "
"the selected cells font weight to Bold."
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh meáchan do chló do na cealla atá roghnaithe faoi láthair. Nuair a "
"roghnaíonn tú roinnt cealla le meáchan cló difriúil, socraítear an meáchan a "
"thaispeántar go Athraitheach (Gan Athrú) agus má fhágtar mar sin é "
"coinneofar do shocruithe meáchain reatha go léir do gach cill. Mar shampla, "
"athrófar meáchan cló na gcealla roghnaithe go Trom."

