#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgid "Generic"
msgstr "Cineálach"

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:59
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This is the default format and Calligra Sheets autodetects the actual data "
"type depending on the current cell data. By default, Calligra Sheets right "
"justifies numbers, dates and times within a cell and left justifies anything "
"else."
msgstr ""
"Seo an fhormáid réamhshocraithe agus braitheann Calligra Sheets an cineál "
"sonraí iarbhír go huathoibríoch ag brath ar shonraí reatha na cille. De réir "
"réamhshocraithe, comharann Calligra Sheets uimhreacha, dátaí agus amanna "
"laistigh de chill ar dheis agus comharann clé aon rud eile."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:65
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The number notation uses the notation you globally choose in System Settings "
"-> Common Appearance and Behavior -> Locale -> Country/Region & Language -> "
"Numbers tab. Numbers are right justified by default."
msgstr ""
"Úsáideann an nótaíocht uimhreacha an nótaíocht a roghnaíonn tú go domhanda i "
"Socruithe Córais -> Cuma agus Iompar Coiteann -> Logántacht -> Tír/Réigiún & "
"Teanga -> cluaisín Uimhreacha. De réir réamhshocraithe, bíonn na huimhreacha "
"comhfhadaithe ar dheis."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:69
#, kde-format
msgid "Percent"
msgstr "Céatadán"

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:71
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When you have a number in the current cell and you switch from the dcell "
"format from Generic to Percent, the current cell number will be multiplied "
"by 100%.\n"
"For example if you enter 12 and set the cell format to Percent, the number "
"will then be 1,200 %. Switching back to Generic cell format will bring it "
"back to 12.\n"
"You can also use the Percent icon in the Format Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bhíonn uimhir sa chill reatha agus má athraíonn tú ón bhformáid "
"dcell ó Generic go Percent, déanfar uimhir na cille reatha a iolrú faoi "
"100%.\n"
"Mar shampla, má chuireann tú 12 isteach agus má shocraíonn tú formáid na "
"cille go Percent, beidh an uimhir ansin 1,200%. Má athraíonn tú ar ais go "
"formáid cille Generic, tabharfar ar ais go 12 í.\n"
"Is féidir leat an deilbhín Percent a úsáid sa Bharra Uirlisí Formáide "
"freisin."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:76
#, kde-format
msgid "Money"
msgstr "Airgead"

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:78
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The Money format converts your number into money notation using the settings "
"globally fixed in System Settings -> Common Appearance and Behavior -> "
"Locale -> Country/Region & Language -> Money. The currency symbol will be "
"displayed and the precision will be the one set in System Settings.\n"
"You can also use the Currency icon in the Format Toolbar to set the cell "
"formatting to look like your current currency."
msgstr ""
"Déanann an fhormáid Airgid d’uimhir a thiontú go nótaíocht airgid ag baint "
"úsáide as na socruithe domhanda atá socraithe i Socruithe Córais -> Dealramh "
"agus Iompar Coiteann -> Logántacht -> Tír/Réigiún & Teanga -> Airgead. "
"Taispeánfar an tsiombail airgeadra agus is é an cruinneas atá socraithe i "
"Socruithe Córais.\n"
"Is féidir leat an deilbhín Airgeadra sa Bharra Uirlisí Formáide a úsáid "
"freisin chun formáidiú na cille a shocrú chun go mbeidh cuma d’airgeadra "
"reatha air."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:83
#, kde-format
msgid "Scientific"
msgstr "Eolaíoch"

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:85
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The scientific format changes your number using the scientific notation. For "
"example, 0.0012 will be changed to 1.2E-03. Going back using Generic cell "
"format will display 0.0012 again."
msgstr ""
"Athraíonn an fhormáid eolaíoch d’uimhir ag baint úsáide as an nótaíocht "
"eolaíoch. Mar shampla, athrófar 0.0012 go 1.2E-03. Má théann tú ar ais ag "
"baint úsáide as formáid chealla Cineálach, taispeánfar 0.0012 arís."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:91
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The fraction format changes your number into a fraction. For example, 0.1 "
"can be changed to 1/8, 2/16, 1/10, etc. You define the type of fraction by "
"choosing it in the field on the right. If the exact fraction is not possible "
"in the fraction mode you choose, the nearest closest match is chosen.\n"
" For example: when we have 1.5 as number, we choose Fraction and Sixteenths "
"1/16 the text displayed into cell is \"1 8/16\" which is an exact fraction. "
"If you have 1.4 as number in your cell and you choose Fraction and "
"Sixteenths 1/16 then the cell will display \"1 6/16\" which is the nearest "
"closest Sixteenth fraction."
msgstr ""
"Athraíonn an fhormáid codáin d’uimhir ina codán. Mar shampla, is féidir 0.1 "
"a athrú go 1/8, 2/16, 1/10, srl. Sainmhíníonn tú an cineál codáin trína "
"roghnú sa réimse ar dheis. Mura féidir an codán cruinn a fháil sa mhodh "
"codáin a roghnaíonn tú, roghnaítear an ceann is gaire.\n"
"Mar shampla: nuair a bhíonn 1.5 againn mar uimhir, roghnaímid Codán agus Sé "
"Déag 1/16, is é an téacs a thaispeántar sa chill ná \"1 8/16\" ar codán "
"cruinn é. Má tá 1.4 mar uimhir i do chill agus má roghnaíonn tú Codán agus "
"Sé Déag 1/16, taispeánfaidh an chill \"1 6/16\" arb é an Sé Déag codán is "
"gaire é."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:100
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"To enter a date, you should enter it in one of the formats set in System "
"Settings -> Common Appearance and Behavior -> Locale -> Country/Region & "
"Language -> Time & Dates. There are two formats set here: the date format "
"and the short date format.\n"
"Just like you can drag down numbers you can also drag down dates and the "
"next cells will also get dates."
msgstr ""
"Chun dáta a iontráil, ba chóir duit é a iontráil i gceann de na formáidí atá "
"socraithe i Socruithe Córais -> Dealramh agus Iompar Coiteann -> Logántacht -"
"> Tír/Réigiún & Teanga -> Am & Dátaí. Tá dhá fhormáid socraithe anseo: an "
"fhormáid dáta agus an fhormáid dáta gearr.\n"
"Díreach mar is féidir leat uimhreacha a tharraingt anuas is féidir leat "
"dátaí a tharraingt anuas freisin agus gheobhaidh na cealla eile dátaí "
"freisin."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:107
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This formats your cell content as a time. To enter a time, you should enter "
"it in the Time format set in System Settings -> Common Appearance and "
"Behavior -> Locale -> Country/Region & Language -> Date & Time. In the Cell "
"Format dialog box you can set how the time should be displayed by choosing "
"one of the available time format options. The default format is the system "
"format set in System Settings. When the number in the cell does not make "
"sense as a time, Calligra Sheets will display 00:00 in the global format you "
"have in System Settings."
msgstr ""
"Formáidíonn sé seo ábhar do chealla mar am. Chun am a iontráil, ba chóir "
"duit é a iontráil san fhormáid Ama atá socraithe i Socruithe Córais -> "
"Dealramh agus Iompar Coiteann -> Logántacht -> Tír/Réigiún & Teanga -> Dáta "
"& Am. Sa bhosca dialóige Formáid Cealla is féidir leat a shocrú conas ba "
"chóir an t-am a thaispeáint trí cheann de na roghanna formáide ama atá ar "
"fáil a roghnú. Is é an fhormáid réamhshocraithe an fhormáid chórais atá "
"socraithe i Socruithe Córais. Nuair nach bhfuil ciall leis an uimhir sa "
"chill mar am, taispeánfaidh Calligra Sheets 00:00 san fhormáid dhomhanda atá "
"agat i Socruithe Córais."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:113
#, kde-format
msgid "Datetime"
msgstr "Dáta-am"

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:115
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"To enter a datetime, you should enter it in one of the formats set in System "
"Settings -> Common Appearance and Behavior -> Locale -> Country/Region & "
"Language -> Time & Dates. There are two formats set here: the date format "
"and the short date format.\n"
"Just like you can drag down numbers you can also drag down dates and the "
"next cells will also get datetimes."
msgstr ""
"Chun dáta agus am a iontráil, ba chóir duit é a iontráil i gceann de na "
"formáidí atá socraithe i Socruithe Córais -> Dealramh agus Iompar Coiteann -"
"> Logántacht -> Tír/Réigiún & Teanga -> Am & Dátaí. Tá dhá fhormáid "
"socraithe anseo: an fhormáid dáta agus an fhormáid dáta ghearr.\n"
"Díreach mar is féidir leat uimhreacha a tharraingt anuas is féidir leat "
"dátaí a tharraingt anuas freisin agus gheobhaidh na cealla seo a leanas "
"dátaí agus amanna freisin."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:122
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This formats your cell content as text. This can be useful if you want a "
"number treated as text instead as a number, for example for a ZIP code. "
"Setting a number as text format will left justify it. When numbers are "
"formatted as text, they cannot be used in calculations or formulas. It also "
"change the way the cell is justified."
msgstr ""
"Formáidíonn sé seo ábhar do chealla mar théacs. Is féidir leis seo a bheith "
"úsáideach más mian leat go ndéanfaí uimhir a láimhseáil mar théacs seachas "
"mar uimhir, mar shampla i gcás cód ZIP. Má shocraítear uimhir mar fhormáid "
"téacs, fágfar í mar chomhfhírinniú. Nuair a fhormáidítear uimhreacha mar "
"théacs, ní féidir iad a úsáid i ríomhanna ná i bhfoirmlí. Athraíonn sé "
"freisin an chaoi a bhfuil an chill comhfhírinnithe."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:127
#, kde-format
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Saincheaptha"

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:128
#, kde-format
msgid "The custom format does not work yet. To be enabled in the next release."
msgstr ""
"Ní oibríonn an fhormáid saincheaptha go fóill. Le cumasú sa chéad eisiúint "
"eile."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:136
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This will display a preview of your choice so you can know what it does "
"before clicking the OK button to validate it."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánfaidh sé seo réamhamharc de do rogha ionas gur féidir leat a fháil "
"amach cad a dhéanann sé sula gcliceálann tú ar an gcnaipe Ceart go leor chun "
"é a bhailíochtú."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:146
#, kde-format
msgid "Displays choices of format for the fraction, date or time formats."
msgstr "Taispeánann sé roghanna formáide do na formáidí codáin, dáta nó ama."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:156
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can add here a Postfix such as a $HK symbol to the end of each cell "
"content in the checked format."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat Iar-fhíric a chur leis anseo, amhail siombail $HK, ag "
"deireadh ábhar gach cille san fhormáid sheiceáil."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:159
#, kde-format
msgid "variable"
msgstr "athróg"

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:163
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can control how many digits are displayed after the decimal point for "
"numeric values. This can also be changed using the Increase precision or "
"Decrease precision icons in the Format toolbar. "
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat rialú a dhéanamh ar líon na ndigit a thaispeántar i ndiaidh "
"an phointe deachúil le haghaidh luachanna uimhriúla. Is féidir é seo a athrú "
"freisin trí úsáid a bhaint as na deilbhíní Cruinneas a Mhéadú nó Cruinneas a "
"Laghdú sa bharra uirlisí Formáide. "

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:168
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can add here a Prefix such as a $ symbol at the start of each cell "
"content in the checked format."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat réimír a chur leis anseo, amhail siombail $, ag tús gach "
"ábhar cille san fhormáid atá seiceáilte."

#: ui/dialogs/LayoutPage_Float.cpp:172
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can choose whether positive values are displayed with a leading + sign "
"and whether negative values are shown in red."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat a roghnú an dtaispeántar luachanna dearfacha le comhartha + "
"ag tús an liosta agus an dtaispeántar luachanna diúltacha i ndath dearg."

