#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QGroupBox, horizontalGroup)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:45
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<qt>Set the content position horizontally in the cell.\n"
"<b>Standard</b> is default and is set from the format you choose.\n"
"<b>Left</b> means the content will be displayed on the left of the cell.\n"
"<b>Center</b> means the content will be in the center horizontally in the "
"cell.\n"
"<b>Right</b> means the content of the cell will be displayed on the right of "
"the cell.</qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt>Socraigh suíomh an ábhair go cothrománach sa chill.\n"
"Is é <b>Caighdeánach</b> an réamhshocrú agus socraítear é ón bhformáid a "
"roghnaíonn tú.\n"
"Ciallaíonn <b>Clé</b> go dtaispeánfar an t-ábhar ar thaobh na láimhe clé den "
"chill.\n"
"Ciallaíonn <b>Lár</b> go mbeidh an t-ábhar sa lár go cothrománach sa chill.\n"
"Ciallaíonn <b>Deas</b> go dtaispeánfar ábhar na cille ar thaobh na láimhe "
"deise den chill.</qt>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, standard)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:54
#, kde-format
msgid "Standard"
msgstr "Caighdeánach"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, center)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:68
#, kde-format
msgid "Center"
msgstr "Lár"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox4)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:85
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Your text will appear oriented in the angle you set here. Positive values "
"will move it counter-clockwise and negative values will move it clockwise."
msgstr ""
"Beidh do théacs le feiceáil san uillinn a shocraigh tú anseo. Bogfaidh "
"luachanna dearfacha é tuathal agus bogfaidh luachanna diúltacha é deiseal."

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox4)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:88
#, kde-format
msgid "Rotation"
msgstr "Rothlú"

#. i18n: ectx: property (suffix), widget (QSpinBox, spinBox3)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:110
#, kde-format
msgid "°"
msgstr "°"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QGroupBox, buttonGroup2)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:132
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<qt>Set the content position vertically in the cell.\n"
"<b>Top</b> means the content will be displayed on top of the cell.\n"
"<b>Middle</b> means the content will be in the middle vertically in the "
"cell.\n"
"<b>Bottom</b> means the content of the cell will be displayed at the bottom "
"of the cell.</qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt>Socraigh suíomh an ábhair go hingearach sa chill.\n"
"Ciallaíonn <b>Barr</b> go mbeidh an t-ábhar le feiceáil ar bharr na cille.\n"
"Ciallaíonn <b>Lár</b> go mbeidh an t-ábhar sa lár go hingearach sa chill.\n"
"Ciallaíonn <b>Bun</b> go mbeidh ábhar na cille le feiceáil ag bun na cille.</"
"qt>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, top)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:141
#, kde-format
msgid "Top"
msgstr "Barr"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, middle)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:148
#, kde-format
msgid "Middle"
msgstr "Lár"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, bottom)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:155
#, kde-format
msgid "Bottom"
msgstr "Bun"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QGroupBox, indentGroup)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:165
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the amount of indent that will be used in the cell when you choose the "
"Increase Indent or Decrease Indent actions."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh an méid eangaithe a úsáidfear sa chill nuair a roghnaíonn tú na "
"gníomhartha Méadaigh an tEangú nó Laghdaigh an tEangú."

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, indentGroup)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:168
#, kde-format
msgid "Indent"
msgstr "Eangaigh"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox3)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:177
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This is only available when the rotation is 0°.\n"
"Wrap text wraps the text so it fits in the previous cell size. If this is "
"not checked, the text will stay on one line and the cell size will be "
"adjusted to contain the text.\n"
"Vertical text puts your text vertically."
msgstr ""
"Níl sé seo ar fáil ach amháin nuair atá an rothlú 0°.\n"
"Fillteann téacs fillte an téacs ionas go n-oirfidh sé don mhéid cille roimhe "
"seo. Mura bhfuil tic curtha leis seo, fanfaidh an téacs ar líne amháin agus "
"déanfar méid na cille a choigeartú chun an téacs a choinneáil.\n"
"Cuireann téacs ingearach do théacs go hingearach."

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox3)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:180
#, kde-format
msgid "Text Option"
msgstr "Rogha Téacs"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, multi)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:186
#, kde-format
msgid "Wrap text"
msgstr "Fillte téacs"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, vertical)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:193
#, kde-format
msgid "Vertical text"
msgstr "Téacs ingearach"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, shrinkToFit)
#: ui/dialogs/PositionWidget.ui:200
#, kde-format
msgid "Shrink to fit"
msgstr "Laghdaigh chun go n-oirfidh sé"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QWidget, ProtectionWidget)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:35
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This tab enables you to set Cell Protection. All cells are protected by "
"default (that means cell content cannot be changed) and for the cell "
"protection to be active you also need to protect the sheet using the Tools -"
"> Protect Sheet... menu and to provide a password.\n"
"You can also hide the cell formula in order to protect the way you calculate "
"the formula. This also needs to enable sheet protection to work.\n"
"You can hide the cell content with Hide all and again this needs sheet "
"protection.\n"
"You can learn more about all these settings in the User Manual in the "
"Advanced Calligra Sheets chapter."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an cluaisín seo ar do chumas Cosaint Cille a shocrú. Tá gach cill "
"cosanta de réir réamhshocraithe (is é sin le rá nach féidir ábhar na cille a "
"athrú) agus chun go mbeidh an chosaint cille gníomhach ní mór duit an "
"bhileog a chosaint freisin ag baint úsáide as an roghchlár Uirlisí -> Cosain "
"Bileog... agus pasfhocal a sholáthar.\n"
"Is féidir leat foirmle na cille a cheilt freisin chun an chaoi a ríomhann tú "
"an fhoirmle a chosaint. Caithfidh cosaint bileoige a chumasú freisin.\n"
"Is féidir leat ábhar na cille a cheilt le Folaigh gach rud agus arís "
"teastaíonn cosaint bileoige chuige seo.\n"
"Is féidir leat tuilleadh eolais a fháil faoi na socruithe seo go léir sa "
"Lámhleabhar Úsáideora sa chaibidil Bileoga Calligra Ardleibhéil."

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox2)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:41
#, kde-format
msgid "Printing"
msgstr "Ag priontáil"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, m_bDontPrint)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:48
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the content of the cell will not be printed. If this is not "
"checked (default), the cell content will be printed.\n"
"Note that you can print it even if the cell is protected"
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil tic sa rogha seo, ní phriontálfar ábhar na cille. Mura bhfuil "
"tic sa rogha seo (réamhshocrú), priontáilfear ábhar na cille.\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara gur féidir leat é a phriontáil fiú má tá an chill faoi "
"chosaint"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, m_bDontPrint)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:51
#, kde-format
msgid "&Do not print text"
msgstr "&Ná priontáil téacs"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, groupBox1)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:61
#, kde-format
msgid "Protection"
msgstr "Cosaint"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, m_bHideAll)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:69
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This hides the cell content and works only when the sheet is protected. "
"Whether the cell itself is protected or not does not matter."
msgstr ""
"Folaíonn sé seo ábhar na cille agus ní oibríonn sé ach nuair a bhíonn an "
"bhileog faoi chosaint. Is cuma an bhfuil an chill féin faoi chosaint nó nach "
"bhfuil."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, m_bHideAll)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:72
#, kde-format
msgid "Hide &all"
msgstr "Folaigh &uile"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, m_bIsProtected)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:97
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the cell content will be protected. This is the default "
"behavior. You need to protect the whole sheet using the Tools -> Protect "
"Sheet... menu option for this individual cell protection to work. See the "
"manual for more details in the Advanced Calligra Sheets chapter. When a cell "
"is protected, its content cannot be changed."
msgstr ""
"Má tá sé seo seiceáilte, beidh ábhar na cille cosanta. Seo an t-iompar "
"réamhshocraithe. Ní mór duit an bhileog iomlán a chosaint ag baint úsáide as "
"an rogha roghchláir Uirlisí -> Cosain Bileog... chun go n-oibreoidh an "
"chosaint cille aonair seo. Féach an lámhleabhar le haghaidh tuilleadh sonraí "
"sa chaibidil Bileoga Calligra Ardleibhéil. Nuair a bhíonn cill cosanta, ní "
"féidir a hábhar a athrú."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, m_bIsProtected)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:100
#, kde-format
msgid "&Protected"
msgstr "&Cosanta"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, m_bHideFormula)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:130
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When this is checked, the cell is still visible. However, its contents do "
"not appear in the Formula bar. Hiding formula is only working for cells that "
"contain formulae so the user cannot view the formula. And the sheet must be "
"protected for this to work."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bhíonn tic sa rogha seo, bíonn an chill fós le feiceáil. Mar sin "
"féin, ní fheictear a hábhar sa bharra Foirmlí. Ní oibríonn an fhoirmle a "
"cheilt ach amháin i gcás cealla ina bhfuil foirmlí agus mar sin ní féidir "
"leis an úsáideoir an fhoirmle a fheiceáil. Agus ní mór an bhileog a chosaint "
"chun go n-oibreoidh sé seo."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (Calligra::Sheets::LayoutCheckbox, m_bHideFormula)
#: ui/dialogs/ProtectionWidget.ui:133
#, kde-format
msgid "&Hide formula"
msgstr "&Folaigh an fhoirmle"

